\id DEU  
\h Danbu Nina 
\toc1 Danbu Ni Na 
\toc2 Danbu Ni Na 
\toc3 Danbu Ni Na 
\mt1 Mose Lekhabu Ngana  
\mt2 DANBU NINA  
\mt3 Danbu nina sung thu umdan  
\ip Hiche lekhabua kon hin thohgimna, patepna, lung opkaina, kitepna, kinepna leh tahsanna hichengse mudoh in aum'in ahi. Tahsan kiti hi achama thilsem banga semthu thei ahipoi, ti vetsahna chule tahsan kiti hi mimal tompanna leh Pathen mingailut kiguijopna akon bou ahi.  
\ip Danbua kon hin Israel te Canaan gam jon a Jordan vadung agalkai nau ahilchen in, Mose’n mipi henga aseiyin, Egypt gamsunga thil kidangtah tah Pakaiyin akilah sah ho ageldoh sah sohkei uve. Mose chun Pathen thangvahna jeng aseiyin, Pathen'in ichan geiya amite akhohsah a chule ahuhdoh ham, ti thudol jong aseiyin ahi. Hichea kon hin Pakaiyin gentheite, meithai, chaga khohsahna nasatah aneiye, ti muchet ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa, akijih kum chule akijih lona  
\ip Danbu hi Mose’n 1406 BC kuma anajih ahi. Chule Danbu Lekhabu hin Israel te Canaan gam alut kon uva thil umdan ho aseiyin, Mose chun Israel mite chu milim semthu ahou nauva konna akiheimangna diuvin temna aneiyin, apu-apate hou khanga Pathen toh kitepna chu athah beh in alah uvah akilahsah in ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Mose’n Pathen thupeh banga ahilchah  
\p
\v 1 Mose’n thu hichengse hi, Israel mite lhumlam Jordan vadung gamthip noiya aum laiyun aheng uvah ana seipeh in, chule Jordan phaicham Suph, Paran, Tophel, Laban, Hazeroth le Di-zahab kimlaiya chun ngahmun akisem un ahi.  
\v 2 Sinai molsang apat Kadesh-barnea chan chu angaiya banga nisom le khat kenglam ahin, chule Seir molsang kijotpa ahi.  
\v 3 Israel mite chun kum somli jou lhasom le lhakhat lhinna nikho masapen in Egypt gamsung ahin dalha tauvin, Pakaiyin Mose henga aseipeh bang chun Israel mite jouse aseipeh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 4 Hichengse hi Amor mite Sihon lengpa Heshbon alal laiya thilsoh ahin, chule Bashan Og lengpan Ashtaroth le Edrei avaihop lai ahi.  
\v 5 Israel mite Jordan vadung solam Moab gam'a aum laiyuva Pakaiyin athupeh bangin Mose’n jong chingthei tah a aheng uva ahilchen chu anoiya chengse hi ahi.   
\s1 Sinai dalha dinga thupeh  
\p
\v 6 “Sinai molsanga kaum laiyun Pakai Pathen'in kaheng uva hiti hin aseiye, 'Hiche molchunga hin phat sottah naum tauve.'  
\v 7 Tun ngahmun phelhauvin cheuvin. Amor mite chenna thinglhang gam chule akimvel jouse le Jordan phaicham, Canaan mite, Lebanon mite chule Euphrate vadung chan gei cheuvin.  
\v 8 Vetan, Keiman hiche gam leiset jouse hi nangma kapeh nahi! Chen lang agam khu galo tan, ajeh chu hiche gam leiset jouse hi Pakaiyin peh dinga kitepsa napu napa teu Abraham, Isaac chule Jacob chilhah te jouse loding ahi.”   
\s1 Mose'n ama phung cheh akon lamkai alhendoh  
\p
\v 9 Mose’n aseikit in, hiche phatlai chun kana seiyin, nangho jouse ka changa kavaihom hi keima din ahahsa lheh jeng tai.  
\v 10 Pakai na Pathen'in na mite apun sah in, ahsi jat in na semdoh tauve!  
\v 11 Chule napu napa khanga pat Pakai na Pathen chun asang sang'in napunbe sah uhen, akitepna bangin phatthei naboh uhen!  
\v 12 Nangho vetsui hi abai tapon, naboina hou iti kachanga ka suhlhap jou ding ham?  
\v 13 Hijeh chun ama ama insung kaiya kon'in thu hethem upa phabep lheng doh tem in, keiman amaho chu nangho lamkaiya ka pansah ding ahi.  
\v 14 Nangin jong, ‘Na thilgon hi aphalheh jenge tin nana seiye.’  
\v 15 Keiman upa ching le thil hethem phabep ama insung kaiya konna na lhendoh ho chu kapuijin, nangma thutan vaihom dinga ka pansah ahi. Mi phabep chu mi asang chunga vaihom din apangin, mi phabep jakhat chung, mi somnga chung chule mi phabep chu mi som chunga ding ahi.  
\v 16 Hichun keiman thutan vaihom ho henga ka seiyin, ‘Nanghon na sopiu Israel mite le gamdang mi nalah uva hung cheng hoa konna thutan ding nahin mudoh diu ahi. Na dinmun cheh uva dettah in pang cheh uvin.  
\v 17 Chule thutanna hoa sihneina ima nei hihhel uvin. Ahao hihen avai chung hijongleh thutan ding chu phatah in kholchil sohkeiyun. Mi khattou lunghan jeh in kicha hih uvin, ajeh chu adih e tia thu natan uchu Pathen dei ahi. Amavang thutan ding ahahsa behseh aum leh keima henga hin lhut uvin, keiman hichu katan ding ahi.  
\v 18 Hichun keiman ijakai bol ding jouse naheng uva ka seipeh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 19 Pakai, Pathen'in eithupeh bang uchun Sinai mol dalhan gamthip lah a kichapum in ikitol uvin, Amor mite chenna lam ijon tauvin Kadesh-barnea mun ilhung tauve.  
\v 20 Hichun keiman hiti hin kaseiye, ‘Tun nangho Amor mite chenna gam Pakai iPathen'in eipeh nau gam ilhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Vetan! Pakaiyin na masang lam uva gam nakoi peh tauvin ahi. Cheuvin lang galo tauvin ajeh chu na Pakai na Pathen uchun nangho dinga kitepna anei ahi. Kicha hih uvin, chule lungthoi hih un, ati.  
\v 22 Ahinlah na boncha uvin kahenga hiti hin nasei uve, ‘Amasan ei lamkai diuvin misol masa ute chutileh ama hon ilhunna diu lampi aboncha ahin hetthem diu, chuteng hoilai khopi mun'a chu ilhun thei uvem kicheh ding ahi.  
\v 23 Hichu pha kasan, mi som le ni ka lhengdoh in, ama ama insung kailhah a konna mikhat cheh ahiuve.  
\v 24 Amaho gamthip lama chun achepeh uvin chule Eshcol phaicham ahung gei tauvin, hiche mun'a chun aum tauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Ama hon gamsung gasoh phabep ahin choi un hiti hin asei uve. “Pakai, Pathen'in eipeh nau gam khu tahbeh in apha lheh jenge, atiuvin ahi.”   
\s1 Mipi phunchelna  
\p
\v 26 Ahinlah nang hon Pakai, Pathen thupeh nit louvin agamsunga che ding nanom pouve. \x + \xo 1:26 \xt Danbu Ni Na 9:23; Heb 3:16\x*  
\v 27 Na ponbuh uva kon'in hiti hin na seiyun, ‘Pakaiyin eimu dauvin ahileh ‘Hijeh a chu Egypt gam'a konna eihin puidoh uva Amor mite thagam sah ding ati, ahi.’  
\v 28 Tua hoiya iche diu hitam? Isopi te houvin thil um chan ijakai asei uvin, ‘Agam mite khu eiho sang'in asang thei un chule eiho sang'in jong athahat theijun, akhopi hou jong alen thei in chule khopi kul kigen ho jong asang theijin chunga thangvan aphai! Chule hiche mun'a chun Anak chilhah te jong kamu uve.’  
\v 29 Ahinlah keiman hiti hin ka seipeh uve, ‘Amaho jeh in tija hih in, ki jong kicha hih un!  
\v 30 Na Pakai, na Pathen'u na masang lam uva ache jingin ahi. Egypt gam'a namu bang uva Pakaiyin nangho dinga gal asat ding ahi.  
\v 31 Mipan acha akhohsah bangin Pakai na Pathen'in nache lena gamthip lamlhung keiya iti nahin pui galkai ham, ti nangman na hesoh keiyin ahi. \x + \xo 1:31 \xt Act 13:18\x*  
\v 32 Ahinlah hichan geiya anatoh jouvin nang hon Pakai na Pathen'u na tahsan hih laiyuve, \x + \xo 1:32 \xt Heb 3:19\x*  
\v 33 ama chu na masang lam uva achen munpha laipen achun ngahmun asemin chule janteng meivah khoma naveng jiuvin, sunteng meibol khoma na lhonpi jiuvin ahi.’   
\s1 Kiphinna jeh a gotna  
\p
\v 34 Pakaiyin na phunchelna hou ahin jadoh tan ahileh, alunghang lheh jeng tan, lungdamsel in kitepna aneiyin ahi. \x + \xo 1:34 \xt Heb 3:18\x*  
\v 35 Itinama jongleh nang hon hiche khanga lungphat louna keng puma napu napa teu khanga pat peh dinga ka tepsa gam khu nalo louhel diu,  
\v 36 Jephunneh chapa Caleb bouvin alo ding ahi. Aman hiche gam hi amu ding ahi, ajeh chu lunglha louva Pakai thupeh juijing ahi. Ama le achilhah ten hiche gam sung phabep masanga agamu masat bang uva alo diu ahi.  
\v 37 Nangho jeh in keima chung jenga jong Pakai alung phamo tai. Aman aseiyin, “Mose, nangma jeng jong gam tepna nalut louding ahi!”  
\v 38 Nangma khela Nun chapa Joshua chun mipi aboncha gamsung chan a alamkai ding ahi. Ama chu tilkhouvin, ajeh chu aman Israel miten alodiu gamsung chan a alamkai ding ahitai.  
\v 39 Keiman gam khu na chate kho hepha loulai ho ka chensah ding ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon eimat gam diu ahi tin na kichauve, hinlah ama hon alo diu ahi.  
\v 40 Tun nangho kileuvin gamthip jotpeh un, Twipi San lam jonin che tauvin.  
\v 41 Chule na chonset phong uvin, “Pakai adia chonse kahi tauve! Pakai thupeh banga gamsunga khu kache uva gal kaga sat diu ahi.” Ajeh chu na mite hon athal cheh akichoiyun, gamsung lo ding khu baikhen chan agel un ahi.  
\v 42 Amavang Pakaiyin nangho kom'a seiyin tin thupeh aneiye, ‘Galsat nasat louding ahi, ajeh chu keiman kalhonpi louding, nangho bou na cheuva ahileh, nagal miteuvin nasat gam diu ahi.  
\v 43 Hiche hi keiman ka seipeh nahiuve, hinlah nangaisah pouvin, avelin Pakai doumah bolin galsat in nakon un ahi.  
\v 44 Chuin Amor mite chu khoite jat bangin ahung kon tauvin, Seir le Hormah chan geiyin nahin delkhum tauve.  
\v 45 Chuin Pakai henga kappum in nakile uvin, hinlah Aman nataona asang tapoi.  
\v 46 Hiti chun Kadesh mun'a phat sottah nacheng tauvin ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Gamthip noiya kum phabep  
\p
\v 1 Chuin gamthip lang jondin ikiheiyun Twipisan lam jon in icheuvin, Pakaiyin asei bangin, Seir molsang lama chun phat sottah lungdong in ivahleleuvin ahi. \x + \xo 2:1 \xt Minbu 21:4\x*  
\v 2 Hichun Pakaiyin hiti hin eiseipeh in,  
\v 3 Nangho gamthip lah a lungdong in naum sot lheh tauve; sahlam gamkai mano tauvin.  
\v 4 Thupeh hichengse hi mipi henga seiyin: “Nanghon na sopiu Esau chilhah Edom mite chenna Seir mun na jotpa diu ahi. Edom mite chu kichat nan alhun den theiju ahi, ching theiyun.” \x + \xo 2:4 \xt Semtilbu 36:8\x*  
\v 5 Aheng uva ima na ngeh lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu keiman Seir gam jouse amaho kapeh ahitan, nangho gambeh neocha jong na kipe theilou diu ahi.  
\v 6 An leh twi nangai chat uva ahileh, aman napeh uva na kichoh cheh diu ahi.  
\v 7 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in nabol natoh jouseu phatthei abohtan. Aman gamthip noiya kal nason chan geiyuva pat ave lhih jingin. Kum somli sung in Pakai, Pathen'in lhasam louvin na umpiuve.  
\v 8 Chuin Esau chilhah ho chenna Seir mun igalkai uvin. Arabah phaicham kiti Elath le Ezion-geber akon hungna lampi vang ipeldoh uvin ahi. Hiti chun sahlam nelgam lam juiyin Moab lam ino tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Pakaiyin aseiyin, “Lot chilhah Moab mite na suhgim lou diu, gal jong nabolkhum louhel diu ahi. Ar gam Leiset pumpi amaho kapeh ahitan, nangho gam beh neokhat jong na chan thei lou diu ahi.” \x + \xo 2:9 \xt Semtilbu 19:37\x*  
\v 10 (Mihat Emim mite chu Ar mun'a ana cheng uvin ahi. Amaho chu asang thei un chule atha u-jong ahat in Anakim mite tobang chu ahiuve.  
\v 11 Emimte le Anakim ho chu Rephaim tinjong akiheuvin, Moab miten vang Emim tin akou un ahi.  
\v 12 Masang chun Hor mite chu Seir mun'a ana cheng uvin, hinlah amaho chu Esau chilhah te hotoh gal ana kibol uvin, Hor mite chu ana jamdoh tauvin. Israel miten Canaan mite adel gam uva agam pumpi Pakaiyin apeh tobang’u ahi.)  
\v 13 Mose’n avelin aseiyin, ‘Chuin Pakaiyin iheng uva hiti hin aseiye, Zered galkai dingin cheuvin, ati banginigalkai tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Kadesh Burnea ihin dalhah kal-u kum somthum le get ahitan, Pasal galsat thei jouse gamthip la h a athisoh tauve. Hichu Pakaiyin atep banga thilsoh ahi. \x + \xo 2:14 \xt Minbu 14:28-35\x*  
\v 15 Pakaiyin asuhmanghel kahseuvin, amaho chu adou in ahi.  
\v 16 Galbol thei pasal jouse athi gam phat chun,  
\v 17 Pakaiyin ka henga hiti hin aseiyin,  
\v 18 Tunia hi Ar mun'a pat Moab gamgi na galkai diu  
\v 19 Lot chilhah Ammon mite chenna nalut diu, hinlah amaho na suhgim lou diu gal jong nabol khum lou diu ahi. Hiche gam hi Ammon mite kapeh ahitan, agam hi nnag ho kapeh thei louding ahitai. \x + \xo 2:19 \xt Semtilbu 19:38\x*  
\v 20 (Hiche gam chu Rephaim mite gam'a ana kihe ahin, Ammon miten vang Zamzummim mite atiuve.  
\v 21 Amaho jong chu asang thei un chule athau ahat thei uvin Anakim mite tobang ahiuve. Hinlah Pakaiyin amaho chu asugamhel tauvin ahileh, chuin Ammon miten agam alo tauve.  
\v 22 Pakaiyin Seir mun'a Esau chilhah te dinga na-atoh bang banginabol in chule Hor mite asugam in ahileh hiche mun'a chun amaho acheng tauvin ahi. Hijeh chun Esau chilhah te tuni chan geiyin acheng tauvin ahi.  
\v 23 Hiche tobang hin Crete apat Caphtorit mite chunga thilsoh ana lhungin, Avvit mite chu anasu-gam hel uvin, Gaza khopi chan alo tauve.)  
\v 24 Mose’n avelin aseiyin, ‘Pakaiyin hiti hin aseiye, tun Arnon Gorge mun galkai dingin che tauvin! Vetan, Sihon, Amorite Hesbon lengpa khu nakhut uva kapeh doh ding chule agam pumpi nangma na chan ding ahi. Nokhum unlang agam khu lo tauvin.  
\v 25 Tu nikhoa kipat gam Leiset a cheng mihemte chunga tijatna kalhun sah ding ahi. Nachung chang thu-u ahin jah doh tengu leh kichat nan alhun den diu ahi.   
\s1 Sihon asatnau  
\p
\v 26 Mose’n aseikit in, ‘Kadeshmoth gamthip apat Heshbon lengpa Sihon henga chamna thuseiyin palai khat kasol in:  
\v 27 Nagam sung ka jotpa diu ahi. Lampi jeng ka jotpa diu amavang, akimvel lah kahopa lou diu ahi.  
\v 28 Anneh ding le twidon ding neipe uvin, hichu aman kapeh diu ahi. Thil ijakai chung chona kangai chat pipen uchu ahileh nagam ka jotpa uva kagal kai diu hi ahi.  
\v 29 Seir mun'a Esau chilhah ten agam kajotpa uva ka galkai nadiu eiphal peh uvin, hiche tobang chun Ar mun'a cheng Moab mite jengin jong abol uvin ahi. Hijeh chun Pakai, Pathen'in eipeh nau gam Jordan vadung ka gal kaitheina diuvin na gamsung nei jotsah tauvin katiuve.  
\v 30 Hinlah Heshbon mun'a Sihon lengpan agamsung hopa ding chu anom tapoi, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in Sihon lengpa lungthim chu asutah in chuin Pakaiyin eiki thopi uvin ahileh galjona chu eipe tauve.  
\v 31 Chuin Pakaiyin hiti hin aseiyin, Vetan, Keiman tua kipat Sihon lengpa leh agam leiset na khut uva kapeh doh pan ahitai. Tun kipan uvin agam pumpi lo dingin kon tauvin, ati.  
\v 32 Chuin Sihon lenpan eiho chunga gal bol dingin kho lhang asam tan, Jahaz apat agalsat miho henga hetsahna aneiyin ahi.  
\v 33 Ahinlah Pakai, Pathen'in eiho khut a apedoh tan ahileh, achapa te chule amite jouse jaonan i-satgam hel tauvin gal jona i-chang tauvin ahi.  
\v 34 Akhopi jouse leh amite jouse abonchan ithat gam hel tauvin, hichu pasal jouse leh numei chapang jaona ahi. Mihem khat a khat cha jeng jong asohcha tapon ahi.  
\v 35 Khopi sunga gancha jouse abonchan ichom tauvin chule thil ijakai manlu jouse jong i-chang tauvin ahi.  
\v 36 Pakai, Pathen'in ei-panpi uvin ahileh Aroer kiti Arnon Gorge, Gorge khopi chule agam pumpi Gilead chan geiyin abonchan ijousoh hel tauvin ahi.  
\v 37 Ijeh inem itileh, Ammon mite gam dalhan Jabbok vadung chule gamsunga khopi ho, Pakai thupeh bang banga i-dalhah jal’u ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Og asatnau  
\p
\v 1 Chuban in Bashan lamjon in ikitol uvin, hiche Edrei mun'a chun Og lengpa le agalsat mihon eino khum uvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hinlah Pakaiyin ka henga aseiyin, ‘Kicha hih un, ajeh chu keiman Og lengpa le agalsat ho abonchauva na khut uva kapeh doh ding, chule agam jouse jong kapeh ding nahiuve. Hesbon gamvaipo Amor mite Sihon lengpa nabolnabang bang uvin bol'un, ati.  
\v 3 Chuin Pakai, Pathen'in Og lengpa le amite abonchan eiho khut a apedoh in, amaho chu ithatgam keiyuvin ahi. Mihem khatcha jeng jong aki hinghoi tapoi.  
\v 4 Alal-na khopi somgup ijousohkei tauvin, hichu Argob gamkai Bashan lenggam pumpi ahi. Khopi khat jeng cha jong asohcha tapoi.  
\v 5 Hiche khopi ho jouse chu akimvel aboncha pal phatah a kigen le kelkot phatah a kisem sohkei ahi. Chule kho phabep akimvela pal kigen lou jong ilo tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Hesbon lengpa Sihon isuhgam bang uvin, Bashan lenggam pumpi jong abonchan ijousoh hel tauvin ahi. Khopi tin’a mihem jouse ithat soheki uvin numei chapang jaona pasal jouse ahi.  
\v 7 Khopi jousea gancha ho ihinghoi uvin, thil ijakai manlu jouse jong ichom tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Amor mite lengpa lalna gam lhumlam Jordan vadung jong ilo’uvin, hichu Arnon Gorge apat Hermon molsang chan gei ahi.  
\v 9 (Sidon mite chun Hermon molsang chu Sirion tin akou un chule Amor miten Senir tin akou uve.)  
\v 10 Tun eihon Gilead le Bashan gamkai pumpi ijousoh tauvin, Og lengpa gamvai pohna Salecah le Edrei chan geiyin ijousoh hel tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 (Bashan lengpa Og chu Rephaim mite dinga leng nukhah pen ahitan. Alupna chu thih a kisem ahin, chule asan dan adung feet som le thum, availam letdan feet gup alhing in ahi. Hiche lengpa lim hi Ammon mite khopi Rabbah mun'a aum nalayin ahi.)   
\s1 Jordan solam kihom  
\p
\v 12 Hiche gam pumpi chu ilo tauvin ahileh, keiman Reuben le Gad insung adingin Aroer apat Arnon Gorge chan gei in chule Gilead gam kehkhat le khopi phabep jaonan kapedoh tan ahi.  
\v 13 Manasseh chilhah te dingin, Gilead gam kehkhat le Bashan gam pumpi Og lengpa lalna gam chu ka pedoh tan ahi. (Hiche hi Bashan gam Argob gamkai pumpi hi Rephaim tia kihe ahi).  
\v 14 Manasseh insunga lamkai amin Jair, ama hin Bashan, Argob gamkai pumpi ajousoh hel in, Geshur mite le Maacah mite gamgi chan gei ahi. Jair chun hiche gam chu ama min aputsah in, Jair khopi asah tan, tuni chan in Jair tin akihe jing na laiyin ahi.  
\v 15 Keiman Gilead chu Makir insung kapedoh tai.  
\v 16 Chule keiman Reuben le Gad insunga dingin Gilead gam phabep jong kapen ahi. Arnon Gorge lhanglam lailung apat Ammon mite chenna Jabbok vadung chan ahi.  
\v 17 Jordan phaicham Galilee dillen lhanglam San dung, apat Jordan vadung gamgi chan gei ahi. Hichu solam Pisgah toh kimat ahitai.   
\s1 Mose Jordan galkai loudinga hilchahna  
\p
\v 18 Hiche phatlai chun keiman ama insung cheh, lhumlam Jordan a cheng dingin thupeh ka neiyin ahi: Hiche gam pumpi hi Pakai, Pathen'in nangho napehsau hijongleh, na gal-miteuvin na sopi te ho chenna Jordan gam aho pauva galkai diu ahi. \x + \xo 3:18 \xt Joshua 1:12-15\x*  
\v 19 Chule najiteu, nachateu chule na gancha jouseu jaona keiman kapeh khopi hoa cheng diu ahi.  
\v 20 Pakaiyin Israel mite dinga kivenbitna gam napedoh tauvin, chuin ama hon Jordan vadung chan geiyin aching uvin, chuin nangho na boncha uvin Pakaiyin na pehnau gam achun nacheng khom tauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun keiman Joshua henga thupeh hicheng hi kaneiyin: Nanghon hiche leng teni chunga Pakai natoh abonchan namusoh tauvin. Pakaiyin lhumlam gamkai Jordan chengsea angaiya bang banga na atoh ding ahi.  
\v 22 Hijeh chun hiche nam mite khu kicha hih in, Pakaiyin nangma dinga gal asat ding ahi.   
\s1 Mose’n gam chotlut ding akham  
\p
\v 23 Chuin keima Pakai henga katao vin hiti hin kaseiye. \x + \xo 3:23 \xt Minbu 27:12-14; Danbu Ni Na 32:48-52\x*  
\v 24 O Thanei chungnung Pakai, nangman keima nasohpa henga naban thahat naki lahsah in ka musoh tai. Koiham pathen dang van leh leiset a hitobang thil kidang bol thei ding?  
\v 25 Nalung ahileh, Jordan hi nei galkai sah inlang, gamhoi tah Lebanon molsang ho nei musah tan, ati.  
\v 26 Hinlah nangho jeh in Pakai ka henga alungphamo tan, ka taona angaisah tapoi. Chuin aman aseiyin, aphatai! Imadang seibe datan, ati.  
\v 27 Pisgah molchunga kaltouvin lang, gam jouse gavetan, amavang Jordan vadung na galkai louding ahi.  
\v 28 Nangma khel in, Joshua thaneina pen lang hilchah jotan, ajeh chu Joshua in mipi aboncha Jordan chan agalkai pia, alam kai ding ahi. Masanga namu gam jouse aboncha aman mipi apeh ding ahi.  
\v 29 Chuin Beth-peor kiti mun'a chun kaum tauvin ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Mose’n thu angai nadiuva ahilchahna  
\p
\v 1 Tun, Israel miten danthu kahil jouseu phatah in ngaiyun, Pakai, Pathen'in napu, napa teu khanga pat napehnau gam nalhun theina diu le agama nachen theina diu ahi.  
\v 2 Ka thupeh a kon'in ngaisah louna ima neihih hel uvin. Pakai, Pathen a konna ka thupeh chengse hi phatah a najui diu ahi. \x + \xo 4:2 \xt Rev 22:18,19\x*  
\v 3 Baapeor mun'a Pakaiyin nangho dinga ichan geiya na atoh namusohkeiyun ahi. Hiche mun'a chun Pakai, Pathen'in Baal doi hou jouse abonchan asugam sohkeiye. \x + \xo 4:3 \xt Minbu 25:1-9\x*  
\v 4 Hinlah Pakai, Pathen tahsan a thua nung jouse, tuni chan in na boncha uvin nadam nalaiyun ahi.  
\v 5 Vetan, Pakai, Pathen a konna jui ding dan hichengse hi nangho dinga thupeh ahi. Ajeh chu hichengse hi gamsung nalut tengu leh phatah a najui kimsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 6 Hichengse hi najui uva ahileh, na kimvel uva cheng nam dangte sanga athem leh achinga naum diu ahi. Hitobang nunle khan ahin jahdoh tengu leh, hiche nam mite hi datmah umtah in aching lheh uve tia asei diu ahi!  
\v 7 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen ikom cha uva aum jing banga, eiho Pathen tobang nam dang ten anei khah ngai em?  
\v 8 Hitobanga chu keiman jong na masang uva ka koipeh danthu hijatpi hi, kicheh tah’a ka koipeh bang uva koi dang nam in hitobang anei khah ngai em?  
\v 9 Ijeh inem itileh vetan! Nanghon namit tah uva namu chan uchu nahaimil lou diu ahi. Hiche hi na damsung uva nalungthim uva konna na jamdoh sah lou diu ahi! Natu na chate chan geiya achin jing diu ahi.  
\v 10 Chule Pakai, Pathen'in Sinai mol chunga adin nikhoa ka henga thu asei chu na haimil lou diu ahi. Mipi ho abonchan ka henga hinpuiyin, keiman ijakai kahil diu ahi. Chutileh ama hon keima gin ding dan ahet uva, atu acha khang gei uva jong keima eigin jing diu ahi.  
\v 11 Nangma mol chunga na keng in nahung dingin, Molchung vum jouse meibol in atom in chuin mu athim lhatan ahi. \x + \xo 4:11 \xt Potdohbu 19:16-18; Heb 12:18,19\x*  
\v 12 Chuin Pakaiyin nangma henga thu aseiyin, meikong in akilah in, Ama awgin chu najan ahinlah tahmel in namupoi; ajeh chu awgin bou najah ahi.  
\v 13 Pakaiyin kitepna asemin, Thupeh som nanit jing diuvin thupeh aneiyin, songpheng ni chunga ajihdoh in ahi. \x + \xo 4:13 \xt Potdohbu 31:18; 34:28; Danbu Ni Na 9:10\x*  
\v 14 Hiche mun'a chun Pakaiyin thupeh aneiyin, nangho gamsung nalut kon tengu leh danthu najui diuvin abonchan eihil in ahi. \x + \xo 4:14 \xt Potdohbu 21:1\x*   
\s1 Milim doi thudol'a gihna  
\p
\v 15 Hijeh chun nangho ching theiyun! Sinai mol chunga Pakaiyin najah uva thu asei nikho chun, nang hon tahmel in namu pouve.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun nang hon milim doi numei leh pasal lima semthu a-angsunga na bokhup uva na kisuhboh louhel diu, \x + \xo 4:16 \xt Potdohbu 20:4; Thempu Dan 26:1; Danbu Ni Na 5:8; 27:15\x*  
\v 17 gancha hihen chung leng vacha hijongleh, \x + \xo 4:17 \xt Rm 1:23\x*  
\v 18 tol-lhang lah a ganhing hihen, twipi noiya um ganhing limsem thu kitiphot angsunga na bohkhup lou diu ahi.  
\v 19 Chunglang vea lha, ahsite chule vanthamjola thil ho jong bohkhup a akin bol ding na ngaito louhel diu ahi. Hichengse khu aboncha Pakai, Pathen'in leiset a cheng mihemte apeh ahi.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu nangho hi Pakai, Pathen'in Egypt gamsung meilhum lah a kiloidoh a Pathen dei tum mong mong dinga tunia hi nasemu ahin, hichu nasuhmil lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 4:20 \xt Potdohbu 19:5; Danbu Ni Na 7:6; 14:2; 26:18; Tit 2:14; 1 Pet 2:9\x*  
\v 21 Hinlah nangho jeh in Pakai ka henga alungphamo tan. Pakaiyin kitepna asemin keima Jordan vadung galkaiya, keima hiche gamsunga khu kalut thei louding ahitai. \x + \xo 4:21 \xt Minbu 20:12\x*  
\v 22 Keima khela hiche gamsung lodinga Jordan vadung nagal kai diu ahi. Keima vang hiche solam vadung pama hi thiden ding kahitai.  
\v 23 Hijeh chun chingthei un Pakai, Pathen'in kitepna napeh hou aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi. Pathen doumah milim doi sem ding gohih un, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen dinga doumah umtah ahi.  
\v 24 Pakai, Pathen hi meikong a kilahji ahin; thangtomna aneiji ahi. \x + \xo 4:24 \xt Heb 12:29\x*  
\v 25 Ahunglhung ding phat hoa, tu le cha nahin neiyuva gamsunga na hung chen tengu leh, milim doi kiti sema a-angsunga na bohkhup louhel diu ahi. Hitobang thil hi Pakai dinga thet umtah leh Pakai lunghanna ahi.  
\v 26 Tuna van leh leiset kasan hi nangho hettohsahna ding ahi. Ka kitepna na suhkeh uva ahileh, Jordan vadung galkaiya gamsunga na hetman lou uva na manthah jeng diu ahi. Hinkho chomcha bou nanei diu; hetman louva thinan na lhunden diu ahi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu nam dangte lah a Pakaiyin nathe cheh diu, lhom cha bouvin gamsung nalo diu ahi. \x + \xo 4:27 \xt Danbu Ni Na 28:36\x*  
\v 28 Hiche mun'a chu, gamdang mite lah a milim doi song le thinga kisem thu, ima jathei lou, muthei lou ho kin nabol diu ahi.  
\v 29 Chuteng Pakai, Pathen nahin hol kit diu, nalungthim pumpiuva nahin hol tengu leh namu bep diu ahi. \x + \xo 4:29 \xt Jeremiah 29:13\x*  
\v 30 Ahunglhung ding phat hoa, hitobang din mun'a naum uva gim genthei nan nalhun den tengu leh, Pakai, Pathen angsung nahin bel diu, Pakai thusei jouse nangai diu ahi.  
\v 31 Ajeh chu na Pakaiyu, Pathen uhi ngailutna a dim jeng ahin; na lung na heija Pakai lam nahin bel teng aman na damsah ding ahi. Ijeh inem itileh, napu napa teu khang apat akitepna ageldoh jingin ahi.   
\s1 Pathen khat seh ahi  
\p
\v 32 Tun leiset ahung kisem apat tuchana Pathen'in ichan geiya mihemte akhohsah ham, ti thusimle vanthamjola ijakai jouse kholdoh uvin. Hitobang thil ki dang ho hi najah a namu khah uvem?  
\v 33 Nanghon meikonga Pathen akilah a, awgin najah bang uva nam dang ten hitobang thil kidang atokhah tah uvem?  
\v 34 Pathen dang in nampi khat gim hesoh na a kon apui doh a, thil kidang ijakai aki lahsah gal asat peh, ban thahat pana kithopina, ki dang tah a na-atohna um kha tam? Ahinlah nangho Pakai, Pathen'in Egypt gam naum lai uva anatoh ijakai na musohkei tauvin ahi.  
\v 35 Pakaiyin ijakai na muchen sah tauve, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen tobang dang umlou ahi. \x + \xo 4:35 \xt Mk 12:32\x*  
\v 36 Pakaiyin van'a kon'in awgin na jahsah uvin, thupeh ijakai aneiyin ahi. Pakai meikonga akilah in nangho nahou piu vin ahi.  
\v 37 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin napu napa teu angailun chule a chilhah te chan gei phatthei aboh ahi. Pakaiyin abanthahat apan in, Egypt gam'a konna nahin pui galkaiyu ahitai.  
\v 38 Nangho dingin namdang te gamla tah in achon doh in, Pakaiyin nangho chenna ding gamnom tah na peuvin, tunin na cheng tauvin ahi.  
\v 39 Hijeh achu hiche hi na geldoh jing diu leh na lungthim uva na chin jing diu ahi: Pakai, Pathen hi van'a jong leiset a jong Pathen ahin, Pathen dang ama tobang aumpoi.  
\v 40 Tunia ka thupeh chengse aboncha na juikim sohkeiyuva ahileh, ijakai phacham kimsohkei ding nachateu chan geiya phatthei chang diu ahi. Imatih chana gamsunga kipah leh lungmonga nachen diu, na hinkhou asotna dinga Keiman thupeh hichengse aboncha kapeh nahiuve.   
\s1 Bitna khopi ho  
\p
\v 41 Chuin Mose’n khopi thum solam Jordan vadunga kichol nadingin atung doh in ahi. \x + \xo 4:41 \xt Joshua 20:8,9\x*  
\v 42 Koi tobangin mihem khat alam louva atha a, suhna ding beiya auma ahileh, ama chu hiche mun'a hi jamlut ding ahinkho aki huhdoh ding ahi.  
\v 43 Khopi thum ho chu: Bezer kiti gamthip lah a hichu Reuben in sunga ding; Ramoth kiti Gilead mun'a hichu Gad in sunga ding; Golan kiti Bashan mun'a hichu Manasseh insunga ding ahi.   
\s1 Pathen danthua kihilna  
\p
\v 44 Thupeh hichengse hi Mose’n Israel mite henga aseipeh ahi.  
\v 45 Hichengse hi danthu jui ding’a Mose’n Israel miten Egypt gam adalhah uva apeh,  
\v 46 Beth-peor toh kinai solam Jordan vadung phaicham ngahmun aum laiyuva apeh ahi. Phat masa chun hiche gam hi Amor mite lengpa Sihon in Hesbon mun'a konna ana vaipoh ahi. Hinlah Egypt gam'a konna Mose leh Israel mite ahung doh uchun ana sugam hel tauvin ahi.  
\v 47 Chuin Israel miten Bashan lengpa Og lalna gam leh anei agou jouse achom chai keiyuvin, solama Amor mite leng teni jaona ahi.  
\v 48 Israel miten Aroer apat Arnon Gorge chule Sirion mol Hermon tiajong kihe chan geiyin ajousoh hel tauve.  
\v 49 Chuin ama hon solam gamkai Jordan vadung pang leh, lhanglam San dung chan geiyin ajousoh uvin, Pisgah noilam chan gei ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Thupeh som ho  
\p
\v 1 Mose’n Israel mite akoukhom in aheng uva aseipeh tan ahi, Israel miten phatah in ngaiyun. Tunin Dan thupeh chengse hi jasohkeiyun, kihilnan neiyun lang najui kimsohkei diu ahi!  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen'in Sinai mola kitepna eisem peh tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Pakaiyin hiche kitepna hi ipu-ipateu toh asem ahipon, amavang tunikhoa eiho jouse dinga asem ahi.  
\v 4 Pakai mol chunga meikong in akilah in nangho kimaiton nakihou limpiuvin ahi.  
\v 5 Nangho leh Pakai kimlaiya keima ka dingin ahi, ajeh chu nang hon meikong nakicha uvin molchung na nailut ngam tapouve. Pakaiyin ka henga thu aseiyin, athusei doh aboncha nangho kapeh son ahi. Pakai thuseidoh chu hiche hi ahi:  
\v 6 Keima na Pakai leh na Pathen kahi, Egypt gam'a soh a naum laiyuva na huhdoh pau chu kahi.  
\v 7 Kei tailou Pathen dang nanei loudiu ahi.  
\v 8 Milimsemthu kiti nanei thei lou diu, van le leiset chule twikhanglen sunga hijongleh pathen limsemthu nanei thei lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:8 \xt Thempu Dan 26:1; Danbu Ni Na 4:15-18; 27:15\x*  
\v 9 Hitobang limsemthu ho angsunga chu naboh khup uva, akin nabol louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu keima na Pakaiyu leh na Pathen u-kahin, pathen dang semthua konna thang-tomji ka hin, hiche chonset nachu nacha teu khang geiya pap kalhunsah ding; keima ei pam pai insung pumpi chunga, khangthum leh li chan geiya lethuhna ka lhunsah ding ahi. \x + \xo 5:9 \xt Potdohbu 34:6,7; Minbu 14:18; Danbu Ni Na 7:9,10\x*  
\v 10 Hinlah ka thupeh nit a keima eingailu jing ho chunga, akhang akhanga ngailutna kalhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 11 Pakai, Pathen min nasuhboh louhel diu ahi. Koi hileh Pakai min suboh chan chu ngaidam chang louding ahi. \x + \xo 5:11 \xt Thempu Dan 19:12\x*  
\v 12 Pakai, Pathen thupeh banga, Sabbath nikho theng chu nanit jing diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:12 \xt Potdohbu 16:23-30; 31:12-14\x*  
\v 13 Natohna ding nigup naneiyun ahi, \x + \xo 5:13 \xt Potdohbu 23:12; 31:15; 34:21; 35:2; Thempu Dan 23:3\x*  
\v 14 hinlah nisagi lhinni Sabbath nikho hi Pakai, Pathen dinga nikho theng ki todoh ahi. Hiche nikhoa hi koima chan insung natoh abol theilou ding, hiche hi nangho nahiuvin, nachapa teu le nachanuteu, nasoh pasal ho le nasoh numei hou, bongchal ho leh, sa-ngan ho chule nagancha jouse jaona, chule gamdangmi nalah uva hung cheng ho jaona hi ding ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche hi nasuhmil lou diu ahi, khatvei chu Egypt gamsunga soh a um nahiuvin, hinlah Pakai, Pathen'in abanthahat pana nahin puidoh u ahi. Hiche jeh achu Pakai, Pathen'in Sabbath nikhoa ki chol dinga thupeh anei ahi.  
\v 16 Pakai, Pathen thupeh banginnanu, napa jabol un. Chutileh nahinkhou sot ding Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsunga lung monga nachen diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:16 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:16; Matt 15:4; 19:19; Mk 7:10; 10:19; Lk 18:20; Eph 6:2; \xt Eph 6:3\x*  
\v 17 Toltha nabol lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:17 \xt Semtilbu 9:6; Thempu Dan 24:17; Matt 5:21; 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9; Jac 2:11\x*  
\v 18 Jonthanhoi nabol lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:18 \xt Thempu Dan 20:10; Matt 5:27; 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9; Jac 2:11\x*  
\v 19 Gu chat nabol lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:19 \xt Thempu Dan 19:11; Matt 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9\x*  
\v 20 Na sopi nalhep chatvai lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:20 \xt Potdohbu 23:1; Matt 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20\x*  
\v 21 Na sopi jitoh nalupkhom lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 5:21 \xt Rm 7:7; 13:9\x*  
\p Chule nasopi gam jong nachu lou diu, asoh numei hihen pasal hijongleh, abongchal hihen, asangante hijongleh nasopi nei le gou, ijakai lepthola nalah thei lou diu ahi.   
\p
\v 22 Hichengse hi molchunga nakal laiyuva Pakaiyin aseidohsa ahitai. Pakai chu meikong in akilah in aw-sang tah in asam in, chuin meibol le muthim in atomlha jengin ahi. Hiche laimun'a chu aboncha aseiya chule hichengse chu aboncha songpheng nia ajihlut a keima eipeh ahi. \x + \xo 5:22 \xt Heb 12:18,19\x*   
\s1 Pathen hung kilahna mipin akichat  
\p
\v 23 Nanghon awgin le mu-athime ti najauvin chule molchung pumpi athimlha jeng tan ahileh, na insung cheh uva koin lamkaiho le upaho ka henga ahung uvin ahi.  
\v 24 ama hon hiti hin aseiyuve, vetan! I-Pakaiyu le i-Pathen uvin aloupina ki dangtah in eimusah uvin aw-sangtah meikonga kilah chu kaja uvin, tunin kamu tauve. Ajeh chu Pathen'in mihemte henga thu aseiyin, hinlah ima kati deh pouvin ahi.  
\v 25 Tunvang ipi dinga thi ikichat kit diu ham? Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in iheng uva thu asei kit a ahileh, thinan ilhun den uva meikonga iki govam jeng theiyu ahi.  
\v 26 Haina hu neiya hing itobang hijongleh, eiho banga hingjing Pathen awgin ja'a thi louva hing thei aum dem?  
\v 27 Tun nangho cheuvin lang Pakai, Pathen'in ipi asei em gangai tauvin. Chule hung kile kit unlang Pakaiyin ipi asei em ti kaheng uva hung seiyun, chuteng keihon kangai uva kajui diu ahi.  
\v 28 Keima henga nangeh chan’u Pakaiyin ajasoh tan ahi. Pakaiyin hiti hin aseiye, mipi hon nangma henga ipi asei uvem ti keiman ka hesohkeiyin, chule ama hon thudih aseiyu ahi.  
\v 29 Oh, hitia hi ama hon lung ngaichatna anei jing diu chule hiche bang achu ama hon keima eigin jing diu, ka thupeh jong anit jing diu ahi! Hitia chu achon jing uva ahileh, amaho leh achilhah teu chan geiya phatthei chang diu ahi.  
\v 30 Nangma chen lang aheng uva gasei tan, “Na ponbuh cheh uva kile tauvin.”  
\v 31 Hinlah nangma hiche mun'a hin ding den nalaiyin chonna dan thupeh aboncha ka seipeh ding nahi. Chule hichengse hi aboncha mipi ho henga naseipeh ding chutileh ama hon achen nau gamsunga chu ajui jing diu ahi.  
\v 32 Chuin Mose’n mipi ho henga aseiyin, nang hon chingthei tah in Pakai, Pathen thupeh aboncha jui ding go uvin.  
\v 33 Pakai, Pathen'in nathupeh nau lampi chu jui jing uvin. Chutileh nalhun nadiu gamsunga hinkho sot tah nachen thei diu ahi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Thupeh thupipen  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, Pathen'in nangho seipeh dinga danthu eipeh hichengse hi ahi. Hiche gamsung nalut tengu leh, najui kimsohkei diu ahi,  
\v 2 chutileh nadam sung uva natu nachateu khang geiya keima eigin jing diu ahi. Pakai thupeh aboncha nanit sohkeiyuva ahileh, lungmonga naum diu chule nahinkhou jong sot ding ahi.  
\v 3 Phatah in ngaiyun, Israel, ajeh chu hichengse hi najui kimsel diu ahi. Chutileh ijakai phacham kimsohkei ding, napu napa teu khanga pat Pakai, Pathen kitepna banga khoiju le bongnoi lonna gam'a chu nachen diu ahi.  
\v 4 O Israel ngaiyun! Pakai hi i-Pathen’u ahi, chule Pakai ama bou ahi. \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Mk 12:29\x*  
\v 5 Hijeh chun Pakai le na Pathen'u nalungthim pumpiu le natha neisun in ngailu uvin. \x + \xo 6:5 \xt Matt 22:37; Mk 12:30; Lk 10:27\x*  
\v 6 Tunia ka thupeh chengse aboncha chunga kipehna nanei uva najui kimsohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 6:6 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:18-20\x*  
\v 7 Hichengse hi nachateu henga avel vel'a naseipeh diu ahi. In mun'a naumpet'u hihen, lam najot pet'u hihen, nalup konu hihen, nakithodoh pet'u hijongleh, aheng uva naseipeh jing diu ahi.  
\v 8 Hichengse chu na khut’uva kikhi jingun lang chule nachalpang uva jong nakhi chah jing diu, hitia chu na suhmil lou diu ahi.  
\v 9 Na in kot phung uva jong jih unlang chule kelkot mai ajong najih sohkei diu ahi.   
\s1 Thungailou jeh a boina  
\p
\v 10 Ajeh chu na Pakaiyu, na Pathen uvin napu na pateu Abraham, Isaac le Jacob henga akitepna gamsunga napuilut vah diu ahitai. Hiche khopi hoa hi ijakai bukimsel, hichu nang hon man beiya namu diu ahi. \x + \xo 6:10 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; \xt Semtilbu 26:3; \xt Semtilbu 28:13\x*  
\v 11 Insung hoa chu neileh gou ijakai aki lamsa hi ding ahi. Twikul ho jong aki laisa ahin, Olive thing phung le adang hoa konna jong aga naneh diu, hiche ho jouse hi nang hon tu louhel a aga nalo diu ahi. Hiche ho hi naneh tengu leh gamsung pumpi nalodim diu ahitai.  
\v 12 Chuleh chingthei un Pakai, na Pathen'u nasuh mil lou diu ahi, ajeh chu Egypt gam'a soh a naum laiyuva Pakaiyin na huhdoh’u ahi.  
\v 13 Nanghon Pakai, na Pathen'u nagin diu chule Pakai kin jenga na kisah lel diu ahi. Ki hahselna nanei ujongleh Pakai min pana nakihahsel diu ahi. \x + \xo 6:13 \xt Matt 4:10; Lk 4:8\x*  
\v 14 Na kimvel uva nam dangte pathen semthu angsunga naboh khup lou diu ahi.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen hi thangtom thei ahi. Pakai lunghanna chun leiset chunga konna natol mang jeng theiyu ahi.  
\v 16 Nanghon Massah mun'a Pakai, Pathen napatep bang uva avel'a napatep kitlou diu ahi. \x + \xo 6:16 \xt Matt 4:7; Lk 4:12; \xt Potdohbu 17:1-7\x*  
\v 17 Nanghon Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh phatah a nanit jing diu, Dan jouse najui kim sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 18 Pathen mitmua apha jeng bol ding go uvin, chutileh ijakai pha chamkim sohkei ding ahi. Chuteng Pakaiyin napu napa teu khanga pat’a kitepna gamsunga nachen diu ahi.  
\v 19 Pakaiyin asei bangin, hiche gamsunga nagal miteu aboncha Pakaiyin asuhmang hel ding ahi.  
\v 20 Khonung le nachateu vin hitia hi ahin sei diu, hiche dan le thupeh jui ding ho hi ipi jeh a Pakai, Pathen'in napeh ham? tia nahin doh diu ahi.  
\v 21 Chuteng nang hon hitia hi na donbut diu, keiho Egypt gamsunga Pharaoh angsunga soh a kana um laiyuva Pakai, Pathen'in abanthahat a eihin huhdoh'u ahi.  
\v 22 Pakaiyin Egypt gamsunga Pharaoh le amite henga thil kidang ijakai aki lahsah in, ipu ipateu khanga pat akitepna gamsunga cheng dia eihin puiyu ahi.  
\v 23 Pakaiyin Egypt gamsunga konna eihin puigal kaiyu ahin, ajeh chu eihon hiche gam ilo theina diu ahi.  
\v 24 Hijeh achu Pakai, Pathen'in hiche dan thupeh jui ding jouse hi eipeh uva, hichengse ijui kimsohkei uva ahileh ihinkhou sot ding chule imatih chana phatthei ichan diu ahi. Hichu tuni chan geiya idamnau ahi.  
\v 25 Pakai, Pathen a konna dan le thupeh aboncha ijui uva ahileh Pakaiyin eiho jouse them changa eisim diu ahi.   
\c 7  
\s1 Pathen nam lhen  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, na Pathen uvin gamsunga nahin puilut tengu leh, nam dang tampi umho khu asuhmang ding ahi: Hit mite, Girgash mite, Amor mite, Canaan mite, Periz mite, Hiv mite le Jebus mite ahi. Hiche nam sagi ho hi nangho sanga hatjo le pungjo ahiuve. \x + \xo 7:1 \xt Act 13:19\x*  
\v 2 Pakaiyin akhut a konna nangho nahin pehdoh tengu leh, nang hon abonchauva nasuh gamsohkeidiu ahi. Amaho toh ki chamna ima semlouva abonchauva natha gam diu ahi.  
\v 3 Chule amaho toh chun na kichen thei lou diu ahi. Na chanuteu le nachapa te hou chu amaho chanute le chapa te toh nakichen sah louhel diu ahi.  
\v 4 Ajeh chu ama hon na chateu apui mang diu, semthu pathen angsunga abohkhup sah diu ahi. Chuteng Pakai lunghanna nachung uva hung chu jeng ding, chomlou kah a na manthah lo diu ahi.  
\v 5 Hitia hi nabol teidiu ahi, amaicham phung hou le akhom ho aboncha naphuh lhuh peh diu ahi. Chule Asherah ho jong naphuh lhuh diu aboncha meiya nahalvam diu ahi. \x + \xo 7:5 \xt Danbu Ni Na 12:3\x*  
\v 6 Ajeh chu nangho Pakai, Pathen'in vannoi mite lah atumbeh a na lhen’u ahin, chule nangho amagou nahi tauvin, Pakai dinga mitheng te nahi tauve. \x + \xo 7:6 \xt Potdohbu 19:5; Danbu Ni Na 4:20; 14:2; 26:18; Tit 2:14; 1 Pet 2:9\x*  
\v 7 Pakaiyin namdang te banga thalhing le hatjo nahijeh uva nalhen tumu hilouvin, amavang nam neopen nahijeh uva nalhen joh’u ahi!  
\v 8 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin akitepna ageldoh jingin, nachung uva ngailutna anei jingin ahi. Hijeh achu Pakaiyin athahat pana Egypt gam Pharaoh akon suhgimna nachan nauva konna nahuhdoh’u ahi.  
\v 9 Hijeh chun hethem un Pakai, Pathen hi nangho Pathen dihtah mong ahi. Pakai ngailua athupeh nit jing mite chunga, akhang akhanga akitepna akoi jingin ngailutna jong anei jingin ahi. \x + \xo 7:9 \xt Potdohbu 20:5,6; 34:6,7; Minbu 14:18; Danbu Ni Na 5:9,10\x*  
\v 10 Hinlah Pakai nasah louva umho chunga gim genthei alhunsah in asumang jin ahi.  
\v 11 Hijeh chun tunia thupeh kapeh chengse hi aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi.   
\s1 Pathen dei chu ipi ham  
\p
\v 12 Dan le thupeh aboncha najui kimsohkeiyuva ahileh Pakai, Pathen'in na chung uva alungsetna longlou chu akoi jing ding ahi. Ajeh chu napu napa teu khanga pet akitepna ahi. \x + \xo 7:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:13-17\x*  
\v 13 Pakaiyin phattheina leh Ami ngailutna chun naumpi jing diu chule cha jong tampi nahin diu ahi. Pakaiyin gampha tah gaphaso nading leh naganchateu kivahna ding napeh diu, napu napa teu khanga peh dinga akitepna gam nalhun tengu leh louga phatah nachom khom diu, lengpi thah leh Olive thao chule bonghon tampi leh kelngoi hon tampi jaona nanei diu ahi.  
\v 14 Chutengleh Vannoiya nam dangte jouse sanga phatthei nachan diu ahi. Numei, pasal hihen nagancha teu hijongleh cha nei louva khatcha naum lou diu ahi.  
\v 15 Chule dammo veisetna a konna Pakaiyin navenbit jing diu ahi. Egypt gam'a gim genthei nathoh bang uva nathoh sah lou diu, na doumah jouseu aboncha asuhmang ding ahi.  
\v 16 Pakai, Pathen'in nam dangte nakhut a apehdoh chengse aboncha nasuh gam diu ahi. Ngailutna beiya nabol diu chule amaho pathen angsunga nabohkhup louhel diu ahi.  
\v 17 Amavang nang hon hitia hi nasei diu, hiche nam mite hi eiho sang'in ahat jouvin, iti iki doupi thei diu ham?  
\v 18 Hinlah nakichat thei lou diu ahi! Ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin Egypt gam Pharaoh henga ichan geiya na atoh ham ti nageldoh diu ahi.  
\v 19 Pakai, na Pathen uvin amaho chunga tijat umtah’a na atoh geldoh jingun, hichu nangho mitmu tah a thilsoh ahi! Chule thil ki dang ijakai akilahsah ho geldoh jing uvin, abanthahat pana anatoh thil kidang hoa konna Egypt gam'a pet nahin puiyu chu na suhmil lou diu ahi. Hiche banga chu Pakai, Pathen'in tua nagal miteu chunga na atoh ding ahi.  
\v 20 Pakai, na Pathen uvin tijatna phabep namasang lam uva ahin koi ding, chuteng ijakai atol mang soh ding ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche nam mite chunga chu kichatna nanei louhel diu ahi, ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin na umpi jing uve, Pathen thilbol thei kidang ahi.  
\v 22 Pakai, na Pathen uvin hiche nam mite ho hi aloi loiya asuhmang ding ahi. Khatvei pansa na suhmang jeng thei lou diu ahi. Achuti louva ahile gamsate hung dimlha jeng ding ahi.  
\v 23 Hinlah Pakai, na Pathen uvin abonchauva nangho khut a apeh doh ding ahi. Amaho abei kahseuva Pakaiyin asuhnoh phah diu ahi.  
\v 24 Pakaiyin alengte hou nangho khut a apehdoh ding, chuteng nang hon leiset a amin hou na suhmang diu ahi.  
\v 25 Chule amilim doi semthu hou aboncha nahalvam peh diu, milim doi tomna ki mang sum-eng hijongleh khat jeng cha na kilah thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 26 Na insung'u suboh thei ima nanei thei lou diu ahi, ajeh chu amaho kibolna banga nangho jong thina nachan diu ahi. Hitobang thil hoa konna gamna kipan ding chule na kidalse jing diu ahi.   
\c 8  
\s1 Pathen sumil hih un  
\p
\v 1 Tunia ka thupeh chengse hi chingthei tah in jui bukim sohkeiyuvin. Chutileh nahinkhou sot intin, Pakaiyin napu napate khanga pat peh dinga akitepna gam nalo thei diu ahi.  
\v 2 Pakai, na Pathen uvin kum somli gamthip lah a konna nahin puidohna geldoh jingun, ajeh chu Pakai thupeh ijakai nanit kimsoh nadiuva nangho patepna ahi.  
\v 3 Henge, Pakaiyin gilkiela naum laipet tah uvin mana napiuvin ahi. Hiche tobang an-hi napu, napa teu khanga jong um khalou ahi. Ajeh chu mihemte hi changlhah jengseh a hing jou ahipoi ti, Pakaiyin nahetsah nau ahin; amavang Pakai kam sunga konna hung potdoh thu changa bou hinga nahiuve. \x + \xo 8:3 \xt Matt 4:4; Lk 4:4\x*  
\v 4 Kum somli sung in von-ah ding jong nangaicha pouvin chule nakeng ujong imacha atipon ahi.  
\v 5 Hichu geltem uvin: Minu mipan acha ahilna banga, Pakaiyin nangho phatchomna dinga bou nakhoukhah nau ahi.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh chengse abonchan nit kimsohkeiyun lang, Pakai ging jinga hinkho naman diu ahi.  
\v 7 Ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin na gamu phatah twi nenna mun'a nahin puiyuva, hichu phaicham leh thing lhang gam aboncha ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche gam pumpi hi mimchang le kolbu lei jeng ahin; theiba phung, kolbu thei phung, Olive phung leh khoiju lonna gam ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche gamsung hi Pakaiyin ijakai kimsela twi achap nou ahin, chule agamsunga thih jong song banga kimang ahin, thinglhang gam songmantam jeng uma ahi.  
\v 10 Agamsungga naneh tengu leh Pakai, na Pathen'u thangvahna napeh jing diu ahi.   
\s1 Kiletsah jeh a gihsalna  
\p
\v 11 Hinlah chingthei tah in um uvin! Ajeh chu hiche gampha laitah jeh a chu tunikhoa Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh nasuh millou diu ahi. \x + \xo 8:11 \xt Hosea 13:5,6\x*  
\v 12 Nanghon innom nahin kisah doh diu chule haosatah a nain chen diu,  
\v 13 chule nagan chateu jong hung pung cheh cheh ding, sana leh dangka ijakai kimsela nahin neidiu chuteng chingthei tah naum diu ahi.  
\v 14 Chutengleh kiletsah hoithona imacha naneilou diu ahi. Ajeh chu Egypt gamsunga gim genthei nathoh lai uva Pakai, Pathen'in nahuhdoh’u ahi.  
\v 15 Pakaiyin gamthip noiya aipi hang leh gulse holah a nahin puidoh nau nagel doh jing diu, hiche mun chu tolgo lah le gamsa mun ahin, hinlah Pakaiyin twi nape uvin ahi.  
\v 16 Pakaiyin gamthip noiya manna in navah vaset uvin, hichu napu napa teu khanga um khalou anneh ahi. Hiche hi Pakaiyin nangho patepna dinga abol ahin athua nanun cheh diu ahi.  
\v 17 Hiche ho jouse Pakaiyin nangho dinga na atoh ahin, keima hatna a ka kilamdoh ahitia ima nasei louhel diu ahi.  
\v 18 Pakai, na Pathen'u na geldoh jing diu ahi. Pakai bouvin nangho lolhin theina dinga tha napeh’u ahi, ajeh chu napu, napa teu khanga pat kitepna gui lhunsah nading ahi.  
\v 19 Hiche hi nahet jing diuva ka thupeh ahi: Pakai, na Pathen'u sumila pathen dang angsunga na bohkhup uva ahileh, na chung uva thina lhung jeng ding ahi.  
\v 20 Pakai, Pathen nah sah louva naum uva ahileh, nam dang ki sumang ho banga nangho jong na ki sumang diu ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Israel te seichalna  
\p
\v 1 Ngaiyun, O Israel! Tunia hi nangman Jordan vadung galkaiya namdang te chenna nalut ding ahitan, amaho khu nangho jouse sanga hatthei ahiuve. Khopi sunga acheng uvin chule akhopi kimvel uva pal kigen jouse jong vanthamjol chana sang ahi!  
\v 2 Amaho khu nangho sang'in asang jouvin chule athahat jouvin abonchauva Anak chilhah ahiuve. Hijeh chun amahoa kon'in awchang naja tauvin, Anak mite kalvala chungnungjo koi ham? tin asei uve.  
\v 3 Ahinlah nahe sohkei uve tunikhoa hi Pakai, Pathen'in ki dangtah’a aluchung vumuva meikong akilah sah ding asuh gam hel diu ahi. Pakaiyin ahin suhnem diu chuteng nang hon baithet’a natha gam diu ahi. Hichu Pakai, Pathen kitepna ahi.  
\v 4 Pakai, Pathen'in nangho dinga hitobang natoh ahin chaisoh tengleh, ka chonphat jeh uva Pakaiyin hiche gam hi eipeh’u ahi, tia nasei louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu hiche nam mite phatlou jeh a Pakaiyin agam uva konna asoldoh joh ahi.  
\v 5 Nangho chonphat vanga hiche gam hi nalo diu ahipoi. Hinlah hiche nam mite phatlou jeh a adelmang ahin chule Pakai, Pathen'in napu napa teu Abraham, Isaac le Jacob henga aki tepna asuh bukim ahi.  
\v 6 Nangho chonphat vanga Pakaiyin hiche gam hi napeh’u ahipoi ti nahet diu ahi, ajeh chu nangho milungtahte nahiuve.  
\v 7 Gamthip noiya Pakai nalunghan sahnau geldoh jing uvin. Egypt gam nahin dalhah nikho uva pat tuni chana vel ijat Pakai, Pathen doumah nabol doh tah uvem.  
\v 8 Sinai mol jenga jong Pakai doumah nabol uvin hi chun Pakaiyin thagam ding nago uvin ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche hi Sinai molchung kaumlaiya thilsoh ahin, Pakayin songpheng-ni ah imatih chana dingin kitepna chu asem tan ahi. Nisomli le jansomli jen an nelou twidon louvin kaum'inahi. \x + \xo 9:9 \xt Potdohbu 24:18\x*  
\v 10 Chuin Pakaiyin songpheng-ni eipen hichu Pathen ama tah molchunga naum laiyuva athu seidoh chengse akhut’a ajih doh ahi.  
\v 11 Ni somli le jansomli lhin nikhon Pakaiyin kitepna songpheng teni chu eipe tan ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Pakaiyin ka henga aseiyin, Kipat in che tan! Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh miten doumah jeng aboltauve. Chomlou kah in ka thupeh nahsah louvin aki hei mang tauve! Sana limdoi sem in hinkho amang tauvin ahi!  
\v 13 Pakaiyin ka henga asei kit in, ‘Hiche mite lungtah le thungai louna ka muchen tai.  
\v 14 Tun keima che ingting hiche mite hi vannoiya ka suhmang jeng diu ahi. Amaho sanga hatjo le chungnung joa keiman na chillhahte ka tundoh ding ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin molchung vum'a meikong akilui jeng tan ahile, keima ka hung kumsuh in mon mang theilou kitepna songpheng teni chu kahin choiyin ahi.  
\v 16 Keiman kahin vesuh in ahileh, Pakai dingin chonset gitlouna nabol tauve ti ka muchen tai. Sana mangchan bonglim doi nakisem thu tauvin ahi. Pakai, Pathen'in nathupeh nauva kon'in chom loukah in nakihei mang tauve!  
\v 17 Chuin keiman songpheng teni chu tol lhama kasep lhan namit mutah uvin kasep in ahi.  
\v 18 Hinlah Pakai, Pathen angsunga nisomli le jan somli masang chun keiman an jong ka nepon chule twi jong ka don poi. Ajeh chu nang hon Pakai doumah bol in hinkho namang tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Pakai lunghanna nachung uva ahung chuh a na thagam diu chu keima ka kicha lheh jenge, hinlah Pakaiyin ka taona eisanpeh kit in ahi. \x + \xo 9:19 \xt Heb 12:21\x*  
\v 20 Pakai chu Joshua chunga alung phamo lheh jeng tan, tha ding agon ahi. Aaron dingin ka taovin ahileh Pakaiyin ahing hoi tan ahi.  
\v 21 Na chonset nau bonglim chu kalan nen lah a meiyin ka halvam tan ahi. Mei kihalna vutvai abonchan kalan molchung a konna vadung twi a kasep lhatan ahi.  
\v 22 Massah, Taberah le Kibroth-hattavah mun'a jong Pakai doumah nabol uvin ahi. \x + \xo 9:22 \xt Minbu 11:3; \xt Potdohbu 17:7; \xt Minbu 11:34\x*  
\v 23 Chuin Kadesh-barnea mun'a Pakaiyin hiche thupeh mangchan nasol tauvin ahi: Chetou un keiman kapehna gamkhu galo tauvin. Hinlah Pakai, Pathen thupeh nah sah louvin hinkho namang uvin ahi. \x + \xo 9:23 \xt Minbu 13:17; \xt Danbu Ni Na 1:21; \xt Minbu 13:31; Danbu Ni Na 1:26; Heb 3:16\x*  
\v 24 Henge, Pakai doumah jeng nabol uve tihi keiman kahin he jingin ahi.  
\v 25 Hijeh achu nisomli le jan somli Pakai henga ka bohkhup in ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin na boncha uva thagam ding na got’u ahi.  
\v 26 Pakai henga hiti hin kataove, O thaneipen Pakai, hiche mite hi sugam louvin, hinghoi tauvin. Amaho hi namite ahiuve. Chule amaho hi nagoulupen Egypt gam'a nahuhdoh’a naban thahat pana nahin puidoh ahiuve.  
\v 27 Hiche mite chonsetna leh lungtahna a kon'in ngaidam tan, chule ka puluiyu Abraham, Isaac le Jacob geldoh in, ati.  
\v 28 Hiche mite hi na suhmanga ahileh, Egypt miten hitia hi asei diu, ‘Israel mite athi gam tauve, ajeh chu Pakaiyin aki tepna gam'a chu apui lhung lou ahitai.’ Ahilouleh hiche mite hi Pakaiyin avetda jeh a asuh gam ahi tauve; thagam dinga apuile ahi, tia asei diu ahi.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu hiche mite hi nangman naban thahat pana Egypt gamsunga konna nahin puidoh ahiuve.   
\c 10  
\s1 Dokhang song ani channa  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin kaheng ah hiti hin aseiyin, Songpheng ni masanga toh kibang chat hin choiyin chule thingkong khat phatah in sem inlang asunga khum ding ahi. Hiche na ding chun molchunga kahenga hung kaltouvin.  
\v 2 Hiche songpheng chunga chu masanga na sekeh chunga thucheng kijih bang banga kajih lut ding, hichu thingkong sunga nakoi ding ahi.  
\v 3 Keiman thinggi thingkong in kasemin chule amasanga bang banginsongpheng ni ka suitoh in ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Pakaiyin avelin thupeh som ho chu ajih lut in, keima eipetan ahi. Songpheng teni chu kakhut in kachoiyin, molchung lama kakal tou tan ahi.  
\v 5 Molchunga kon ka hung ki heisuh in, kitepna songpheng teni chu thingkong sunga kakoi tan, hichu Pakai thupeh banga keiman kabol ahi. Songpheng teni chu thingkong sunga aumtai.  
\v 6 Israel mite chu Jaakan twikul mun'a kon'in Moserah kiti Aaron kivuina mun'a chun akitol tauvin ahi. Achapa Eleazar chun thempu na atoh ahi. \x + \xo 10:6 \xt Minbu 20:28; 33:38\x*  
\v 7 Hiche mun'a pat chun, Gudgodah mun ajon tauvin, aban'in Jotbathah hiche mun'a chu twisam tampi putna mun ahi.  
\v 8 Hichun Pakaiyin Levi insung mite chu thingkong pu dingin adei lhen tan, chuleh Pakai angsunga ding diu Pakai min'a thempu na atoh diu ahi. Hiche hi amaho natoh ding ahi. \x + \xo 10:8 \xt Minbu 3:5-8\x*  
\v 9 Hiche jeh achu Israel mite lah a Levi insung chu chenna ding gamtum nei louva um ahiuvin, Pakai hi amaho dinga agoulupenu leh Pakai, Pathen thempu kinbol dinga um ahi tauve.  
\v 10 Keiman amasa pena dingin, ‘Nisomli le jan somli molchunga Pakai henga kaum in, Pakaiyin avelin ka taona asang'in nangho nahing hoi tauvin ahi.’ \x + \xo 10:10 \xt Potdohbu 34:28\x*  
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin ka henga aseiyin, keiman napuluiteu khang apat peh dinga ka kitepna, gamlo din mipi ho lamkai tan, ati.   
\s1 Pathen a konna ngaichatna  
\p
\v 12 Chule tun, Israel mite, Pakai, Pathen'in nanghoa konna adei chu ipi ham? Pakaiyin nanghoa konna adeichu Pakai ging jingun lang chule Pakai lunglam jeng nabol diu, na lungthim pumpiuva Pakai lam jeng nakat diu ahi.  
\v 13 Chule tunia najah uva kasei, Pakai, Pathen a konna thupeh chengse aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 14 Veuvin! Chung sangpen leh leiset chunga thil ijakai jouse hi Pakai, Pathen a bou ahi.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin napuluiteu ana ngailun hijeh achu, achilhah teu nangho jouse jong nam dang jouse sanga Pakaiyin na khohsah joh’u ahi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun na lungtah nauva kon'in, na lung heiyun.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu Pakai le na Pathen uhi pathen jouse lah a Pathen chungnung, pakai jouse lah a Pakai chungpen ahi. Ki dangtah Pathen ahin, sihnei langneina beihel Pathen ahi. \x + \xo 10:17 \xt 1 Tim 6:15; Rev 17:14; 19:16; Act 10:34; Rm 2:11; Gal 2:6; Eph 6:9\x*  
\v 18 Pakaiyin meithaiho leh chagaho angailun chule gamdangmi nalah uva chengho angailun, von ki-ah ding apeuvin ahi.  
\v 19 Hijeh chun nang hon jong kholjinmi na ngailut diu ahi, ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gam'a kholjina hinkho na-namanu ahi.  
\v 20 Nanghon Pakai, na Pathen'u kin jeng nabol diu ahi. Kitepna ijakai Pakai min jenga nanei diu ahi.  
\v 21 Pakai ama bou Pathen ahin, chule Pakai bou choi-at dinga lom ahi. Ajeh chu ama bouvin thil kidang ijakai abol in, hichu namit tah uvin namu sohkei uve.  
\v 22 Napu napate hou Egypt gam'a ache uchun amaho mi somsagi bou ahiuve. Hinlah tun nangho Pakai, Pathen'in van'a ahsi jat in na semdoh tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 10:22 \xt Semtilbu 46:27; \xt Semtilbu 15:5; 22:17\x*   
\c 11  
\s1 Pathen ngailun lang athu ngaiyin  
\p
\v 1 Nanghon Pakai, Pathen na ngailut diu chule Pakai dan leh thupeh aboncha najui teidiu ahi.  
\v 2 Chule nalungthim in haimil hih uvin, ajeh chu keiman nachateu henga thu hichengse Pakaiya konna dan leh thupeh khat jengcha jong ajah uvin kasei pon, ama hon Pakai, Pathen loupi le thahatna mu jong amudoh hih laiyuve.  
\v 3 Pakaiyin Egypt gam Pharaoh henga thil kidang tampi akilahsah in, hinlah ama hon hichu amu hih laiyuve. \x + \xo 11:3 \xt Potdohbu 7:8—12:13\x*  
\v 4 Pakaiyin Egypt galsat miho le asakol kangtalai hou chunga itobanga na-atoh ham ti amu pouvin, chule Egypt miten nahindal laitah uva Twipi San dunga Pakai natoh jong amun'ai pouvin ahi. Amaho chu Pakaiyin asumang hel tauve. \x + \xo 11:4 \xt Potdohbu 14:28\x*  
\v 5 Gamthip akon tuni chanin Pakaiyin, ichan geiya nakhohsah uham ti nachateu vin amu nai pouve.  
\v 6 Reuben chilhah, Eliab chapa teni Dathan leh Abiram chunga Pathen natoh jong nachaten amu pouvin ahi. Gamleiset Israel mite chenna aki hoh in, chuin amaho abonchauvin agam hel tauvin; aponbuh hou ahin chule anei leh agou ganchahou, jaonan abonchan amang heltan ahi. \x + \xo 11:6 \xt Minbu 16:31,32\x*  
\v 7 Hinlah nang hon Pakai natoh ki dang abonchan namu sohkei tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun chingtheiyun, tunia thupeh chengse aboncha najui kimsohkeidiu ahi. Chutileh na thahat diu nalhunna diu gamsung nalo thei diu ahi.  
\v 9 Thupeh hi chengse najui uva ahileh Pakaiyin napu napa teu khanga peh dinga akitepna gam napeh diu ahi, ajeh chu amaho chilhah ten hiche khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gam khu aluodiu ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche gam naluodiu khu nahin dalhah’u Egypt gam tobang ahipon, hiche gam leiset achun honsunga ipi muchi hijongleh aga aphapon ahi.  
\v 11 Amavang naluo diu gam hi go jong aneng in, gamphatah ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche gam sung pumpi hi Pakaiyin nangho jouse dinga, aphatcha avet kol jing ahi.  
\v 13 Tunia naheng uva ka thupeh chengse najui uva chule Pakai, Pathen kin jing nabol uva ahileh, \x + \xo 11:13 \xt Thempu Dan 26:3-5; Danbu Ni Na 7:12-16; 28:1-14\x*  
\v 14 Pakaiyin go-nangai chat tengu leh gamsunga go ahin juhsah ding, chule chang khoptup phat ahiteng jongleh go juh atansah ding ahi. Chuteng nang hon louga, lengpithei leh Olive thao nakhop tup diu ahi.  
\v 15 Nagan chate diuva anpha tah tah napeh diu chule nang hon nadu chan’u naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 16 Hinlah chingtheiyun. Na lungthim'u phat mosah hih uvin, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen a konna Pathen dang nabel lo diu ahi.  
\v 17 Achuti louva ahileh Pakai lunghanna chun na halvam jeng diu, Pakaiyin vankot akha ding gotwi aum lou teng nang hon ahina banga chang na khop tup thei lou diu ahi. Chuteng hiche gampha mun'a chu hetman louva na thigam jeng diu ahi.  
\v 18 Hijeh chun ka thupeh chengse hi nalungthim cheh uva koiyun. Na khut uva kibu’uvin chule naluchang uva kop un chutileh imatih chana na haimil lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 11:18 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:6-9\x*  
\v 19 Na chateu henga na seipeh sohkei diu ahi. Insunga naumpet’u hihen, lam najot pet, imut kon chule nathodoh kon teng ujongleh naseipeh diu ahi.  
\v 20 Thupeh chengse chu kot phung leh kelkot jousea najih diu ahi.  
\v 21 Chutileh vanthamjol um laisea, Pakaiyin napehnau gamsunga nangho leh na chateu chule na chilhah teu chan geiya lung monga na chen diu ahi.  
\v 22 Ka thupeh jouse hi chingthei tah a najui diu ahi. Pakai, Pathen lama nache jing diu, chule hichu natuh chah jing diu,  
\v 23 Chuteng Pakaiyin namasang uva nam dang jouse ajamsah ding ahi. Amaho athao hat jo jongleh, Pakaiyin agamu nangho khut a apeh doh ding ahi.  
\v 24 Anneh nakiholna jouseu chu nangho gam hi ding ahi. Chule solam gamkaiya pat lhumlam chan, hichu Euphrate vadung chan geiya nalo diu, hiche gamsunga chu koima chan nasuh loh thei lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 11:24 \xt Joshua 1:3-5\x*  
\v 25 Pakaiyin kitepna anei banga koima chan ima nalo theilou diu chule na chennau gam jousea lungmonga na chen diu ahi.  
\v 26 Vetan, tunin keiman thilni kapeh diu, hichu nang hon khat joh sang nakilhen diu, hichu phat theina leh gao sapna ahi.  
\v 27 Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh chengse hi na nitsohkeiyuva ahileh, nangho phatthei na chan diu ahi.  
\v 28 Hinlah thupeh hichengse hi jui louva, nahsahmoa na koiyuva Pathen a konna na kihei manguva, imatih chana nahet khah lou pathen dang kin nabol uva ahileh gaosapna nachan teitei diu ahi.  
\v 29 Gamsung nalhun tengu leh Pakai, Pathen phattheina Gerizim molsanga naphon doh diu chule gaosapna vang chu Ebal molsang hi ding ahi. \x + \xo 11:29 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:11-14; Joshua 8:33-35\x*  
\v 30 Hiche molsang teni hi, lhumlam Jordan phaicham a Canaan mite chenna, Gilgal khopi toh kinai cha, Moreh apat ki gamla talou ahi.  
\v 31 Ajeh chu nang hon Jordan vadung galkaiya Pakai, Pathen'in peh dinga atepsa gam lhung ding nahi tauve. Gamsung nalhun uva, nachen tengu leh,  
\v 32 tunia keiman kapeh dan jui ding jouse, aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Thilto nading maicham phung  
\p
\v 1 Hichengse hi napu, napa teu khanga Pakai, Pathen'in dan leh thupeh jui dinga na peh’u ahi. Hoilai mun hijongleh nadam sung uva najui jing diu ahi.  
\v 2 Hiche gam khu nalhun uva, nam dangte abonchauva nano mang tengu leh, a pathen milimsemthu jouseu molchunga hihen, gammang lah chule thingphung tinchenga hijongleh na suhmanghel diu ahi.  
\v 3 Amaicham hou nasuh set diu chule maicham phung jouse jong nasuh chim diu ahi. Asherah ho jong meiya nahalvam diu chule apathen min jouseu aboncha na suhmanghel diu ahi. \x + \xo 12:3 \xt Danbu Ni Na 7:5\x*  
\v 4 Hiche Pagan miten pathen ahou banga nang hon nahou lou diu ahi.  
\v 5 Amavang nang hon Pakai, Pathen houna ding mun'a Israel insung aboncha kikhop khomna mun'a chu, gin leh jabol tah’a nahou diu ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche mun'a chu pumgo thilto nahin choi diu, nathilto diu som’a khat, kitepna suhbuh lhitna ding thilto chule na gancha penglha masa jouseu jong na todoh cheh cheh diu ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche mun'a chu nang leh na insung miten Pakai ansunga an neh khom nanei diu, Pakai phatthei naho nachan diu ahi, ajeh chu nangman Pakai thupeh nanit jal ahi.  
\v 8 Pakai kin nabol danu jong kikhel ding ahi. Tunin na boncha uvin natao uve.  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin atumbeh a napeh naugam nangho jouse dinga choldona gam chu na lhun nailou’u ahi.  
\v 10 Hinlah nang hon chomlou kah’a Jordan vadung nagal kai diu chule gamsung nalhun diu ahi. Pakaiyin nagal mite hou jouse a konna choldamna napeh tengu leh,  
\v 11 naboncha uva keiman ka thupeh chengse nahin choi diu pumgo thilto, na thilto diu ho, kitepna suh bulhit nading thilto hichengse hi, Pakai amintheng loupina ding mun'a chu nahin choisohkei diu ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche mun'a chu nachanuteu ahin, nachapa teu chule nasohte jouseu jaona Pakai henga thangvahna nanei khom diu ahi. Chule khopi sunga nachen khompiu Levi mite nagel doh jing diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon gam chanvou anei lou’u ahi.  
\v 13 Nangho chingtheiyun, ajeh chu mun jousea pumgo thilto na todoh thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 14 Na insung miteu chenna mun, hichu Pakaiyin adeilhenna mun'a vang chu natodoh thei diu ahi. Hiche mun'a chu pumgo thilto natodoh diu chule ka thupeh aboncha nabol kimsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 15 Nagan chate vang chu na kitha a khopi tinchanga naneh jeng theiyu ahi. Pakai, Pathen'in phatthei aboh ganchaho chu nadei chan naneh jeng theiyu ahi. Sakhisa leh Sapeng jong naneh bang bang uva hi nanop chan’u naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 16 Gan thisanho vang chu meiya nago lou diu, chule gan thisan jouse chu tollham a twi kisung banga nasun lhah diu ahi. \x + \xo 12:16 \xt Semtilbu 9:4; Thempu Dan 7:26,27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Danbu Ni Na 15:23\x*  
\v 17 Hinlah nang hon na thilto hou chu na khopi sung uva naneh thei lou diu, hichu som’a khat ahin, gathah, Olive thao, nagancha asoh masaho ahin chule kitepna thilto, chule mimal kipehna thilto ho hijongleh khopi dunga naneh thang lou diu ahi.  
\v 18 Hichengse chu Pakaiyin adeilhen na mun'a chu naneh diu ahi. Na chateu ahin, nasohteu ahin chule khopi sunga Levi mite jaona hichu Pakai, Pathen ansunga golvah nabol khom diu ahi.  
\v 19 Chule nadam sung uva Levi mite nageldoh jing diu ahi.  
\v 20 Pakaiyin akitepna banga nagam-u ahin keh let ding, nang hon sa nadu chanu hoilai mun'a hijongleh naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 21 Hichu Pakai deilhenna mun, Pakaiyin akinbol nadia adeilhen namun’a jong naneh thei diu nain mun'a pat kenglama saotah kijot ahi. Chutengleh gancha lah a nakel hon, na kelngoi hon chule nabong hon lah a nadei na kitha uva naneh jeng theiyu ahi.  
\v 22 Nalah uva koi hijongleh atheng hihen, aboh hileh hichu aneh jeng thei ding, Sapeng le Sakhisa banga naneh diu ahi.  
\v 23 Gan thisan vang chu meiya nago vam thei lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu thisan hi hinkho tobang ahin, hinna thisan chule gancha meiya na gotha lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 12:23 \xt Thempu Dan 17:10-14\x*  
\v 24 Hiche khel chun gan thisan chu, twi banga tol lhama nasun lhah diu ahi.  
\v 25 Gan thisan chu meiya nago vam louhel diu ahi. Chutileh nangho leh nachateu nabon chau chunga, ijakai phacham kimsohkei ding ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon Pakai lunglam nabol jeh’u ahi.  
\v 26 Atumbeh a nathilpeh diu leh kitepna thilto chu choiyun lang, Pakaiyin adei lhenna mun'a chu naga koi diu ahi.  
\v 27 Nanghon Pakai, Pathen maicham phunga chu pumgo thilto gan thisan naga todoh teitei diu ahi. Gan thisan jouse chu Pakai maicham kimvela nathe khum sohkei diu, asa vang naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 28 Chingtheiyun ka thupeh aboncha najui kim sohkei diu ahi. Chutileh nangho leh nachateu chunga ijakai phacham kimsoh ding ahi, ajeh chu Pakai lunglama nachon jalu ahi.   
\s1 Thuhillhem akon kiveng un  
\p
\v 29 Pakai, Pathen na-masang lamuva che jing ding, chuteng nam dangte jam gam diu agamsunga konna asuhmanghel diu ahi.  
\v 30 Hiche mun'a chu achon chan’u jui ding nagot louhel diu chule apathen hou kin jong nabol louhel diu ahi. A pathen hou chung chang hetnomna jong nei louva, hiche nam mite hin pathen iti ahou uham tiajong nadoh lou diu ahi.  
\v 31 Nanghon nam dangten apathen’u ahou bang uva Pakai, Pathen nahou louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon Pakai lama dinga doumah jeng abol uvin, achapa teu leh achanute hou jeng jong apathen diuva akatdoh jiu ahi.  
\v 32 Hijeh chun ka thupeh jouse hi chingthei tah’a najui diu ahi. Nanghoa konna ima ki lahdoh sah hih unlang chule amahoa konna jong imacha lah ding nagot lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 12:32 \xt Danbu Ni Na 4:2; Rev 22:18,19\x*   
\c 13  
\s1 Milimdoi houho gotna  
\p
\v 1 Chule nalah uva gaothusei ho khonunga hunglhung ding aseiyun, ama hon thil kidang melchihna ho aki lahsah uve.  
\v 2 Hiche bang chun gaothua asei doh jouseu agui lhungin ahi. Amaho chun hiti hin hinseiyu henlang, ‘hungun, pathen dang hou tau hite, ajeh chu hiche pathen ho hi imatih chana nahet khah louvu ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia chu ahinsei diu amavang, na nahsah louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu nPakai, na Pathen'u thua nanun jing diu chule nalungthim pumpiuva Pakai lam jeng nakat diu, chuteng Pakaiyin nangho nangailut jing diu ahi.  
\v 4 Pakai, na Pathen'u kin jeng nabol diu ahi. Pakai thupeh nanit jing diu, Pakai thusei a bou nanun diu chule Ama lam jeng nakat diu ahi.  
\v 5 Alam louva gaothusei doh’a khonung ding thilmu ho abonchauva thina chang diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon nahuhhing pau Pakai, na Pathen'u Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh pau doumah jeng abol tauvin ahi. Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh a kon'in puimang ding nagouvin, hijeh achu thina nachansah teitei diu ahi. Hitia chu nalah uva konna phatlou naho natol mang diu ahi.  
\v 6 Mikhat touvin guhthima nahin lhep diu nasopipa, nachanu ham nachapa, nangailuttah najinu, ahilouleh naloi ngaipen najah uva hitia hi asei diu, ‘pathen dang hou din cheu hite ati diu, hinlah hiche pathen ho hi napu, na pateu jengin jong ana het khah lou ahi.  
\v 7 Nahin lhep patep diu, napu, napa teu khanga pat le leiset a nahet khah lou pathen hou tauvin, atidiu ahi.  
\v 8 Hinlah athu uva nanun louhel diu ahi. Chule hepina jong nanei lou diu, ven jong naven bit thei louhel diu ahi.  
\v 9 Amaho chu thina nachansah teitei diu ahi! Amasa tah in kho lhangsam leu chun mipin nahin kithopi diu ahi.  
\v 10 Phat louna keng mihem chu thina nachansah diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon Pakai, na Pathen a kon'in puimang ding nagouve. Egypt gam'a soh a naum laiyuva Pakaiyin nahuhdoh'u ahi.  
\v 11 Chuteng Israel pumpin ajahsohkei diu kichatna anei diu, adih louva chonkit talou ding ahiuve.  
\v 12 Pakai, na Pathen uvin napehnau khopi sunga nachen tengu leh, nang hon hitia thu kisei najah diu,  
\v 13 nalah uva gaothusei hon nasopi hou henga hiti hin aseiyun alam kaiyuve, pathen dang houvin cheu hite atiuvin, hinlah hiche pathen ho khu imatih chana nahet khah louvu ahi.’  
\v 14 Hitobang dimun hoa konna nakikhol cheh diu ahi. Nalah uva hitobang thil aum mong taiti aki cheh tengleh,  
\v 15 hiche khopi sung leh achilhah te jouseu le agancha jouseu jaona na suhmanghel diu ahi.  
\v 16 Mun kihong laiya chu aboncha nahalvam heldiu chule khopi chu Pakai, Pathen dinga pumgo thiltoa pang ding ahi. Hiche khopi chu kiledoh kit talou ding chule sajong kisadoh kit louding ahitai.  
\v 17 Khopi sahdoh nathei thil khat cha jong naum den sahlou diu ahi. Chuteng Pakai milungsetna chu nachan diu chule hepina dimset a napu, napa teu khanga akitepna banga nam lentah naso diu ahi.  
\v 18 Pakai, na Pathen'u thupeh aboncha najui kimsohkeiyuva ahileh, Pathen mihepina chu nachan jing diu ahi.   
\c 14  
\p
\v 1 Nangho Pakai, na Pathen a mong nahinau photchetna dingin, nachalsam kalval uva navotol louhel diu ahi. Hichu athiho lunghempina ahi. \x + \xo 14:1 \xt Thempu Dan 19:28; 21:5\x*  
\v 2 Pakai, na Pathen diuva nangho atheng nahi tauve, leiset chunga nam jouse lah a goulu pena nalhen doh’u ahitai. \x + \xo 14:2 \xt Potdohbu 19:5,6; Danbu Ni Na 4:20; 7:6; 26:18; Tit 2:14; 1 Pet 2:9\x*   
\s1 Satheng leh sathenglou  
\p
\v 3 Chule gancha boh kiti phot naneh thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 4 Hichengse vang hi naneh thei diu ahi: bongchal, kelngoi, kelcha,  
\v 5 sajuh, pelkai, sakhi, gam kel, chule molchunga kelngoi jaona neneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 6 Nanghon a-an lhai umho naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 7 Hinlah a-an lhai umlou sa vang chu naneh lou diu ahi. Hichu sangong sang, talep, bui amaho cheng hin an-lhai aneiyun ahinlah a-ihdoh pouvin ahi. Hijeh achu hiche gancha ho hi nangho dinga athenglou ahi.  
\v 8 Chule vohcha jong naneh lou diu ahi. Anlhai aneiyin hinlah a-ihdoh poi, hijeh achu nangho dia athenglou ahiye. Hiche gancha hose hi neh jong naneh thei lou diu chule toh jong natoh khah lou diu ahi.  
\v 9 Twikhanglen'a cheng ganhing lah a, aling nei naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 10 Hijeh chun twikhanglen'a um alingnei naneh diu, hinlah aling nei lou kitiphot vang naneh lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu hichengse hi nangho dia athenglou ahi.  
\v 11 Chule nang hon chungleng vacha namkim naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 12 Hinlah vacha hichengse hi naneh thei lou diu ahi: muthang chule mubong naneh lou diu,  
\v 13 chule Muvom, muthi, sumbupi,  
\v 14 va-ah leh ama tobang va dang jouse,  
\v 15 muthi, muthi-muhchom, chule adang phabep jaona,  
\v 16 sumbupi nou, sumbupi len, sumbu changlit,  
\v 17 muthibong, sumbu changlit, sumbupi, Egypt mite muthi,  
\v 18 bah chule adang phabep jaona naneh lou diu ahi.  
\v 19 Tollham a ganhing vahle jouse hi naneh lou diu ahi, ajeh chu athenglou ahi.  
\v 20 Hinlah vacha lhanei atheng kitiphot chu naneh diu ahi.   
\p
\v 21 Ganthikam kiti naneh louhel diu ahi. Nakhopi sung uva kholjin miho naneh sah thei diu ahilouleh na hetkhah lou mikom'a najoh thei diu ahi. Amavang nang hon naneh thei louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen diuva atheng nahiuve. Chule nang hon kelchanou chu kelchapi noitwiya nahon lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 14:21 \xt Potdohbu 23:19; 34:26\x*   
\s1 Hopsom peh ding dan  
\p
\v 22 Gasoh lah a som’a khat ding nakoi doh diu gasoh jouse lah a, som’a khat kumseh le na todoh diu ahi. \x + \xo 14:22 \xt Thempu Dan 27:30-33; Minbu 18:21\x*  
\v 23 Hiche som’a khat chu Pathen houna mun'a nahin choi diu Pakai, Pathen'in amin dopsang nadinga alhenna mun'a chu nahin choi diu, hichu Pakai angsunga naneh diu ahi.  
\v 24 Pakai, na Pathen uvin phatthei nahin boh tengu leh mun gam lha tah hijongleh lousohga tamtah nalo diu, chuteng hoilai mun'a kon hijongleh som’a khat nahin choi diu ahi.  
\v 25 Amun chu agamlat behseh a ahileh, hiche gasoh chu najoh diu najohna manu vang chu Pakai, na Pathen'u houna mun'a chu nalhut diu ahi.  
\v 26 Nahung lhun tengu leh, nang hon nadeichan nasumuva nakichoh diu bongchal, kelngoi, kelcha, lengpitwi chule adang donthei nachoh jeng theiyu ahi. Chuteng nangho leh na insung mi teuvin Pakai ansunga an-najon khom diu ahi.  
\v 27 Chule nalah uva Levi mite nahebol jing diu ahi. Ajeh chu amaho chenna ding nei louva um ahiuve.  
\v 28 Kumthum lhinsih leh som’a khat achombeh a nahin choi diu, hichu khopi toh kinaichaa nakhol khom diu,  
\v 29 hichu Levi mite napeh diu ahi. Ajeh chu amaho gam nei louva khosa ahiuvin, hichu ama hon aneh uva lungkim sela umdiu ahit. Chutile Pakai, na Pathen uvin phatthei naboh diu ahi.   
\c 15  
\s1 Sabbath kum chamlhatna  
\p
\v 1 Kum sagi alhinseh leh khat kom'a sumpa bat a nalah jouseu chu na le sah diu ahi.  
\v 2 Hichu nabol teitei diu ahi. Israel mite lah a hitobanga thil bat a kila jouse chu nakile sahto naphat-u ahi. Koiman asopi aheng akom'a thil bat a alah thei louding ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen dinga kilha ongna lhung ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche bat kilesahto nahi Israel mite insunga ding bou ahin, kholjin miho jao lou ahi.  
\v 4 Koima vaichatah a umlou ding ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin na pehnau gamsunga phat theina hunglhung ding ahi.  
\v 5 Tunia keiman kapeh thupeh aboncha nanit kimsohkeiyuva ahileh Pakai, Pathen'in phattheina chamkim naboh diu ahi.  
\v 6 Chuteng Pakai, na Pathen uvin akitepna banga phatthei naboh teidiu ahi. Nam dangten naheng uva sumpa ahinlah diu chule nang hon vang bat a ima nalah lou diu ahitai. Namdangte chunga vaihoma napan diu, nangho chunga koiman thaneina a vai ahop louding ahi.   
\s1 Vaichate kithopina  
\p
\v 7 Hinlah Pakai, na Pathen uvin napehnau gam nalhun tengu leh, Israel insunga konna avaicha aum khah leh ama chu nadal bol louhel diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:7 \xt Thempu Dan 25:35\x*  
\v 8 Hongphal tah a amaho chu achandiu gambeh napeh diu ahi.  
\v 9 Bat a thilpeh ding hijongleh itlouhel a napeh diu ahi. Ajeh chu khat leh khat bat a konna kilepeh naphat chu nakhut uva um jing ahi. Bat a peh ding nada uva mikhat nachung uva lhisona aneiya ahileh, phat louna chonset achu lhalut nahi tauve.  
\v 10 Vaichaten angaichat banga hongphal tah a napeh diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin natoh nalam lamuva phatthei naboh diu ahi.  
\v 11 Na chennau gamusunga chu vaicha um jing ding ahi. Hiche thupeh hi najui jing diu ahi, ajeh chu Israel mite lah hihen midang lah hileh vaicha a hinkho mang um jing ding ahi. \x + \xo 15:11 \xt Matt 26:11; Mk 14:7; Jn 12:8\x*   
\s1 Soh a kivul ho dan  
\p
\v 12 Hebrew mite lah a konna numei hileh pasal hileh soh dinga kiphal aum leh kum gup sunga nangho najen diu, kumsagi ahung lhun tengleh nang hon hiche sohnu ham sohpa ham chu, chamlhatna napeh diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:12 \xt Thempu Dan 25:39-46\x*  
\v 13 Soh pasal chu na soldoh tengu leh, khut goh keuva nasol lou diu ahi.  
\v 14 Alhahna dinga gancha honkhat napeh diu, najubel tun nauleh lhongdapna toh napeh tha diu ahi. Nanei nagou lah uva kijepna phabep jong napeh tha diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in ijakai napeh'u ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche hi nageldoh jing diu ahi. Nangho Egypt gam'a soh in nana um un Pakai, Pathen'in na lhatdoh’u ahi! Hijeh a chu keiman hiche thupeh hi nangho kapeh nahiuve.  
\v 16 Hinlah soh chun ‘Keiman ka dalhah louding nahi’ tia aseiya ahileh, ajeh chu aman nangma leh na insung mite angailut jal ahi.  
\v 17 Hitobang dinmun'a konna hi nang hon jong nakotbul uva konna nasoh uchu, nahin lepui diu chuteng hinkho lhumkeiya naheng uva um thei ding ahi.  
\v 18 Nasoh uchu nasoldoh tengu leh hahsatna a nagel lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu kum gup sunga ajo chana nahin jenu ahitan, Pakai na Pathen uvin phatthei naboh diu ahi.   
\s1 Gancha peng masa  
\p
\v 19 Na ganchate lah uva konna apeng masa jouse Pakai, Pathen henga nahin choi diu ahi. Na ganchateu lah a apeng masa kitiphot chu louna natohsah lou diu chule gancha hon lah a nalhatsah lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:19 \xt Potdohbu 13:12\x*  
\v 20 Ajeh chu gancha peng masa jouse hi Pakai, Pathen henga nahin choidiu nangho leh na insung mi teuvin Pakaiyin alhena mun'a chu kumseh leh naneh khom diu ahi.  
\v 21 Hinlah hiche gancha pengmasa chu a elbai ham ahilouleh mitcho ahikhah leh nang hon Pakai, na Pathen'u henga na todoh lou diu ahi.  
\v 22 Hichu nangho leh na insung mi teuvin nain mun uva naneh jeng theiyu ahi. Hichu koi hileh aboh hihen aboh lou hijongleh sa juhsa naneh bang uva naneh thei diu ahi.  
\v 23 Chule sa thisan chu meiya na halvam thei lou diu ahi. Hichu tol lham chunga nasun lhah diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:23 \xt Semtilbu 9:4; Thempu Dan 7:26,27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Danbu Ni Na 12:16,23\x*   
\c 16  
\s1 Kalchuh Kut  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, na Pathen uva dinga kumseh le kut nabol diu ahi. Hichu Abib* lhamasa hi ding ahi. Ajeh chu hiche lhasunga hi Pakaiyin Egypt gam'a konna jan muthim noiya nahin puidoh-u ahi. \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-20; Thempu Dan 23:5-8; Minbu 28:16-25\x*  
\v 2 Hiche kut ading chun nagan chateu lah a kon todoh ding chengse chu Pakai, Pathen'in adeilhenna houmun a chu nahin choi diu, hiche mun chu Pathen loupina ding ahi.  
\v 3 Hichu cholsolou changlhah toh aneh tha diu ahi. Nisagi sunga cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh diu ahi, ajeh chu Egypt gam'a konna kinotah a nahungnau avetsah ahi. Hiche changlhah hi neuvin suhgim vetsahna changlhah ahin, chutileh nadam lai sung seuva Egypt gam'a konna nahung potdoh nau na geldoh jing diu ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche nisagi sunga hin koiman cholsosa a-in mun'a koihih hen. Kut adia kelngoi natha tengu leh, hiche sa chu koiman jingkah khovah geiyin koihih hen.  
\v 5 Hiche kut hi khopi tinchenga nabol thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 6 Pakai, Pathen'in adeilhenna mun a bou chu nabol diu ahi, ajeh chu Pakai, na Pathen uvin amin choiatna dinga alhen ahi. Nisa alep lhah tengleh hichu Egypt gam'a nahung potdoh nau vetsahna nabol diu ahi.  
\v 7 Sachu nakisem diu Pakaiyin alhenna mun'a chu naneh diu ahi. Chule jingkah lam leh na ponbuh mun cheh uva nakile thei diu ahitai.  
\v 8 Hinlah aban nigup sunga chu cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh diu ahi. Anisagi lhin ni chu Pakai, Pathen adia nikho thenga nanit sohkei diu, koiman na atoh thei louding ahi.   
\s1 Hapta kut  
\p
\v 9 Lousohga nakhop tup nikho uva pat hapta sagi nasim diu ahi. \x + \xo 16:9 \xt Thempu Dan 23:15-21; Minbu 28:26-31\x*  
\v 10 Chujou tengleh Pakai, na Pathen uva dinga Kalchuh Kut golvah nabol diu ahi. Pakaiya konna phatthei nachanna hou ijakai nahin choisohkei diu ahi.  
\v 11 Chuteng Pakai, na Pathen uvin houmun adei lhenna mun'a chu na hinchoi diu golvah nabol diu, hiche mun'a chu Pathen min choiat a um ding ahi. Na khopi sung uva nachanuteu leh na chapa teu chule Levi mite ahin, chagate, kholjin miho chule meithai ho jaona a golvah nabol khom diu ahi.  
\v 12 Ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gam'a soh-changa hinkho mang nahiuve ti nageldoh jing diu, thupeh hi chengse hi najui diu ahi.   
\s1 Lhambuh kut  
\p
\v 13 Lhosohga, lengpiga ijakai nakhop tup tengu leh nisagi sunga lholhun kut naman teidiu ahi. \x + \xo 16:13 \xt Thempu Dan 23:33-36,39-43; Minbu 29:12-38\x*  
\v 14 Hiche golvah loupi hi nachanuteu leh nachapa teu, nasoh te hou, Levi mite, chaga ho, kholjin mi chule meithai ho jaona nabol diu ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche golvah hi nisagi sunga Pakaiyin alhenna mun'a chu nabol diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiya konna phatthei nachannau gasoh chu ahin, hiche kut hi mijouse adia kipana hi ding ahi.  
\v 16 Kumseh leh Israel miten hiche kut thum ho hi aman jing diu ahi: Mon mang theilou changlhah kut, lholhun kut chule khoptup kut ahi. Hiche ahung lhun tengleh pasal a kailha kitiphot Pakai, Pathen angsunga kilah ding, koima chan khut goh keuva Pakai angsung anai lut thei louding ahi.  
\v 17 Mijousen ajokham khama phattheina chu Pakai henga ahin lhut cheh diu ahi.   
\s1 Thudih a vaihom  
\p
\v 18 Pakaiyin napeh nau khopi jousea thutan vaihoma pang ding nakoisohkei diu ahi. Amaho chun miho chunga chamdela thu atan diu ahi.  
\v 19 Koima chunga langnei sihneiya thil ima nabol lou diu ahi. Aching athem hihen, khomu louva hijongleh Pakai mit mua chamdela thu natan diu ahi. \x + \xo 16:19 \xt Potdohbu 23:6-8; Thempu Dan 19:15\x*  
\v 20 Adih a kivaihopna chu um jing hen, chutileh Pakai, na Pathen uvin napeh nau gamsunga lungmonga nachen diu ahi.  
\v 21 Asherah thing mangcha a pathen lim nasemthu louhel diu ahi. \x + \xo 16:21 \xt Potdohbu 34:13\x*  
\v 22 Chule aguh a hou dinga khom ima naphu thei lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen adia hitobang chu thet umtah ahi. \x + \xo 16:22 \xt Thempu Dan 26:1\x*   
\c 17  
\p
\v 1 Ana damlou gancha kiti phot Pakai, Pathen henga natodoh thei lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiya dia hitobang thilpeh ho hi thet um ahi.  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gam'a nachen tengu leh, nalah uva konna numei hileh pasal hileh Pakai, na Pathen'u mitmua aphalou nabol thei lou diu chule kitepna nasuhboh thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 3 Semthu pathen dang angsung, nisa chule ahsiho vamthamjol kitiho jouse angsunga naboh khup theilou diu ahi. \x + \xo 17:3 \xt Potdohbu 22:20\x*  
\v 4 Hitobang ho hi nakhol chilsohkei diu ahi. Ajeh chu Israel mite lah a hitobang hi umkha get inte.  
\v 5 Numei hileh pasal hileh hitobanga chon chu, khopi pam lama nodoh ding songa se lih ding ahi.  
\v 6 Hinlah mikhat jeng seh thutannan mithat hih un, mithum beh thutanna'a chu thina nachan sah thei diu ahi. \x + \xo 17:6 \xt Minbu 35:30; Danbu Ni Na 19:15; Matt 18:16; 2 Crth 13:1; 1 Tim 5:19; Heb 10:28\x*  
\v 7 Thutanpa chun songa ase masat ding, chuteng mipin ase ding ahi. Hitia chu nalah uva konna aphalouva chon chu nano doh diu ahi. \x + \xo 17:7 \xt 1 Crth 5:13\x*  
\v 8 Nalah uva thilsoh chung thutanna ahahsat behseh a, hichu phat louna, tol-that, mithat chule dan chung kalvala chon achung thua boina chom chom neiya auma ahileh, hitobang chu Pakai, na Pathen henga nalhut diu ahi.  
\v 9 Chule hitobang ho chu danthempuho henga aphatcha napui diu ahi. Ama hon achung chang thu angai diu chuteng thu lhuhna asem diu ahi.  
\v 10 ama hon thu lhuhna asem uchu Pakai muntheng lama nahin lhut diu, ama hon asei bang uva nabol diu ahi.  
\v 11 Dan dungjuiya thulhuhna chu ahin phondoh tengu leh, thulhuhna jouse chu ahina banga chelha ding, imacha na hapbe thei tah lou diu ahi.  
\v 12 Koi hileh Pakai, Pathen angsunga thutan vaihom ho natohna deilou vetsahna jal'a kisa auma ahileh, thina chang ding ahi. Hitia chu phat louna kiti phot Israel mite lah a konna nano mang diu ahi.  
\v 13 Hitobang chu mijousen ahin jahsohkei diu, chuteng koima aphalouva chon ngam talou ding ahi.   
\s1 Leng ding kilhenna  
\p
\v 14 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsung nalhun diu ahitai. Hiche gamsung nalhun tengu leh, i-lamkai diuvin leng khat, nam dangte kivaipoh nabangintungdoh tau hite tia nasei diu ahi. \x + \xo 17:14 \xt 1 Samuel 8:5\x*  
\v 15 Chutengleh Israel mite lah a Pakai, Pathen'in atundoh ding ahi. Hichu nalah uva mikhat pen pang ding, amavang kholjin mi nalhen thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 16 Leng a pang pen ding pen chun, sakol kangtalai ngaichat jeh a mikhat tou Egypt gam'a sakol kangtalai cho dinga asol thei louding ahi. Ajeh chu nangho Egypt gam nakile kit thei lou diu ahitai. \x + \xo 17:16 \xt 1 Lgt 10:28; 2 Thusimbu 1:16; 9:28\x*  
\v 17 Lengpa chun jitampi anei thei louding ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon Pakai a konna apui mang thei diu ahi. Chule ama ding jenga jong sana leh dangka akikhol thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 17:17 \xt 1 Lgt 11:1-8; \xt 1 Lgt 10:14-22,27; 2 Thusimbu 1:15; 9:27\x*  
\v 18 Leng touna mun alo tengleh, amapa chun danbu akilah ding, alal-touna mun'a chu akikoi ding ahi.  
\v 19 Hiche danbu lekhajol chu akom'a akoi ding adamlai sunga asim jing ding ahi. Hichea konna chu dan leh thupeh ijakai Pakaiya kon'in aum'e ti amu chet ding, dengchang tah’a ajui jing ding ahi.  
\v 20 Hiche lekhajol asima konna chu kiletsahna puma, achenkhompi mijouse sanga chungnung kahi tia umlou ding ahi. Chule hichea konna hi lamchoma kihei mang louva um jing ding kahi tijong ahet doh thei ding ahi. Keima leh ka chilhah ten Israel sung hi akhang akhanga ka vaihop diu ahi, tijong het dohna anei thei diu ahi.   
\c 18  
\s1 Thempuho chanvou  
\p
\v 1 Thempu hon hiche hi nageldoh jing diu ahi, ajeh chu Israel insung mijouse lah a Levi insung kailhah hi chenna ding gam chang lou ahiuve. Hijeh achu Thempua pang Levi mite hon Pakai, Pathen adia ki todoh chengse hi chang diu ahi.  
\v 2 Israel nam sunga konna gamtum neilou ahiuvin, Pakai hi amaho dinga agoulu penu ahitan, hichu aheng uva Pakai kitepna ahi. \x + \xo 18:2 \xt Minbu 18:20\x*  
\v 3 Hichengse hi mihon gancha dinga ahin choi lah a thempu ho chan ding chu ahi: bongchal ahin kelngoi hijongleh ama hon adah akeng, agilpi chengse chu thempupa henga apeh lut diu ahi.  
\v 4 Nanghon jong na lou sohgao lhung masaho, lengpitwi, chang, thaotwi chule nakelngoi mul kivou masapen chu neh diu ahi.  
\v 5 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in phung jouse lah a Levi insungmite hi imatih chana ama lhacha a pang dia alhen doh ahi.  
\v 6 Chule Israel mite chenna khopi holah achu Levi miten adeisah laiyu Pathen houna mun'a ahin lhen doh diu ahi.  
\v 7 Levi dang ho banga kigela Pakai, Pathen min pana akin bola pang jeng thei diu, chuteng Pakai angsunga natong jing Levi mite banga akin bola pang diu ahi.  
\v 8 Ama insungmite akon thilpeh ijat um jongleh, thil ki todoh jouse aneh khopset aneh thei diu ahi.   
\s1 Atheng dinga kouna  
\p
\v 9 Nangho Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsung nahin jot tengu leh, chingtheiyun hiche gamsunga namtin vaipi chonna dan thet umtah tah hokhu najui louhel diu ahi.  
\v 10 Nangho lah a konna koiman achanu ham achapa ham khat chu meiya agoa kilhaina a amanchah thei louhel ding ahi. Doithu hihen, phunsanna hihen, ipidoi mangcha hijongleh, \x + \xo 18:10 \xt Thempu Dan 19:26; \xt Potdohbu 22:18\x*  
\v 11 buma bolna hihen, thilha a konna gaobol theina hihen, mitphel doithepna chule thilha a konna gaothem kiti jong khat jeng cha nalah uva konna um thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 18:11 \xt Thempu Dan 19:31\x*  
\v 12 Hitobanga chon mihem chu Pakaiya dinga thet umtah ahi. Hijeh achu Pakai, Pathen'in nangho masanga hiche lai mun'a cheng ho jouse anadel mang ahi.  
\v 13 Chule nangho Pakai, Pathen adia mi kitah nahi teidiu ahi. \x + \xo 18:13 \xt Matt 5:48\x*  
\v 14 Ajeh chu hiche mun'a cheng mite hon doithem ho thusei angaiyun, amavang Pakai, Pathen'in hitobang hoa na chon diu aphal pon ahi.   
\s1 Themgao atah le alhem ho  
\p
\v 15 Mose'n avelin aseikit in, Israel te lah a konna Pakai, Pathen'in kei bang banga thempu khat nahin tundoh peh diu ahi. Chuteng nang hon ama thu chu nangaiyuva nakhohsah cheh diu ahi. \x + \xo 18:15 \xt Act 3:22; 7:37\x*  
\v 16 Nanghon Sinai molchunga mipi ho kikhop nikhon Pakai, Pathen henga nadei, nangai chan hiti hin naseiyun ahi. Pakai, Pathen awgin leh ama a konna meikong kilah chu neijah sah kit hih hel un, ajeh chu hitobang kajah uva kamu uva konna chu keiho ka thilo jeng theiyu ahi, natiuve.  
\v 17 Chuin Pakaiyin keima henga aseiyin, ama hon asei chanu hi adih lheh jeng e, ati.  
\v 18 Chule Pakaiyin aseiyin keiman nasopi te lah a konna hi nang tobang khat ka tundoh ding, hiche themgaopa kam sunga chu ijakai ka thumop sohkei ding, hichea konna chu keiman ama ka thumop bang banga aman jong mite jouse athupeh son ding ahi.  
\v 19 Koi hijongleh hiche themgaopa thusei nah sah lou auma ahileh, amapa chunga chu lhen chilna lhung ding ahi. \x + \xo 18:19 \xt Act 3:23\x*  
\v 20 Keima thupeh kal vala chon auma chule pathen limsem thu min pana thusei apang themgao khat tou aum ngei ngeiya ahileh, amapa chunga chu thina lhung teitei ding ahi, tin aseiye.  
\v 21 Hichea chu nang hon Pakai thusei ahipoi, tia lungopkaina nalungthimsung uva nanei khah uva ahileh,  
\v 22 themgao khat in thu aseiya athu seidoh aguilhunva ahilouleh adihlou tengleh, hitobang chu Pathen akon mong ahipoi ti photchetna ahi. Themgaopa chun ama macham chama asei ahin, hitobang themgao chu gin jong nagin louhel diu ahi.   
\c 19  
\s1 Bitna khopi ho  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, Pathen'in nangho napehnau gamsunga cheng mite ahin suhgam teng, nang hon agamsung pumpiu chuleh a in jouseu nalodiu akhopi uva nachen diu ahi. \x + \xo 19:1 \xt Joshua 20:1-9\x*  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsunga na chenlut tengu leh, nang hon hiche gamsung chu chenna dinga thum naso diu ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia chu Pakaiyin napehnau gamsung chu khopi thum naso diu, hiche khopi jousea chu lampi nasem lut cheh diu, nalah uva konna koi tobang mithat auma ahileh, ama chu hiche sunga chu jamlut a kihuhdoh thei ding ahi.  
\v 4 Mikhat touvin kidoupi beiya, khat chu amoh tha khah tah a ahileh, khopi khat pen pen achu jamlut a kihihuh hing thei ahi.  
\v 5 Tekah nan, mikhat chu asopipa toh gamlah lama thing phuh dinga akon doh’a thing aphuh laitah a aheicha lap chu aki khodoh a, asopipa chu akhokhah jeng tah’a ahileh, aheicha chun asopi chu akhokhah a thina atokhah’a ahileh, mithat khapa chu khopi thum holah a khat pen pena jamlut a ahinkho aki huhdoh ding ahi.  
\v 6 Chule kihuhdohna dinga khopi chu agamlat behseh a ahileh, akahlah a phula thei khat touvin ahin delkhuma atha jeng thei ahi. Hinlah mithat khapa chun akidoupi hilouvin, khutsoi jeh a atha khah ahi.  
\v 7 Hitobang akon kiven doh theina ding chun, keiman naheng uva khopi thum sem uvin kati ahi.  
\v 8 Pakai, Pathen'in napului, napalui khang uva pat napehsau gamsung hi akehlet ding, agam sung hi aboncha napeh doh diu  
\v 9 chuteng nang hon khopi thum nalhendoh bediu ahi. (Chingthei tah a kathupeh nangaiyuva Pakai, Pathen nangailut uva alampi nacheuva ahileh Aman hiche gam pumpi hi napeh diu ahi).  
\v 10 Hitia chu nabol uva ahileh, Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau hiche gamsunga hi mona beihela thina umlou ding ahi. Chuteng monabei ho thina jal'a mo nachan lou diu ahitai.  
\v 11 Hinlah koitobang khat chun asopi ahot bola, chang lhih jinga aum a, adel khum jenga ahileh, hiche tolthatpa chu khopi ho lah a khat pena chu jamlut a kisel jeng thei ahi.  
\v 12 Chuteng upa chensge chu kon uva mithat pa chu khopi sunga aga hol doh diu, ama hon aga mudoh diu amapa chu phulahna a ahin lhut diu, athina ding chan gotna apeh uva, thina achansah diu ahi.  
\v 13 Tolthatpa chunga chu lainatna ima nanei lou diu ahi! Hichu Israel mite lah a konna thisan sona chu nasuh bei diu; hichu nangho dinga aphalama pang ding joh ahi.   
\s1 Adih a thutan khohsah ding  
\p
\v 14 Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gam sung nalhu tengu leh nanei nagou hou, napu napa teu va pat gamgi song kitung ho chu khat jeng cha jong nabodoh lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 19:14 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:17\x*   
\p
\v 15 Themmona jouse lah a konna mikhat sehseh in themmo thu aseiya konna, adang khat chu themmonamoh chansah lou diu ahi. Hitobang chu hettohsah mini ham mithum ham ahitenglehbou themmo kichan sah bep ding ahi. \x + \xo 19:15 \xt Minbu 35:30; Danbu Ni Na 17:6; Matt 18:16; Jn 8:17; 2 Crth 13:1; 1 Tim 5:19; Heb 10:28\x*  
\v 16 Midang khat chu muda man meimeiya konna adih louva bol jeng louding, hettohsah tothoa doumah a abolthei louding,  
\v 17 chule mini chu akidouva ahileh anigela Pakai angsung leh thempu ho masang leh thutan vaihom ho henga hung cheh ding ahi.  
\v 18 Chutengleh thutan vaihom hon achan chin thu chu giltah a akhol diu ahi. Hinlah jou leh nal thua Israel khattou ahehset a ahileh,  
\v 19 Hitobanga ahehsepa chu gotna peh chang ding ahi. Hitobang Thil phalou chu nalah uva konna na suhmangdiu ahi.  
\v 20 Chuteng midang jousen ahin jah sohkeiyuva, kichat nan alhun den diu, nangho jouse lah a thilse kiti him him abol kit tah lou diu ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche hotobang gitlouna ahin koima khoto hih un! Gotna chang dia dan chu, hinkho khela hinkho, mit khela mit, ha khela ha, khut khela khut chule kengphang khela kengphang lah ding ahi. \x + \xo 19:21 \xt Potdohbu 21:23-25; Thempu Dan 24:19,20; Matt 5:38\x*   
\c 20  
\s1 Galsat miho dinga dan kisem ho  
\p
\v 1 Nagal miteu toh kisat dinga nakon doh tengu leh, sakol ahin kangtalai, nanghoa sanga tamjo namu diu, hinlah nakichat lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu nangho Egypt gamsunga konna nahinpui doh'pau Pakai, Pathen'in naumpi jing uve!  
\v 2 Galmun nalhun masang kahseuva, nalah uva thempupa chu mipi jouse masang lama namakai sah diu ahi.  
\v 3 Chule mipi henga thu asei ding, Vo Israel te ngaiyun! Kichatna jong neihih un, ajeh chu tunia nangho nacheuva amaho khu naga kisatpi diu ahi! Nagal miteu kichat nan kihot hih unlang, gin jong nagin loudiu ahi.  
\v 4 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in nangho dinga gal asat ding! Na masang lam uva lamkai jing ding, galjona nachan diu ahi!  
\v 5 Chuphat leh gal vaipoa pang hon mipi henga hitia hi asei diu ahi. Koiham inthah tungdoh a thenso louva koi? Nalah uva hitobang mihem chu auma ahileh, ama chu galmun'a thiden jeng thei ahi. Athiden khah tah’a ahileh, a in chu midang dinga thensona um ding ahi.  
\v 6 Lengpi lei laiya natonga lengpi thei tepkha lou koiham? Amapa jong chu inlama kile jeng thei ahi. Achuti louva ahileh galmun'a thina ato jeng thei, alengpi lei jeng jong midang chan lo ding ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche bang chun pasal koi tobang khat chu jinei dinga kigosa dem a umta, ahinlah jinei loulai koi ham? Ama jong chu in kilea jinei thei ahi. Ajeh chu galmun'a thina nachan'a naji ding nu chu midang chang jeng thei ahi.  
\v 8 Chule sepai vaihom natonga pang hon mipi henga hitia hi asei nah lai diu ahi. Meidoi, kichase um em? Aumleh in a kile hen, ajeh chu midang asuh meidoilo ding ahi, tia aseidiu ahi.  
\v 9 Sepai vaihom natonga pangho chun sepai ho henga hitia chu asei chaisohkei tengu leh, aloi loiya lamkai alhendoh diu ahi.  
\v 10 Chule khopi khat nabulhu konu leh, amasan hiche khopi chu ki champi din tem un.  
\v 11 Hiche khopi chun natepnau ahin ngaiyuva, kelkotpi chu nahonpeh uva ahileh, na vaihomna noiyuva umdiu, nakinu bollea pang diu ahi.  
\v 12 Ahinlah kicham ding gel louva kidoupi ding joh ageluva ahileh, khopi chu nabulu tei ding ahi.  
\v 13 Chuteng Pakai, Pathen'in hiche khopi chu nangho khut a ahin pehlut ding, na chemjam'uva pasal jouse natha diu ahi.  
\v 14 Hinlah numei le chapang, thilkeo ho nakikoi khom diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in khopi sunga konna chu nopsa tah a na manchah diuva napeh'u ahitai.  
\v 15 Nachen nauva konna gamla tah a um khopi ho, hitia chu nabol sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 16 Pakai, Pathen'in napeh nau hiche khopi chengsea chu naum tengu leh, ahing thei jouse nasuh gam diu ahi.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in naseipeh bang uva, Hit mite, Amor mite, Canan mite, Periz mite, Hiv mite chule Jebus mite hijongleh abonchauva nasuh gam hel diu ahi.  
\v 18 Chutileh hiche mite a konna chu milim doi kisem thu ho a konna nakihei mang thei diu, amaho pathen semthua konna nakiven tup uva, nalhah lutlou diu ahi.  
\v 19 Khopi khat bulu dinga phatsotpi naumkim tengu leh thingphung naphuh lou diu ahi. Aga neuvin, hinlah aphung phuh hih un, thingphung ho chu nagalmiteu ahipoi.  
\v 20 Hinlah thingphung aphachompoi tia nagel houvang chu naphuh uva, khopi sunga galmite toh kidouna galmanchah a naman theiyu ahi\f + \fr 20:20 \ft \f*.   
\c 21  
\s1 Toltha jeh a dan  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, Pathen'in napeh'u nachennau gamsunga chu thise khat tou auma, ahivanga hiche thise chu koitha pen ham ti, aki hedoh thei lou aum a,  
\v 2 hitobang dinmun chu aum khah tah a ahileh, na upateu leh vaihom natong chengse chu hung diu, nakhopiu leh akim vel'a khopi chengse chu phatah atetoh sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia chu abol diu thise tohpa umna a konna chu, khopi akinaipi pen chu mo kichan ding ahi. Bong ala khat lou natong kha loulai hichu agakai diu ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche mochanga khopi sung mite chun, bongla chu phaicham lah khat a ahin kai diu, hiche phaicham chu lou natohnaa kimang khalou hi ding, phaicham mun'a chu bongla gol chu angong chang aheboh diu ahi.  
\v 5 Chuteng Levi thempuho abonchauva ama sang lama hung masa diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in amaho chu akin natong dinga alhen dohsa ahin, Levi thempu ho thusah bang banga kinopmona leh kinah boutam jouse aboncha thu chaina um ding ahi.  
\v 6 Thisepa umna toh kinaina mun'a bongla kithana mun'a chu, khopi sunga upaho jousen twiya akhut akisop cheh diu ahi.  
\v 7 Hichu amaho dinga hettohsahnaa pang ding, “Keiho khut a konna hiche thise hi thisan kiso ahipoi, thisan kiso pet jeng jong kamu hih hel uve,” tia seina diu ahi.  
\v 8 O Pakai, nangman nahuhdohsa nami Israel mite hi ngaidam tan, hiche themmona thisan kisona ho jal'in nami Israel te chunga lethuhna neihih helin, thisan kiso jal'a amaho chunga lethuhna achan nalou dinga, taona anei peh teitei diu ahi.  
\v 9 Hitia chu nangman jong mona beihela thisan kiso na chung changa konna Pakai, mitmua adih a natohna chu nabol tengu leh suhtheng najong nanei diu ahi.   
\s1 Numei kimanho thu  
\p
\v 10 Namel mateu toh gal kisat dinga nakon doh tengu leh Pakai, Pathen'in na melmateu chu nangho henga ahinpeh doh khah tah’a ahileh, nangman jong amaho chu gal hinga nahin kai ding ahi.  
\v 11 Chule hiche gal hing lah a konna chu numei mel-hoitah nakimu doh’uva ahileh, nangmhon jong hiche numei chu naji diuva na kipui jeng theiyu ahi.  
\v 12 Chuteng hiche numei chu nangho inlama nahin puidiu, asam jouse natan peh diu chule atin jouse jong natan mui peh diu ahi.  
\v 13 Hiche numei nu jong chun soh kivonna chu akoiya, nangho insunga chu cheng jing ding lhani jen anu leh apa pul adou ding ahi. Hitia chu nangho jong numeinu henga na galut diu, nangho jong ama dia ajipa nahi thei diu, nupa naum thei diu ahi.  
\v 14 Amanu chunga hi lungkim louna nanei uva ahileh, nang hon jong amanu chu achena nom chana nasol jeng theiyu ahi. sum leh paiya jong najoh doh thei lou diu chule soh ki bolna bang banga jong nabol louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon amanu hi na luppi sau ahitai.   
\s1 Chapa tah ho goulo  
\p
\v 15 Koitobang pasal khat chun numei ji ni akop a, khatnu adeiya khatnu vang chu adeimo joh’a, ahivanga anigel lhona cha ahin lhon tah a, adeimo nu chun cha pasal ahin khat tah a ahileh,  
\v 16 ajipa chun kho nunga achapa te thil leh lo ahin hoppeh nikho tengleh, adeimo johnu chapa sanga chu adeinu chapa chu gel khohna aneiya langnei na jong anei thei louding, apeng masa chu apeng masa bang bang abol thou thou ding ahi.  
\v 17 Adeimo johnu chapa chu achapa lah a atah pen ahi tia aphondoh ding, anei agou jouse lah a chan nia tam joa apeh ding ahi. Ajeh chu ama dia chapa masapen ahin, mi-upa chan ding chu achansah thou thou ding ahi.   
\s1 Sei ngailou chapa  
\p
\v 18 Chapa khat touvin Pakai thungai lou chule anu, apa thu jong ngai louva doumah jenga achona ahileh,  
\v 19 Hiche chapa chu anu leh apan jong khopi kelkot lama, thutan vaihom ho henga ahin puilut jeng lhon ding ahi.  
\v 20 Chuteng anu leh apan jong hiche ka chapa hi doumah jeng aboldoh tan chule kathu lhon jong angai hih hel in, milop tah le phatseh a jukhamnaa hinkho mang jeng ahitai, ati lhon ding ahi.  
\v 21 Chutengleh hitobang miphalou chu khopi sunga cheng mipi ho chun songa aselih jeng diu ahi. Hiche hi Israel pum pin amu sohkei uva, kichaa umdiu ahi.   
\s1 Dan dang dang ho  
\p
\v 22 Mihem khat touvin thina chan gotna pehna thei chonset a alhah khah tah a, amapa chu tha teitei ding ahi tah leh, ama chu thing chunga konna na khai lih jeng theiyu ahi.  
\v 23 Amavang hiche na khai lihpau chu khovah chana na khai den thei lou diu, nakho vahsah ngei ngeiyuva ahileh nang hon Pakai, Pathen'in nagoulo dinga napeh nau gamsung nasuh boh'u ahitan, hijeh achu nakho vahsah louhel diu ahi. \x + \xo 21:23 \xt Gal 3:13\x*   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 Na sopi bongchal ham khat tou avah mang na mua ahileh, hichu nakimu mosah lou diu, don-nahsah mo’a na koi lou diu, amavang namu chan uchu nasopi henga nahin kailut joh diu ahi. \x + \xo 22:1 \xt Potdohbu 23:4,5\x*  
\v 2 Hiche gancha neipa chu nangma inlam toh kigam lha a um ahia, achenna nahet lou uva ahileh agancha chu nang hon na inlam uva nahin kai diu, aneipa na sopipan ahung hol kahsea na ventup peh diu ahung hol tengleh phate chaa na lepeh diu ahi.  
\v 3 Asangan ham khat namu tah ujongleh hitia chu nabol diu, asangkhol ham namu ujongleh hiti ma achu nabol peh diu ahi. Ipi thil le lo hijongleh nang hon nasopi thil namu khah tah’uva ahileh na le peh cheh cheh diu, hitia chu nakithopi diu ahi.  
\v 4 Na sopi khat sangan ham, bongchal ham khat chu lampia alhusa namu khah’uva ahileh, hichu napanpi tei diu ahi. Na sopi gancha alhua chu na phoh doh peh diu, nahuhdoh diu ahi.  
\v 5 Chule nalah’uva numeiyin pasal chunga kaisa akivonna ponsil chu kivonnaa aman thei louhel ding, hitobanga chon chan chu Pakai, Pathen dinga thet umtah ahi.  
\v 6 Vabu hamkhat chu na tokhah’uva hichu tollham ham thing chung ham khat a um, vabu sunga chu atwiham anou ham khat chu vapin aop khum lai ahileh, hichu anousen puma namat thauva nasuh gam loudiu ahi.  
\v 7 Ahinlah vapi chu nadel mang'uva ahileh, anou chengse chu nakilo thei diu ahi, achutileh phat theina jong nachan diu chule nangho dinga hinkho sotnaa pang ding ahi.  
\v 8 Chule nang hon in thah nasah teng ujongleh, bilha nunga konna mi akhih lhahna louding, thisan jal'a themmona achuhna lou dinga, bilha gol jousea aki-tanden nading nasem peh diu ahi.  
\v 9 Chule na lengpi lei laiyuva muchi ni natu kop thei lou diu, muchi ni natu kop’uva ahileh hichu munthenga todoh dinga ki sang thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 22:9 \xt Thempu Dan 19:19\x*  
\v 10 Bongchal ham sangan ham khat chu, lou kainaa naman kop thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 11 Tupat kihel leh pat chom kihel khom jong mangchaa, kisilna a naman thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 12 Na kivonnau ding na sangkhol chol'u mong ning lam lia chu, pat hol khat cheh naba diu ahi. \x + \xo 22:12 \xt Minbu 15:37-41\x*   
\s1 Jonthanhoina chunga dan kisem  
\p
\v 13 Pasal khat chun numei aji dinga akipuija, alup khompia chujou le numeinu chu athet bol jeng louding ahi.  
\v 14 Hiche numei nu chu jachat na leh jumna dimset’a alha jenga, hiche numei nu chu kaji dingin kapuiyin kaluppin ahileh, athenglou mitoh lum khomsa ahitai, ti asei khah ngei ngeiya ahileh,  
\v 15 Hiche numei nu chu anu leh apan jong khopi sung lam kelkot’a thutan vaihom ho henga chu apui lut lhon ding, amanu hi atheng mong mong ahi nai ti, photchetna aga bol lhon ding ahi.  
\v 16 Chuteng numeinu pan jong hitia hi aphondoh ding, hiche pasalpa toh'hin kicheng ding mong monga kana pehdohsa chu ahitai. Ahinlah pasalpan vang muda in solmang ding agoe, tia asei ding ahi.  
\v 17 Chugoh keu hilouvin, amanu chunga hin jachatna tampi alhunsah in, “Hiche nachanu chunga hin nungah thengsel ahina ima kamu doh tapoi,” tia asei ding ahi. Chuteng apan jong ka chanu hi nungah theng mong mong ahi, tiphotchetna hicheng hi ahiye tia asei ding, ajeh chu hitobang photchetna dinga chu numeinu anu leh apan jong khopi kelkot thutan vaihom ho, henga aphondoh lhkonna pon asil lhon ding ahi.  
\v 18 Chujou tengleh khopi sunga upahon jong, hiche pasalpa chu amat uva ajep diu ahi.  
\v 19 Chule pasalpa chu dangka shekel jakhat a aleu sah diu, hiche dangka shekel jakhat chu nu ngahnu pa chang ding ahi. Ajeh chu hiche pasalpa chun Israel nungah khat aminset sah jeh ahi. Chule numeinu jong jia anei ding, ahinkho lhum keiya dinga ajia pang ding ahi.  
\v 20 Amavang nungahnu chunga chu, athenge tiphotchetna aum tah louva ahileh,  
\v 21 Amaho chun hiche nungahnu chu apa in kot phunga konna ahin kai doh diu, chuteng khopi sunga cheng josuen amanu chu songa aselih jeng diu ahi. Ajeh chu hiche numeinu chu chondih louna mangchan aki ngolsah tan, Israel insunga, apa insunga hiti chun ana chon tan ahi. Hitobanga chon chan phalou jouse chu nasuh dih jing diu ahi.  
\v 22 Chule pasal khat chun pasal dang jikhat chu aluppi khah tah a ahileh, numeinu ahin pasal pa ahin anigel lhkonna thina chang lhon ding ahi. Hitobang achu Israel sunga thil dihlou chonna jouse nasuh bei diu ahi.  
\v 23 Chule khopi sunga nungah thengsel khat chu pasal khat touvin, kholai dung ham khat a chu aki timatpi jeng tah a ahileh,  
\v 24 Hitobanga chon teni chu ani lhkonna khopi sung lam kelkot phunga nahin kaidoh diu, ani lhona songa na selih jeng diu ahi. Ajeh chu numeinu jong chu apanpi thei mi tampi kho sunga aum in, ahinlah ama peng doh louhel in aum in, pasal pan jong aheng akom chu asuh set jeng ahin, hitobang chondan dih lou jouse hi nalah uva konna nasuh thengsel diu ahi.  
\v 25 Hinlah nungah khat chu mitoh lumkhomsa ama chu gamlah a pasal khat touvin ana lupkhom pia, pasalpa chun numeinu chu tha guma amat chah a akitimat pia ahileh, hiche dinmun'a vang hi pasal pa bouseh thina chang ding ahi.  
\v 26 Hitobang dinmun thilsoh chung chang hi, numeinu ima kilo theilou ding ahi. Ajeh chu numeinu chunga hin thina chan gotna pehna ding aum pon, pasal khat in asopipa lam ajot lutna thina achansah tobang ahi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu hiche numeinu chu pasal pan gamlah a adel khum a akitimatpi ahin, numei khangdong nun jong kithopi ding ngaicha in apeng in, hinlah koiman ajah peh lou ahi.  
\v 28 Chule pasal khat touvin nungah theng tah khat chu alup pi khah tah a, thahat husana amanu chu akitimat pia alup pettah lhon akimat doh a ahileh, \x + \xo 22:28 \xt Potdohbu 22:16,17\x*  
\v 29 Hiche pasalpa, nungahnu kitimatpi pa chun numeinu pa chu dangka shekel somnga apeh ding ahi, ajeh chu amapa chun numeinu chu akitimatpisa ahitan, a hinkho lhum keiya ji dinga aki puiya hinkho aman ding ahi.  
\v 30 Koitobang pasal khat chun, apa jinu chu jia agel thei louhel ding chule apa ji khat chu anih aho peh thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 22:30 \xt Thempu Dan 18:8; 20:11; Danbu Ni Na 27:20\x*   
\c 23  
\s1 Mijalah a konna pampei ding ho  
\p
\v 1 Pasal khat chu til lahsa leh hinpi kitansa ahileh pampaiya um ahi. Amapa chu Pakai hou’in sung kikhopna mun'a hunglut thei talou ding ahi.  
\v 2 Chule nalah uva konna noti cha jeng jong Pakai houbung sunga jao thei louding, khang som chan geiya noti chanu—chapa te ho chu khat jeng cha jong, Pakai houbung sunga lha thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia chu Ammon mite ahin, Moab mite ani lhona Pakai houbung sunga lha theilou diu ahi. Khangsom chan geiya Pakai houbung sunga lutthei lou diu, hichu imatih chana ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:3 \xt Nehemiah 13:1,2\x*  
\v 4 Ajeh chu nangho Egypt gamsunga konna nahung potdoh uchun, lampi dunga changlhah leh twisih neo chan jong nana lamto pouvin ahi. Amavang Mesopotomia gamsunga Pethor mun'a Beor chapa Balaam chu ana lamhil uvin, achena mun chana dingin aga thah kit un ahi. \x + \xo 23:4 \xt Minbu 22:1-6\x*  
\v 5 Ahinlah Pakai, Pathen'in Balaam thusei chu anahsah pon, Pakai, Pathen'in Balaam henga gaosapna aneiyin, chuin nangma ding’in phatthei nan aheidoh tai, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in nangma nangai lun ahi. \x + \xo 23:5 \xt Minbu 23:7—24:9\x*  
\v 6 Imatih chana nang hon amaho chamlen nading leh ahaosatna diuva lampi ima nasem doh peh thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 7 Amavang Edom mite kiti nolna nanei thei lou diu, nangho dinga na sopiu ahi. Egypt mite jong thetbolna nanei lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gamsunga ana khopemsa nahiuve.  
\v 8 Edom le Egypt mite chengse vang khang thum alhin tengleh, Pakai houbung sunga lhathei diu ahi.   
\s1 Galkon ho umdan  
\p
\v 9 Chule namelmateu toh gal kisat dinga nakon doh tengu leh, nangho jong thilse jousea konna na kikangse diu ahi.  
\v 10 Ajeh chu jankah chun namite lah a khat touvin botwi hinche doh taleh, amapa chu ngahmun'a konna pam lama paidoh a um jeng ding, ngahmun sung kitia chu hungvah lut kit louding ahitai.  
\v 11 Nilhah lam tengleh vang ama chu twiya ki sutheng ding, nilhum lam teng ngahmun sunga hung lut thei ding ahi.  
\v 12 Ngahmun polama chu ehkul khat nasem diu, hiche mun'a chu eh-thaa na cheji diu ahi.  
\v 13 Nagal manchah'u poh lah a chu lei-tuhna thei khat naki poh jing diu, ehtha dinga naum tengu leh hiche lei laina achu na leiyuva naeh nathah diu, na thah chai tengu leh hichu leiya na le vuh diu ahi.  
\v 14 Pakai, Pathen'in nangho nahuhdoh diu leh ngahmun'a chu nangho huhdoh dinga um jing ahin, hiche naum nau ngahmun chu kisutheng jing ding ahi. Chutileh Pakai, Pathen'in naum nau ngamun'a chu thil thenglou ima amudoh louding, nanghoa konna kihei mang louva na umpi jing diu ahi.   
\s1 Dan dang ho  
\p
\v 15 Aneipa a konna hung jamdoh soh chu, nang hon aneipa chu namoh peh jeng thei lou'u ahi.  
\v 16 Ama toh chun nachen khom jing diu, hoilai mun'a hijongleh na khopi sung'uva chu aman adeilhenna mun pena chu nachen sah jeng diu ahi. Chule hiche soh chu nang hon jong achunga gimna ima nalhun sah thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 17 Chule Israel insunga konna numei khat jeng cha jong noti a kichem chavei um thei louding ahi. Hitobanga chu Israel insung’a pasal hon jong milimsemthu doia neiya notia kisa chavei um theilou ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:17 \xt Thempu Dan 19:29\x*  
\v 18 Ucha kithana man le notia konna man chu Pakai, Pathen henga nahin choidiu nato doh thei lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu hiche teni hi Pakaiya dinga thet umtah ahi.  
\v 19 Na sopi khat chu sum thoiya nabat sah theilou diu, napeh'u jongleh hichu athoiya napeh thei lou diu, ipi hijongleh aneh chan chu bat a ima um thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 23:19 \xt Potdohbu 22:25; Thempu Dan 25:36,37; Danbu Ni Na 15:7-11\x*  
\v 20 Amavang hitobang chu gamchom miho chunga nabol thei diu, ahinlah nasopi kiti pou chunga athoi kiti napeh thei lou diu ahi. Athoi nalah lou uva ahileh tua nachen lutna diu mun'a khu Pakai, Pathen'in phattheina lhingsela naboh diu ahi.  
\v 21 Pakai, Pathen adia thil khat peh ding natiuva ahileh hichu napeh ding tengu leh lungkihna ima nanei louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in nangho chunga ahin del khum jeng ding, napeh lou uva ahileh hichu nangho dinga chonset a kisim ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:21 \xt Minbu 30:1-16; Matt 5:33\x*  
\v 22 Kitepna nanei lou uva ahileh hichu chonset a ki sim lou ahi.  
\v 23 Nakam a nasei dohsau khat chu nabol doh tei nadin ki hambol jing uvin, ajeh chu nangho jong Pakai, Pathen henga kitepna nei puma nakam'uva napotdohsah'u ahitai.  
\v 24 Chule nangho lengpi leiya nachen lut tengu leh nadei chan'u naneh jeng theiyu ahi. Ahinlah neocha jeng jong nasakhao-dip sung'uva naki het lut louhel diu ahi.  
\v 25 Na heng nakom pau loulaiya nagache lut tengu leh achangvui chu na kisi theiyu ahi. Amavang, koite mangcha a naheng nakompa changvui chu na-at thei louhel diu ahi.   
\c 24  
\s1 Jida chunga dan  
\p
\v 1 Pasal in numei chu ji dinga akipui teng, hiche numeinu chu achung’a themmona ana um khah tah a, ajipa chu alung lhaisah jou tah louva ahileh, ajipan jong kidana lekha phatah asut ding hichu akichoi sah a, a insunga konna asoldoh ding ahi. \x + \xo 24:1 \xt Matt 5:31; 19:7; Mk 10:4\x*  
\v 2 Chuteng numeinu chu che a, pasal dang khat toh gakicheng thei ahi.  
\v 3 Chule hiche ajipa jong chun numeinu chunga chu, lungkim louna aneikhah a ahileh, amasa ngaiya banga kidana lekha asut peh ding akichoi sah a a-insunga konna asoldoh jeng ding ahi. Ahinlah aji luipa chu ana thi khah tah leh,  
\v 4 Ama nu dinga ajimasa pa aluipa chun, ji dinga aki lepui thei tah louding ahi. Ajeh chu hitobang thil ho hi Pakaiya dia thet umtah ahin, Pakai, Pathen'in napeh nau gamsunga hitobang thilpha lou aboh ho hi na umsah loudiu ahi.  
\v 5 Pasal khat chu ajinei thah ahileh, amapa chu galsat mia panda hen chule natoh dang jong bolsah louding ahi. Kum khat lhingset ain mun'a um ding, alungdei pennu chutoh noma umkhom ding ahi.  
\v 6 Chule koiman chang sum man, sumhei song man hijongleh thil dang khat toh kisaiya bat a alah thei louding ahi. Hichu alah khah tah a ahileh, mihem hinkho thil bat mana alah ahitai.  
\v 7 Koi hileh asopi Israel mi khat tou aguh a aguh pattah akimat doh’a ahileh, hiche ami guhdoh chu soh banga abol tah a, aki joh mang jenga, hitobang gucha chu thina nachan sah diu, hiche ho chu nalah uva konna na suhmang diu ahi. \x + \xo 24:7 \xt Potdohbu 21:16\x*  
\v 8 Chule phah natna chung chang thudol ahin, Levi thempu hon nahilna bang uva nabolna diuvin limgeh chan um uvin, keima thupeh banga nang hon jong nabol doh theina diu ahi. \x + \xo 24:8 \xt Thempu Dan 13:1—14:54\x*  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Egypt gamsunga konna nahung potdoh uva Pakai, Pathen'in Miriam abolna chung thudol achun limgeh chan um un. \x + \xo 24:9 \xt Minbu 12:10\x*  
\v 10 Na sopi khat touvin thil khat bat a alah khah tah’a ahileh, nangho jong ama insunga chu namoh lut lou diu chule hiche hi akhela kaki lah ding ahi, tiajong thil ho chu nalhen thei lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 24:10 \xt Potdohbu 22:26,27\x*  
\v 11 Chule nangho in polama naum diu, nangho thil bat a lapa vang chu insunga lut a, nabat sahna diuva thil na lepeh diu pen chu ahin choidoh diu ahi.  
\v 12 Nangho thil bat a lapa chu mivaicha neilal ahi khah tah leh, nang hon achunga asea lethuhna nanei lou diu ahi.  
\v 13 Nisa lhum tengleh hiche athil bat man chu na le sah diu, chuteng aman aponsil achol pen chu lupna a aman ding, nang hon jong phatthei nachan tei diu ahi. Hichu Pakai, Pathen maiya thil dihtah ahi.  
\v 14 Soh thalah khat chu nasuh gim louhel diu, hitobanga vaichaa hinkho mang mihem chu, na gamsung'uva cheng nasopi mikhat tou hi nante. \x + \xo 24:14 \xt Thempu Dan 19:13\x*  
\v 15 Hitobang mihem chu naki thalah nikho mamau nilhum masang a, atohman chu napeh diu ahi. Ama chu mivaicha tah ahin, athaman chu anga jing ding, a chuti louva ahileh ama a konna lhasetna hunglhung thei ding, aman jong nangho douna jal'a Pakai henga thu hinsei in tin, hichu nangho dinga chonset ahi.  
\v 16 Chule mipa ho chu achate jal'a thina ki chansah louhel diu, achate jal'a jong apate thina ki chansah louding ahi. Amavang koi hileh ama ama chonset jal'a bou chu thina kichan sah ding ahi. \x + \xo 24:16 \xt 2 Lengte 14:6; 2 Thusimbu 25:4; Ezekiel 18:20\x*  
\v 17 Khopem mikhat leh chagapa chung thua adihna thutan chu nahei loudiu, meithai ho ponsil jong thilbat mana nalahpeh thei lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 24:17 \xt Potdohbu 23:9; Thempu Dan 19:33,34; Danbu Ni Na 27:19\x*  
\v 18 Ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gamsunga soh changsa nahiuvin, Pakai, Pathen a konna lhatdamsa ihiuve, ti nasuh mil lou diu, hiche pen tah jeh a chu keiman bol in tia ka thupeh chu nabol jeng diu ahi.  
\v 19 Lou laiya chang at a nakon tengu leh, lou laiya changpal nadalhah thei lou diu, changpal le akhai athang ho jong nanung lo thei lou diu ahi. Hiche ho chu chaga ho leh nubei, pabei meithai ho ding ahi. Chuteng Pakai, Pathen'in nabol natoh jouseuva konna phattheina dimset naboh diu ahi. \x + \xo 24:19 \xt Thempu Dan 19:9,10; 23:22\x*  
\v 20 Olive thing na phuh lhuh tengu leh, avel vel'a nivei chang naphuh lou diu, mivaicha, chaga, nulou, palou ho dinga nakhen tei diu ahi.  
\v 21 Lengpi leiya lengpiga naki chop khom teng ujongleh, nadalhah nasa nung'uva akhai chengse chu na donlou diu ahi. Ajeh chu chaga, mivaicha, meithai nulou, palou ho ding ahiye.  
\v 22 Ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gamsunga ana soh changsa chu nahiuvin, hichu nagel doh jing diu chule hichengse hi nabol diuva ka thupeh nahi.   
\c 25  
\p
\v 1 Mihem khat le khat akinah a, akiheh lhona ahileh, thutan vaihom hon achungthu lhon atan peh diu, themmonanei lou chu them achansah diu, themmonanei chu themmo achansah diu ahi.  
\v 2 Chule themmo changpa chu voh ding alhah khah tah a ahileh, thutan vaihompa chun themmo changpa chu alupsah ding, them changpa mitmua chu athemmona jat dungjuiya avoh ding ahi.  
\v 3 Hitobang mihem chu molsom li chan thoh thei ding, hiche kal achu thoh thei louding ahi. Ajeh chu amapa chu miho masang'in kijep jep jing tahen lang hileh, aki neosah behseh jeh achu muset a naum thei diu ahi. \x + \xo 25:3 \xt 2 Crth 11:24\x*   
\s1 Upa jinu vetpeh thu  
\p
\v 5 Chule insunga pasal ni chengkhom teni chu khat joh sang chu chapa beiya thina ato khah tah a ahileh, athipa jinu chu pasal dang angsunga chea jinei thei louding ahi. Amavang numei nu jipa sopipa vang chu hiche nu angsunga chu, che ding amanu chu ajia aki puiding ahi. Asopi ji khat kive kol bang banga avet kol ding ahi. \x + \xo 25:5 \xt Matt 22:24; Mk 12:19; Lk 20:28\x*  
\v 6 Hichea chapa ahin masat pen chu, a sopipa athi tasa chu khanggui jop mat nadinga, Israel insunga ama minchu suhmanga um louding ahi.  
\v 7 Ahinlah adam nalaiya sopipa chun athipa jinu chu deilouva, ji dinga akipui nom tah louva ahileh, asopipa jinu jong che ding kelkot phung lama thutan vaihom ho henga hitia hi agasei ding ahi. Ka jipa sopipan athisa asopipa hi Israel insunga amin ajop nom tapon ahi. \x + \xo 25:7 \xt Ruth 4:7,8\x*  
\v 8 Chuteng hiche khopi sunga upa chengse chu, cheuva amapa kom'a chu agasei diu ahi. Amavang hichan nunga jong ‘Keiman hichenu hi kaji dinga ka kipui louding ahi’ tia asei nah laiya,  
\v 9 Chule asopi athipa ji nun jong anailut ding, amapa chu akengchot asut peh ding, amai chang chil aset den ding, hitia hi ahenga aseipeh ding, ‘Pasal koi hijongleh asopipa khela insung khat sem doh nomlou chu hitia hi kibol ding ahi,’ tia asei ding ahi.  
\v 10 Amavang chu amin Israel insung ahi tia kisei ding, chule akengchot kisut lhah peh pa insung tiajong kihe ding ahi.   
\s1 Dan dang phabep  
\p
\v 11 Pasal khat leh khat chu akinah a, pasal dang khatpa jinu ham chun khatpa a konna chu ajipa chu huhdoh ding agot a ahileh, hiche nu chun anai lut a khatpa chu ahinpia amat a ahe peh jenga ahileh,  
\v 12 Hiche numei chu akhut natan peh diu, lung sa-ihna beihel a naum diu ahi.  
\v 13 Chule nasakhao sung jeng'uva jong thil tena ni napoh kop lou diu, khat alen khat aneo tia napoh kop lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 25:13 \xt Thempu Dan 19:35,36\x*  
\v 14 Nangho insung jenga jong thil tena alenkhat ahin, aneokhat hiteni chu nakoi tha lou diu ahi.  
\v 15 Thil agih tena achoma nakoi diu, aboncha bukimsel ding, hitia chu najui kim sohkeiyuva ahileh, Pakai, Pathen'in nangho nachennau gamsung jousea phat theina lhingset naboh diu ahi.  
\v 16 Ajeh chu hitia thil adih louva bola natohna jouse chu Pakai, Pathen dinga thet umtah ahi.   
\s1 Amalekte kisuh gam  
\p
\v 17 Nangho Egypt gamsunga konna nahung pot laiyuva, Amalek miten ichan geiya nabol gimu hitam, nalam lhah nauva nabolna jouseu chu nagel doh jing diu ahi. \x + \xo 25:17 \xt Potdohbu 17:8-14; 1 Samuel 15:2-9\x*  
\v 18 ama hon nalam lhah laitah un nadel khum jeng uvin, na chol laitah uva ichan geiya gim genthei a nalhau hitam? Pathen ging louhel in nachung uva na atong tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in nangho choldamna nape tauvin, nakim vel'uva namel mateu jousea konna nacholdo sah diu, Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau nagoulo nadiu mun'a nachen lut tengu leh, nang hon jong vannoi leiset a Amalek mite chenna jouse chu na suhmang hel diu ahi, tichu nagel doh jing diu ahi.   
\c 26  
\s1 Gamasa thilto  
\p
\v 1 Nangho Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsunga nachenlut tengu leh,  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen'in napeh'u, nalou lhosoh-gau masa a konna phabep khat nakoidoh diu, hichengse chu pucha sunga nakoi khom diu, chuteng Pakai, Pathen'in adeilhenna mun achu nachea'uva naga lhut diu ahi. \x + \xo 26:2 \xt Potdohbu 23:19\x*  
\v 3 Hiche laimun'a thempu natongpa kom'a chu nache uva, hitia hi ahenga nagasei diu ahi. Tunin keiman Pakai, Pathen henga ka phondoh ahitai, ajeh chu Pakai, Pathen'in ipului khang uva pat aki tepna gamsunga keima ka hunglhung tai, tia nasei diu ahi.  
\v 4 Hiteng chule, Thempu pan jong na pocha uchu na doplhah peh diu, hichu Pakai, Pathen maicham maiya nagakoi peh diu ahi.  
\v 5 Nanghon Pakai, Pathen henga hitia hi nasei diu, keima pupa chu Ram mi anahin, hiche mun'a chu khopem ahin, ami jeng jong lhomcha bou ahi. Chomlou kah in Egypt gamsunga nam lentah ahung hidoh tan, ahung hatdoh jeng tan ahileh mihem jeng jong tampi ahung hidoh tan ahi.  
\v 6 Chujouvin Egypt miten ei sugim lheh jeng tauvin, gentheina tin chang eithoh sah uvin, soh le kol in hinkho iman sah uvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin kapu, kapa luiteu khanga pat, Pathen henga chun ka tao un, Pakaiyin ka taonau awgin ajatan ahileh, ka thoh gimna jouseu le gim hesoh a kaumna jouseu amusohkei tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chutah chun Pakaiyin athahat apan in, abanjang thahat apantan, kichat umtah leh melchihna kidang tamtah tothon Egypt gamsunga kon chun Pathen'in eihin puidoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Hichea kon chun eihin pui galkai uvin ahileh, khoiju le bongnoi lonna gamsunga chun ka hung galkai lhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Tun Pakai vetan, nagman nei peh'u leiset gamasa chengse kahin lhut tai. Chutengleh Pakai, Pathen angsunga hi natun doh diu, Pakai, Pathen chu chibai naboh diu ahi.  
\v 11 Pakai, Pathen a konna thilpeh jouse hin kipana nachan sah diu, nangho nahiu vin, Levi mite ahin chule nalah uva hung kholjin miho jouse jaona na kipa sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 12 Chule hopsom pehna dinga, kum thum sunga peh ding dol chengse nasim toh sohkei diu, hichengse chu Levi mite ahin, nulou palou, meithai ho dinga na khindoh ding, na khopi sung'uva cheng jousen aneh uva va sohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 26:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 14:28,29\x*  
\v 13 Chule Pakai, Pathen angsunga nasei diu, ka insunga kon'in ijakai atheng jouse chu ka koidoh sohkei tan ahi. Hiti chun, athil theng jouse akon chun Levi mite, kholjin mi, nulou, palou chule chaga ho leh meithai ho kape tan ahi. Na thupeh abonchan ka subukim sohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 14 Kaboi pet tah jengin jong hopsom ka mangcha hih nai, athenglou dinmun'a kaum laiyin jong hopsom neocha jong ka kilah hih uve, hopsom kiti hi mithi opnan jong thilpeh a kamang khapouvin, keiho hin Pakai thupeh abonchan kajui jingun, nangma thupeh bang banginijakai ka bol kimsohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 15 Na umna muntheng laiya kon chun neihin vetan, chule nami Israel te napehna gamsunga hin phatthei lhingset hin boh tauvin, ajeh chu hiche gamsung hi khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gam ahin, kapu kappa teu khang apat eipeh sau ana hitai, tia nasei ding ahi.   
\s1 Pakai dei lhentum nam  
\p
\v 16 Hijeh chun Pakai, Pathen'in tuni hin nang hon hiche chondan josue hi na jui diuvin nape tauve. Hicheng ho jouse hi nahinkho lhum keiyuva natoh doh nadiuva limgeh chaa naum diu ahi.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu nang hon hiche hi tunia, Pakai thudol'a na phondoh'u ahitan, nangho dia tonsot Pathen ahijingin, ama lampi jinga na lamlhah diu chule achonna dan jouse le athupeh aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 18 Pakaiyin hiti hin aseiyin, na chung chang thua aphongdoh in, nangho hi aman aphondoh banga amite mong mong ama dia lhentum chu nahi diu, athupeh jouse hi nanit bukim sohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 26:18 \xt Potdohbu 19:5; Danbu Ni Na 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; Tit 2:14; 1 Pet 2:9\x*  
\v 19 Chuteng Pakaiyin, asemsa vannoi leiset mite lah a choi-atna dim, jabolna dimset a natun doh diu ahitai. Pakaiyin aseidohsa bang banga nangho hi nam thengte nahi jing diu ahi.   
\c 27  
\s1 Song a dan kisun  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Mose chu Israel upa chengse toh akilhon tan, miho henga hiti hin aseiye. tunia ka thupeh chengse hi aboncha nanit sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen'in napeh nau gamsung nahin jot uva Jordan vadung nahung gal kai tengu leh, song len phabep natun diu hiche songho chu songlou mangchaa abona na loinam sohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:2 \xt Joshua 8:30-32\x*  
\v 3 Hiche song kiphut ho chunga chu Pakaiyin, napu luite hou henga athutepsa banga nagal kai tah jeh uva, Pakai, Pathen'in na pehnau gamsung nalut tengule, dan thu akisei thu chengse aboncha najihlut sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 4 Tunia kathupeh banga Jordan nagal kai tengu leh songho chu naphudoh sohkei diu, Ebal molchunga chu natun doh sohkei diu, hiche songho chu aboncha song-lou mangchaa na loijol namsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche mun'a chu Pakai, Pathen dinga maicham khat natun doh diu, maicham chu song jeng mangchaa nasem diu, songho suhnamna dinga chu thih jeng naman lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:5 \xt Potdohbu 20:25\x*  
\v 6 Pakai, Pathen dinga natun doh'u maicham chu thih manchah jeng hilou ding, hiche maicham chu pumgo thilto todohnaa na manchah diu ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche maicham chunga chu chamna thil jong nakatdoh diu, asa jong chu nang hon naneh jeng diu, Pakai, Pathen angsunga kipah tah a naum diu ahi.  
\v 8 Chuteng danthu jouse hi aboncha kichihsela, hiche song chunga hi najih doh sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 9 Hiti chun Mose jong Levi thempuho jaonan thu aseiyin, Israel insung pumpi henga hiti hin aseiyin. Vo Israel te ngaiyun, tunia pat nangho Pakai, Pathen dinga amite nahi tauve  
\v 10 Ajeh chu nang hon Pakai, Pathen thusei jeng nangai diu, athupeh leh tunia achona dan thupeh chengse aboncha najui kimsohkei diu ahi.   
\s1 Ebal mola kon ki gaosap  
\p
\v 11 Mose’n jong mipi jouse chu aphohsal jengin, aheng uvah hiti hin asei tan ahi.  
\v 12 Jordan vadung nagal kai tengu leh, mipi aboncha phatthei bohna chang dinga aboncha Gerizim molchunga ding den sohkei diu ahi. Simeon ahin, Levi, Judah, Issachar, Joseph chule Benjamin hichengse chu hidiu ahi. \x + \xo 27:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:29; Joshua 8:33-35\x*  
\v 13 Ebal molsang gaosap chansah dinga mipi hijat chu kitang den ding Reuben, Gad, Asher, Zebulun, Dan chule Naphtali ahiuve.  
\v 14 Chuteng Levi miten jong aw-sangtah a aphondoh uva, Israel pumpin hichu ajah sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 15 Chule Pakaiya dia thet um mihem khutsem milim kilha jol ho, guhthima hou ding go ah mi chu apat patna gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi, tia lhangphong tah a asap jal diu, mipin jong hichu adonbut’a Amen! atipeh diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:15 \xt Potdohbu 20:4; 34:17; Thempu Dan 19:4; 26:1; Danbu Ni Na 4:15-18; 5:8\x*  
\v 16 Koi hileh anu le apa jabol lou mihem chu gaosap na chang jeng hen tia asap teng, hichu adonbut uva Amen! atipeh diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:16 \xt Potdohbu 20:12; Danbu Ni Na 5:16\x*  
\v 17 Aheng akom asopi toh agamgi sukeh chan chu gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi. Hichu mipi hon adonbut diu, Amen! ati peh diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:17 \xt Danbu Ni Na 19:14\x*  
\v 18 Lamlhahna dunga mitcho elbai sugim ham, puicha vai ham khat chu gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi. Hiche jong chu mipin adonbut’a, Amen! atipeh diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:18 \xt Thempu Dan 19:14\x*  
\v 19 Kholjin miho leh chaga meithai kikah a thu adih louva tan mihem chu, gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi. Hitia ahinsei teng mipin adonbut’a, Amen! ati sohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:19 \xt Potdohbu 22:21; 23:9; Thempu Dan 19:33,34; Danbu Ni Na 24:17,18\x*  
\v 20 Pasal khat touvin apa jinu chu aluppi khah tah a ahileh, amapa chu gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi. Ajeh chu amapa hin apa jinu nih ahopeh’e atiuleh mipin jong, Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:20 \xt Thempu Dan 18:8; 20:11; Danbu Ni Na 22:30\x*  
\v 21 Ijemtia gancha toh lumkhom aum khah tah ahileh, ama chu gaosapna chang jeng hen, tia asei teng mipin jong, Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:21 \xt Potdohbu 22:19; Thempu Dan 18:23; 20:15\x*  
\v 22 Pasal koi hileh apa sopinu toh lum khom ham, ahilouleh anu chanu toh lumkhom auma ahileh, amapa chu gaosapna chang jeng hen tia asei tengleh, mipin jong Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:22 \xt Thempu Dan 18:9; 20:17\x*  
\v 23 Pasal koi hileh ajinu, nu toh lumkhom auma ahileh ama chu gaosapna chang jeng hen tia asei teng, mipin jong Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:23 \xt Thempu Dan 18:17; 20:14\x*  
\v 24 Mihem koi hijongleh aheng akom'a chenga sopipa aguh a thimtha tapou chu, gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi, tia asei tengleh mipin jong Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi.  
\v 25 Themmona beiya mihem chunga thina chansah dinga sum guh ne mihem chu gaosapna chang jeng ding ahi, tia asei tengleh Amen! tia adonbut diu ahi.  
\v 26 Koi hileh athu seidohsa aboncha tong molso lou chan chu gaosapna achung’a chang ding ahi. Hichu mipi hon abonchauva Amen! tia adonbut sohkei diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:26 \xt Gal 3:10\x*   
\c 28  
\s1 Thunun jeh a phatthei channa  
\p
\v 1 Pakai, Pathen thua nanun jing'uva tuni khoa ka thupeh chengse aboncha najui kimsohkeiyuva ahileh, Pakaiyin vannoi leiset a nam jouse lah a nangho achungnung pena natun diu ahi. \x + \xo 28:1 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:13-17\x*  
\v 2 Pakai, Pathen thusei aboncha nangai jing'uva ahileh, phattheina lhingset nachan diu ahi.  
\v 3 Khopi sung le lou jao lah ajong, phattheina lhingset nachan diu ahi.  
\v 4 Natu nachateu jong phattheina chang jing ding, nalou gasoh jeng ujong phattheina chang ding, nagan chateu jouse jong phattheina chang ding, naganchateu le nasangan teu jouse jong phat theina lhingset chang diu ahi.  
\v 5 Na dip jeng ujong phattheina chang dimset ding, nachang sum buh ujong phattheina chang ding ahi.  
\v 6 Na vailhun navaikon teng ujongleh, phattheina nachan diu ahi.  
\v 7 Nagal mite jouseu Pakaiyin lethuhna aneiya gal alal sah ding, lampi khat a bou hung kon diu ahin, ahinlah lampi sagi jena jam cheh sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 8 Na changpang jong phatthei naboh peh diu, nabol natoh jouseu jong aboncha phatthei naboh peh diu ahi. Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsunga chu phattheina lhingset lhung ding ahi.  
\v 9 Pakai, Pathen thupeh chengse aboncha nanit sohkeiyuva, Ama lam jeng nakat uva ahileh, nangho henga akitepna banga vannoi leiset a nam mite jouse lah a, nam dei lhena natun diu ahi.  
\v 10 Hitia chu nabol tengu leh, namtin vaipin ama hi Pakai jal ahimong’e ti aphot chet diu, namtin vaipin nagin sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 11 Ima jouse bukimsela phatthei naboh diu, nacha na nanao teu jouse, nagancha teu, nalou ga jouseu, napu napa teu khanga pat Pakaiyin asei dohsa kapeh ding ahi, atina gamsunga chu nangho haosatna dimset a naum diu ahi.  
\v 12 Chuteng Pakaiyin agoukholna jouse hin hong doh sohkeiyin tin, kum kihei phat cha ahibanga gotwi hung juntin, natoh jouseu chu aboncha phattheina changsoh hel ding, namtin vaipi ho na neichan batna napeh diu, ahinlah nang hon midanga na batlou diu ahi.  
\v 13 Pakaiyin nangho aluchang lama napansah uva, ameito lam mong monga na pansah louhel diu ahi. Khantouna jeng nahi diu, lhahsuh nan nahin jui louhel diu ahi. Tunia chonna dan thupeh chengse aboncha najui kimsohkeiyuva ahileh, nangho phatthei nachan tei diu ahi.  
\v 14 Tunia ka thupeh chengsea konna hi na kihei mang thei lou diu, jetlam le veilam ani gela na palkeh loudiu, pathen milimsemthu hoa konna naki kangse diu, hiche ho tobang chu najen le louhel diu ahiti, sumil louva nagel doh jing diu ahi.   
\s1 Thunun lou jeh a sapsetna  
\p
\v 15 Nanghon Pakai, Pathen thupeh nahsah louva na koiyuva, tunia keiman ka thupeh leh amahoa konna thupeh chonna dan chengse nabol doh theina diuva chingthei tah’a najui lou uva ahileh, anoiya gaosapna ho hin nalhun den jeng diu ahi.  
\v 16 Na chennau khopi sung ahin loumun hijongleh, gaosapna nachan diu ahi.  
\v 17 Na dip'u ahin, nachangbong goina jeng ujong, gaosapna chang ding ahi.  
\v 18 Na chilhah teu ahin, na leiset ga chung'uva jong gaosapna lhung ding, naganchateu jong pung thei louva, nakelngoi nouteu jong pung be talou ding ahi.  
\v 19 Na vailhun, navai kondoh geiyuva gaosapna nachan diu ahi.  
\v 20 Pakai, Pathen'in nachung uva gaosapna tinchang ahin lhun den ding, kisuh nohphahna, lung-opkaina, chule gimna ijakai jouse keima thupeh chengse nadonse tahlou jeh uva nachung uva hijatpi chu lhung jeng ding ahi.  
\v 21 Na jotna diu gamsunga nachen lut kahseh uva Pakai, Pathen'in nachung uva hise natna jat kim nachung uva alhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 22 Pakaiyin natna ki dang nachung uva alhunsah ding, khosih, tipat, tichung sat, chemjam pana nasat gamhel diu, nget leh thing lung nachung uva alhunsah ding, bolgimna hijatpi hi, nathi masang seuva najui le diu ahi.  
\v 23 Nalu lam'uva von chengse sumeng kisoh tading, natahsa noilam chengseu thing kisoh ding ahi.  
\v 24 Chuteng Pakai, Pathen'in na gamsung'uva gotwi jouse leivui leh neldi aki sosah ding, nathi masang seuva van'a konna hung leng suh suh jing ding ahi.  
\v 25 Pakaiyin nangho namel mateu masanga na panpi lou diu, na melmateu toh ki maito dinga lampi khat seh bou na juisah diu, nagal miteu masanga lampi sagi kisoa na jam cheh diu, hi tia chu leiset chunga lenggam jouse lah a kicha puma hinkho naman jing diu ahi.  
\v 26 Nathi long jouseu chungleng vachaten aneh diu, leiset a ganhing namkim in kivahna anei diu, hitia chu aneh tengu leh, leiset a mihem khat jeng cha jong ahoh mang dinga hung ki lulah lou diu ahi.  
\v 27 Chuteng Pakaiyin Egypt gamsunga naum laiyuva uilut ana lansah banga ahin lansah kit ding, na tichung'u pom ding, thisan soh leu ding, boldammo hela tipat natna nanei uva hinkho naman diu ahi.  
\v 28 Pakaiyin nangol sah diu, kho namu thei lou diu, nalungthim pumpiu na suhnoh phahpeh diu ahi.  
\v 29 Chuteng nangho mitcho banga sun jenga jong naki mai lele diu, ipia ki salal jong leu chun na machal thei lou diu, mitin in nasuh genthei diu chule amaho chun nachom gamset diu ahina laiye.  
\v 30 Jidia numei nakihol diu, amanu chu pasal dangkhat toh lum khom ding, in jong naki sah diu hinlah asunga nachen theilou diu ahi. Chule lengpi lei jong nalho diu, ahinlah aga chu naneh thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 31 Nama sang laiyuva na bongchal uchu ki that ding ahinlah asa chu naneh thei lou diu, hunama nasangan'u kila ding ahinlah na kile lah thei tah lou diu, nakelngoi jeng ujong nangho melmate khut a kipedoh ding, koima chan nangho napan hu tahlou diu ahi.  
\v 32 Chule nachanuteu ahin, nachapa teu abonchauva namdang te khut a kipedoh tadiu, nilhum in velhijongleuchun nachan kit tahlou diu, naban thahat'u pana amaho chudoh jouna tha nanei lou diu ahi.  
\v 33 Imatih a nahet khah lou'u nam dang khat in, nalou-gasoh'u nahin hampeh chai keiyun tin, chuteng nangho chunga tantih nei louva hiche thoh gimna chu um jing ding ahi.  
\v 34 Namit teniuvin venan nate, ahinlah nangho mingol kibol nabanga na kidel mang diu ahi.  
\v 35 Natibah hou hungdul doh ding, abeh beh a hung pat ding, na kengtouva pat nalu chan'u pat ding nadam doh lou diu ahi.  
\v 36 Nangho nahiuvin, nachung uva lengvai homte ahin, Pakaiyin napu, napa teu jengin jong ahet phah louhel nam mite khat angsunga nahin puilut diu, hiche mun'a chu thing le songa kisem pathen lim nahou diu ajen lea napan diu ahi.  
\v 37 Hiche mun'a chu Pakaiyin napui lhung diu, mitin ma angsunga kicha puma naum lodiu, imatih chana sei chah a naum diu ahi.  
\v 38 Chule loulaiya tuthei muchi ijakai napoh diu, ahinlah aga seikham lou chakhat nalo khom diu, ajeh chu khaokhopi ten aneh chaigam diu ahi bouve.  
\v 39 Lengpi lei jeng jong nalho'uva naki sah lel pi diu, ahinlah lengpitwi chu nadon louhel diu, hiche lengpi chu lung in aneh gamset ding ahi.  
\v 40 Nachennau gamsunga Olive thingphung tampi nanei diu, ahinlah atwi chu nakinu thei deh deh lou diu ahi. Ajeh chu Olive thingphung nanei chengseu aboncha kisat chop ding ahi.  
\v 41 Chule nang hon chapa tamtah nanei diu, ahinlah khat a khat jeng cha jong nachan lou diu, aboncha sohchang dinga chediu chule nangho panhu ding mihem khat jeng cha jong kisep louding ahi.  
\v 42 Nathing phunghou ahin chule nachennau leiset aboncha khaokhote chenna jeng ding ahi bouve.  
\v 43 Na heng uva hung chenga kholjin mi chu nangho sanga khang toujing ding, nangho vang na kheh suh cheh cheh diu ahi.  
\v 44 Nanghon jong ama kom'a chu thil ijakai bat a nakilah diu, ama jeng hatna chang ding, nangho ameiya napan diu amavang alua pang ding ahi.  
\v 45 Hiche ho jouse hi gaosapna ahin nachung uva lhung tading, hichengse chun nangho nung ahindel ding naphah thu thu'uva, chuteng nangho naki suhgep hel diu ahi, ajeh chu nang hon Pakai, Pathen thusei nangai tapouvin, achonna dan thupeh chengse jong jui ding nagel lou-u ahi.  
\v 46 Hitobang gaosapna hi nachung uva um jing ding, melchihna le datmo umtah soh ding, nachi lhahteu chan geiya mangthei louva um jing ding ahi.  
\v 47 Chuteng nangho thil hijat jouse chunga hin lungthim kipah in naum jou tahih uvin, Pakai, Pathen kin jeng jong bolding nago tapouve.  
\v 48 Chule nangho gilkela naum diu, ponsil jeng jong nanei lou diu, thilse hijat chunga jong Pakaiyin namel mateu dinga ahinsol miho jenlea napan diu, naman thah kahseuva sohnam kihen oh nachun nakan chah diu ahi.  
\v 49 Hitia chu nangho toh kidou dinga Pakaiyin, leiset kol ning lam akon nam khat ahin puiya, muvanlai banga hung leng lut jeng diu, hiche nam mite pao chu het jong nahet phah lou diu,  
\v 50 Hiche nam mite chu ahang san uvin, upaho jong aging pouvin chule khangdong ho jong aging pouvin ahi.  
\v 51 Amaho hin nagancha teu akitha diu, nasuh gep kahse uva abol diu, na chang jeng ujong themcha akhen lou diu, lengpithei leh thaotwi themcha jong akhen lou diu, nagan chateu ahin na kelngoinouteu ahin, aboncha asuh gamkah seuva ama hon nachennau gamsung adalhah louhel diu ahi.  
\v 52 Na chennau gam na kisonpi namun'u khopi kul sangtah tah’a ki kaina mun ho, naum kim veluva avoh chim kah seuva ano khum diu, hitobanga chu Pakai, Pathen'in napehnau gamsung khopi jousea ngengsi khong tading, tang louva na umkhum diu ahi.  
\v 53 Nanghoa kon ahung pengdoh nachanuteu leh nachapa teu aboncha Pakaiya konna gou thilpeh manlutah hijongleh, namel mateu'vin nahin umkhum uva nagim behseh tengu leh na kitha diu amaho chu anneh a nanei diu ahi.  
\v 54 Nangho lah a milung neng ahin, ahongphal ahin, nasopi ahin, najinu hijongleh neh ding vetsahna a hung pang tading, nachateu lah uva athinu khah pen jong chu neh ki chupia hung pang ding ahi.  
\v 55 Mi phatah khat jong chun achate akithaa aneh teng, ama tahsa jeng jong chu hop ding agel louhel ding ahi. Ajeh chu namel mateu vin na khopi sung jouseu aumkimvel soh hel tauvin ahileh, nagim behseh jeng tauve.  
\v 56 Chule numei chonnem tah le lungneng nu, achon nem behseh jeh a akeng khotaljum jeng jong tol chotsah nom louhel nu chun, ajipa le achanu leh achapte jeng jong akitha aneh ding ahi. \x + \xo 28:56 \xt 2 Lengte 6:28,29; Ka La 4:10\x*  
\v 57 Hiche numei ho chun, akal kah a konna hung peng naosen chu akidop lhah a aneh jeng diu ahi. Ajeh chu namel mateu vin nasugim behseh tauvin, na umkhum sohhel tauvin ahileh, neh leh chah ijakai khat a khat jengcha jong mun'a nanei tapouve.  
\v 58 Hijeh chun hiche lekhabua danthu kijih jouse hi aboncha nanit bukimsohkeiyuva, limgeh chaa nakho sah lou uva, Pakai, Pathen hi na kichat a najabol diu ahi.  
\v 59 Achuti louva ahileh, Pakaiyin nachung uva gim gentheina sangpen ahin lhunsah ding, hiche chung chona chu natna nasatah hunglhung ding tantih nei louva nadammo diu nachung uva hichu ahin lhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 60 Egypt gamsunga nat thohlel naho jouse avel'a nachung uva ahin lhunsah ding, tantih nei louva gim genthei nathoh diu ahi.  
\v 61 Nangho naki suh mang kahseava dinga danthua kijih lutlou natna jouse hi, Pakaiyin nachung uva ahin lhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 62 Nangho hapun in pungbe uvin lang, vanna ahsija pha jong leu chun, lhomcha bou nahi diu ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon Pakai, Pathen thusei nangai tapouve.  
\v 63 Pakaiyin nachung uva thilpha ahin lhunsah a alung oi ji bang’a, hitobang gimna ahung lhun teng jongleh lungoi ding ahi. Na chennau gamsunga konna nadel mang jeng diu ahi.  
\v 64 Pakaiyin leiset kong ningli jousea nathe cheh jeng diu, napu napa teu jengin jong ahet khah louna mun, hiche mun'a chu milimsemthu pathen nahou diu, akinbola nagapan diu ahi.  
\v 65 Chule hiche munhoa chu namtin vaipi dimlha jeng ding, ong thol heuva nachen louhel diu, na keng khotal kisan'u kichol louding, nalungthim'u linglao tading, namit vet jeng ujong phamo tading, nahinkho jeng ujong genthei ding maonaa kichai ding ahi.  
\v 66 Asun ajana kichatna jing hinkho naman diu, nahinkho sung'uva lungngam pela naum thei lou diu ahi.  
\v 67 Jingkah ahileh, O nilhah ka lhangai ta ngeiye, nilhah teng O, jingkah ka lhangai ta ngei! tia nasei diu, namit teniuva navet diu hichu kichatna jingin navop diu, hahsatna chun naum pi jing diu ahi.  
\v 68 Chujou tengleh Pakaiyin Egypt gam lama nahin lepui kit diu, keiman hiche lampi chu na le che kit lou diu ahi, tijong leng Pakaiyin nahin lepui kit diu, namel mateu angsunga soh numei chule soh pasala nagapan sohkeidiu, hiche jouse nunga jong chu koiman nachoh nom lou diu ahi.   
\c 29  
\s1 Kitepna kithah sem  
\p
\v 1 Pakaiyin Horeb molchunga akitepna thu anasei, Moab gamsunga Israel mite henga Mose adin a thupeh kitepna asemho chu hi chengse hi ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Mose’n Israel mi chan chu akou khomsohkeiyin aheng uvah thu aseitan ahi. Egypt gamsunga naum laiyuva Pakaiyin Pharaoh chunga ipi abola chuleh asohte ahin, agamsung pumpi abolna jouse namit tah uvin na musoh tauve.  
\v 3 Nanghon melchihna leh Patepna tinchang tothoa, thil kidang tampi namit uva namu sohkeiyu ahitai.  
\v 4 Ahinlah Pakayin tuni chan in, nangho jouse hetkhen theina lungthim nape hihlai uve.  
\v 5 Keiman nangho gamthip noiya kum somli sungin kapui leuvin, natahsa chung uva ponsil kaijouse khat jeng cha jong aehpon, nakeng chut jeng ujong khat jeng cha asepon ahi.  
\v 6 Keima hi nangho jouse Pakai, Pathen kahi nahetdoh theina diuvin, nang hon changlhah nane pouvin, twi jong nadon pouvin, khamna thei kiti jong nadonkha pouvin ahi.  
\v 7 Ahinlah Hesbon lengpa Og chun kisatpi dingin eihin nailut tauvin ahileh, hikom'a chun eihon jong amani chunga galjona chu inei tauve. \x + \xo 29:7 \xt Minbu 21:21-30; \xt Minbu 21:31-35\x*  
\v 8 Chuin hiche teni gam chu ilahpeh tauvin, Reuben in gouva alo dingin agam keh khatset chu ipeuvin ahi. \x + \xo 29:8 \xt Minbu 32:33\x*  
\v 9 Chuti ahijeh chun hiche kitepna thudol'a kisei thudol ho hi, aboncha nabol sohhel theina diuvin ching thei un, chutin bolleu chun na khut a nathil bol jouseu nakhan tou thei diu ahi.  
\v 10 Tunia hi nangho na boncha uva Pakai, Pathen angsunga nadin sohkeidiu ahi. Nangma phungkhai sung cheh akon lamkai, upaho chule nalah uva vaihom ho jaona Israel mi kitiphot thonlouva pang ding ahi.  
\v 11 Numei chapang ho jouse, ngahmun a cheng khopem ho ahin, nathing poa pang ahin, natwi thala pang mi hijongleh jao kimsohkei ding ahi.  
\v 12 Nangman jong Pakai, Pathen kihahselna banga hitia chu nabol ding, tunin nangman Pakai, Pathen nang toh asemna kitepna sunga hi nalut ding ahi.  
\v 13 Ajeh chu hitia nabol tengleh, Pakaiyin nangma nam khat dinga natun doh ding, nangma kom'a asei dohsa leh napu, napa Abraham, Isaac, Jacob henga athutep banga nangma Pathen jong ahi.  
\v 14 Hiche kitepna hi keiman nangho toh keima kikah dinga bou kasem ahipoi.  
\v 15 Tunin ilah uva jaolou hihen lang, Pakai, Pathen asunga um jouse dinga jong ki semdoh ahi.  
\v 16 Egypt gamsunga ichenlai uva pat, namtin vaipi ijat hamkhat nahin pal galkai tauve, tihi na hesohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 17 Hiche mun'a chu namtin vaipi thilbol thet um tahtah thing leh song’a ki sem milim doi jouse ahin, dangka leh sanaa kisem, hitobanga milim doi ki semthu jouse abonchan na mittah uvin namusoh tauve..  
\v 18 Ajeh chu nalah uva pasal khat ham, numei khat ham, insung khat, namkhat chu alungthim ahei mang jenga hiche milimdoi ki semthu ho kinbola pang jeng thei ahi. Chule nalah uva konna thilse khat chu hung kondoh jeng thei ahin, thingga nehthei lou akha ahinsoh doh jeng ding ahi. \x + \xo 29:18 \xt Heb 12:15\x*  
\v 19 Mi khat touvin kitepna thu kisei doh chengse ahin jah doh a, ama leh ama kichoi sang nan nei ta henlang; alungthim sunga hiti hin sei jeng taleh, ka lungthim sunga louchal tah in thusei jong leng, ka thi louding ahi. Dangchah pet tah a twidon dinga aum laiya twijin alhoh banga, manthahna akibol doh teitei ding ahi.  
\v 20 Hitobanga chon mihem chu Pakaiyin ngaidam achan louding, hitia doumah bol mihem chunga chu Pakai lunghang ding; danthu lekhabua kisun gaosapna jouse amapa chunga chu hunglhung jeng ding, chuteng Pakaiyin hiche pa min chu vannoiya asuhmanga avel'a umkit talou ding ahi.  
\v 21 Danthu kisutna lekhabua kitepna chuleh gaosapna ki seidoh bang’a chu gaosapna achung’a lhung jeng ding, hi tia chon mihem chu Pakaiyin Israel mite lah a konna apam paidoh jeng ding ahi.  
\v 22 Ahung khanglen ding khangdong ho, nama banuva hung kipatdoh ding nachateu ahin, hetphah lou gam'a konna hung kholjin mi jaona Pakaiyin agimsah nau, gentheina chungnung hi amittah uva ahin musah tengu leh ahet them diu ahitai.  
\v 23 Gamsunga cheng jousen kat-song leh chilhang abah diu, muchi tuna lou mun jouse imacha keh talou ding, Sodom leh Gomorrah banga kile khup jenga, Admah leh Zeboiim banga Pakaiyin alunghan teng alekhup del tobang soh ding ahi. \x + \xo 29:23 \xt Semtilbu 19:24,25\x*  
\v 24 Namtin in hitia asei ding, ipi jeh pen tah’a Pakaiyin hiche gamsung hi hitia hi abol jeng hitam? Ipi jeh a hiti loma hi lunghang ahidem? tia asei diu, tija sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 25 Chutengleh mipin hitia hi asei diu, amaho hi Egypt gamsunga aum laiyuva apu, apate hou henga Pakaiyin athupeh angai lou jeh uva, hitobang hi achung uva lhung ahi.  
\v 26 Ajeh chu ama hon pathen limsemthu kinbol len apang uvin, chibai aboh un, Pakaiyin abol diuva adeilou beh thil abol tauvin pathen limsem thu ahou un chule ahetkhah louhel ’u ahou tauvin ahileh, achung uva hitobang thil khu lhung ahiye.  
\v 27 Hijeh achu gamsunga Pakai lunghanna hunglhung jenga, hiche danthu lekhabua kisun gaosapna jouse hi hunglhung jeng ahitai.  
\v 28 Pakai, Pathen chu alunghang behseh jeng tan ahileh, hiche nam mite hi agamsunga konna apaidoh jenga, tulai din mun'a aum bang uva gamdangte khut’a apehdoh jeng ahi.  
\v 29 Thil jouse hi Pakai, Pathen a bou ahin, aki phongdoh jouse jong danthua kisei aumsa ho bou ahin, hichengse hi atonsot tonsot a ichateu khang chana ding ahi.   
\c 30  
\s1 Kisih jeh a kipaman  
\p
\v 1 Hichengse hin nahin lhun den jeng uva, ka seidohsa phattheina leh gaosapna ahin, Pakai, Pathen henga nacheuva hiche gamsunga chu nachen tengu leh, na lungthim uva nageldoh sohkei diu ahi.  
\v 2 Chuteng nang hon nahin nachateu chengse jaona a Pakai, Pathen henga na hung kile diu, tunia ka thupeh chengse hi Pakai awgin mong ahiti, kichihset a najah a nangai diu ahi.  
\v 3 Pakai, Pathen'in na phattheina diu lampi ahinsem ding, na chunguva lungsetna aumsah ding, Pakaiyin muntin'a nathe cheh nauva konna nahin suh khom kit diu ahi.  
\v 4 Vannoi tin chenga kithe cheh jong leu chun, hiche mun'a kon chun Pakai, Pathen'in nahin sukhom sohkeiyun tin, khat jeng cha jong ki dalha louva na kisuh kimsel diu ahi.  
\v 5 Pakai, Pathen'in napu luiteu chenna mun'a chu nahin puilut diu, hiche mun'a chu chenna phatah nanei diu, Pakaiyin napu luiyu, napa luiteu sanga haosatna napeh diu, ha puna na punbe diu ahi.  
\v 6 Pakai, Pathen'in nangho leh na chilhah teu lungthim sunga chep atan ding, chuteng Pakai, Pathen chu na lungthim sung pumpiuva na ngailut diu chule na hebol diu ahi.  
\v 7 Chule Pakai, Pathen'in nangho sugentheiya pang galmite chunga, gaosapna hichengse hi aboncha alhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 8 Chuni tengleh nang hon avel'a Pakai awgin na ngaiyuva, Pakaiya konna thupeh keiman ka pehson chengse aboncha na nitsohkei diu ahi.  
\v 9 Nangho Pakai, Pathen'in nabol natohna jouseu natha hatsah diu, na haodoh sah jeng diu, na chilhah teu ahin, na ganchateu ahin, thalhing sohkei diu ahi. Ajeh chu napu luiteu ahaosat uva akipa bang uva, Pakaiyin nangho na haosah'uva nakipa diu chu adeisah ahi.  
\v 10 Nanghon Pakai, Pathen thupeh chengse hi na ngaiyuva, achonna jouse, danthu lekhabua kisun jouse hi nanit sohkeiyuva, na chilhah teu ahin, na ganchateu ahin, na theiga hou jong aboncha bulhing sel ding ahi. Ajeh chu napu luiyu, napa luiteu ahao banga nangho jong na haosat uva Pakai, Pathen henga na hung kihei lut diu ahi.   
\s1 Hinna leh thina  
\p
\v 11 Ajeh chu tunia ka thupeh chengse hi thil hahsa tah leh, jui hah ding ahipoi.  
\v 12 Chule hiche hi van'a aum in, nang hon ijah uva iboldoh na diuvin, koiham van'a kal touva thuchin eihin poh peh diu ham tinjong seihih un. \x + \xo 30:12 \xt Rm 10:6-8\x*  
\v 13 Nanghon hiche hi twikhanglen gala uma, koipen ham ilah uva galkaiya thuchin eihin poh peh diu ham? tiajong na sei lou diu ahi.  
\v 14 Hichengse hi gamla tah a aumpon, na lungthim uleh na kam sung'uva bou um ahi. Hitobang hi nang hon nabol doh diu mong ahi.  
\v 15 Vetan, keiman na masang lam'uva hinna leh thilpha kakoi in, thina leh thilse jong ka koipeh uve.  
\v 16 Pakai, Pathen'in na thupeh chengseu keiman ka seidoh peh ho hi nanit sohkeiyuva, Pakai, Pathen na ngailut uva, Ama lamlhah jenga bou nalam lhah uva, Ama thupeh chengse leh achonna dan jouse na nitsohkeijyuva ahileh, nangho na pun diu, chule tua na jot lutna diu gamsunga khu phattheina lhingset na chan diu ahi.  
\v 17 Ahinlah na lungthim'uva na kihei mang jeng uva, Pakai thupeh chengse nahsah moa na um-uva ahileh, pathen limsemthu chibai boh midang toh na che khah uva, hiche ho chu na jen leava ahileh,  
\v 18 Tunia hi na jah uva ka seipeh nahiuve, nangho naboncha uva manthah nan nalhun den diu ahi. Jordan vadung galkaiya chenna dinga na che lutna diu mun'a khu, iti nama jongleh na chensot lou diu ahi.  
\v 19 Tunin keiman nangho douna hettohsah na dingin van leh lei kakou khom in, ajeh chu na masang lam'uva hinna leh thina ka koipeh un, phattheina leh gaosapna jong ka koipeh un ahi. Hijeh chun tunin hinna hi kilhen unlang nason na chilhah jeng ujong hinna chang diu ahi.  
\v 20 Pakai, Pathen ngailutna neiyun lang, athupeh chengse nit jingun, ama jenga kingai leu chun thilpha ahi. Ajeh chu nangho dinga hinna leh hinkho sotna ahin, chuteng Pakaiyin napu luiyu Abraham, Isaac chule Jacob henga akihahsel a, amaho peh dinga ana kitepna gamsunga khu nangho na chen diu ahi. \x + \xo 30:20 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; \xt Semtilbu 26:3; \xt Semtilbu 28:13\x*   
\c 31  
\s1 Joshua ngensena  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Mose’n Israel mite henga, thu hi chengse hi aseipeh in ahi.  
\v 2 Ajah uvah hiti hin aseiye, tunin keima kum jakhat leh kum somni ka lhing tai, ajeh chu keima che le vale kabol tahlou ding hichu Pakaiyin ka henga aseiyin, nangman hiche Jordan hi nagal kai thei louding ahi, ati. \x + \xo 31:2 \xt Minbu 20:12\x*  
\v 3 Pakai, Pathen chu nama sang lam'uva che ding, Aman nalam kai diu nama sang lam'uva namtin vaipi hijat pi hi asuhmang jeng ding, nama sang'uva nam mite hon chenna ding gam anei lou diu ahi. Pakai thupeh banga Joshua in nalam kai lhung diu ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche nam tin vaipi khu jat chunga khu, Pakaiyin Amor mite lah a leng teni Sihon leh Og abolna bang banga asuhmang diu ahi. \x + \xo 31:4 \xt Minbu 21:21-35\x*  
\v 5 Pakaiyin amaho jouse khu nangho khut a ahin pehdoh ding, chuteng keiman ka thupeh banga hi nabol diu ahi.  
\v 6 Kichatna ima nanei thei lou diu, chule nahat uva nahansan diu, ging louhel a naum diu ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon na kilhon piu hi Pakai, Pathen ahijingin, Pakaiyin na umpi jing uvin nadalhah louhel diu ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin Mose’n jong Joshua akouvin Israel mite jouse mitmun aheng’a hiti hin aseipeh tai. Hat unlang hangsan uvn, mipi hijat hi napuiyuva Pakaiyin apu apateu khanga akitepna gamsung’a na puilut diu, amaho hi hiche gamsunga chu nachen sah a agam pumpi nalo sah tei diu ahi.  
\v 8 Na masang lam'uva lamkai hi Pakai bou ahin, aman nalhonpi jingun, dalha louva ijakai asuh bukim soh ding, hiche miho chunga khu kichatna nanei lou diu, lungthoi louhela naum jing diu ahi. \x + \xo 31:8 \xt Joshua 1:5; Heb 13:5\x*   
\s1 Kum sagi seh leh sim ding danthu ho  
\p
\v 9 Chuin Mose’n danthu chu asundoh in, danthu lekhabu chu Levi chapa te Pakai thingkong pua pangho chengse chu abonchan ape sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 10 Mose’n amaho chengse chu thu apen hiti hin aseiye. Kum sagi ahung kichaiya, ki lhadohna phat ahung lhin teng, hichu Lhambuh Kut bolphat toh kitoh ding ahi. \x + \xo 31:10 \xt Danbu Ni Na 15:1,2; \xt Danbu Ni Na 16:13-15\x*  
\v 11 Israel mite hi Pakai, Pathen'in adeilhen namun'a chu ahung kilah tengleh, Israel mite jouse jah dinga hiche danthu lekhabu hi nasem doh ding ahi.  
\v 12 Mipi ho chu nakhop kimsohkei ding, pasal ahin, numei ahin, ajahsohkei diu Pakai, Pathen gindan ahet them cheh diu, hiche danthua ki sei jouse aboldoh sohkei na diuva nathu mop cheh diu ahi.  
\v 13 Ajakha loulai achilhah te geiyin ajah theina dingin, Jordan galkaiya hiche gamsung nalut tengu leh hichengse hi nachate hou nahil jing diu ahi.   
\s1 Mose henga Pakai akilahna  
\p
\v 14 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin, nathi nading nikho ahung naitai, Joshua henga seiyin lang ponbuh sunga hung lut lhonin, chutengleh keiman Joshua hi tha kapeh kit ding ahi. Hiti chun Mose leh Joshua jong achelhonin, ponbuh sunga chun aga lut lhon tan ahi.  
\v 15 Chutah chun Pakai chu ponbuh sunga meibang lom banginahung kilah in ahung kitung tan ahi. Hiti chun meibang lom chu ponbuh kotpi phung achun khom banginakitung tan ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Pakaiyin, Mose henga aseiyin, ven! Nangma napu, napate toh nalup khom nading phat ahung naitai. Nangma nung tengleh hiche mite hi abonchauva ahet phah lou nau gamsung ahin chot lut diu, pathen limsemthu nung ahinjui uva, notiho lah a vahlut gamdiu, keima umna jeng jong hepha louva umdiu, keima toh kitepna kasem jeng jong asuh keh hel diu ahi.  
\v 17 Chutia achon ni tengu leh keima lunghanna achung uva hung soudoh jeng ding, keiman jong amaho kanung ngat jeng ding, chuteng mihon amaho abah gam jeng diu, thilse tincheng le hesoh gentheinan abop diu, eiho Pathen'in eiumpi lou phat uva thilse hijatpi hi eiho chunga hunglhung jeng ahitai, tia asei diu ahi.  
\v 18 Hitia thil ahin bol nitengu leh keiman jong amahoa konna kamai kasel manga ka nung sun diu, ajeh chu amaho hin pathen semthu ho abel gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Tun nang hon hichengse sun doh unlang, Israel mite henga nahil them diu ahi. Hiche hi Israel mite douna keima hettohsahna apang jing din akam sung uvah mop sohkeiyun.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu apu, apate hou peh dinga ka kihahselna gamsung khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gamsunga ka hinpui lut phat uvin, anomsa gam tauvin, tun akihei mang gamsohkeiyun pathen chom chom abel tauvin, hiche ho kinbol in apang un, keima don louvin eikoi tauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Thilse tinchengin ahin lhun den diu, hiche la hi amaho dinga hettohsanaa hung pang jing ding ahi. Hiche la hi haimil louhela achilhah teu khangeiya achin jing diu, ajeh chu keiman katepna gamsunga kahin puilut masang uva alunggel ngaitou ijakai ka hetsoh ahitai.  
\v 22 Chuin Mose’n jong hiche nikho mama chun la chu asundoh in, Israel mite jouse ahilthem sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 23 Pakaiyin, Nun chapa Joshua tha apen ahenga hiti hin aseipeh e. Hat jingin, hangsan jingin, ajeh chu nangman Israel chate jouse ka kitepna gamsunga khu nahin puilut ding, keiman kaumpi jing nai, ati. \x + \xo 31:23 \xt Minbu 27:23; Joshua 1:6\x*  
\v 24 Mose’n jong hiche danthu chengse chu abonchan asundoh sohkeiyin, achaina geiyin asundoh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Mose’n Pakai kitepna thingkong pua pang, Levi mite henga hiti hin aseipeh tauve.  
\v 26 Hiche danthu lekhabu hi, Pakai kitepna thing kong sunga chun koijun, hiche hi nangho douna hettohsahnaa pang jing ding ahi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu doumah mah in nachon in, nalou chal e tijong kahen, tun vevin, nangho toh kaum jingin jong Pakai doumah tampi nabol un, ka thi nung le ijat nabolbe diu hitam!  
\v 28 Nalah uva upaho jouse na phung kailhah cheh uva kon'in ka henga hinsol tauvin, nalah uva vaihoma pangho jong hinkou khom unlang, thu hijat chengse hi aheng uva ka seipeh ding, amaho douna hettohsana apang dinga van leh leiset kakou khom ding ahi.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu keima thi nung teng melse tah tah a nachon diu, ka thupeh jousea konna na kihei manghel diu ahiti, ka hesohkeiyin, akhon nileh nachung uva thilse hunglhung ding, Pakai mit mua thilse jeng nahin bol diu, nakhut chaloh danu ijakaiya konna Pakai lunghanna na chung uva hunglhung ding ahi.  
\v 30 Mose’n jong hiche la chu Israel mite jouse nabenga ahetsah tan ahi.   
\c 32  
\s1 Mose labol  
\p
\v 1 Vannoi leiset pumpin ngaiyun, ajeh chu keiman naheng uva hiche thu hi ka seiyin ahi. Keima kam sunga konna thu kisei hi leiset pumpin ngaisohkeiyun.  
\v 2 Keiman nangho jah ding’a ka sei hi goju bang jeng hen, chule ka thusei jong daitwi banginkai jeng hen, hampa lah gotwi nel banginkai hen, hamhing lah a gotwiju banginhung hen, ati.  
\v 3 Ajeh chu keiman Pakai min ka sam jal jengin, O Pathen alen tangeiye, tin sam cheh uhen!  
\v 4 Pathen hi songpi ahin, athilbol achamkim tangeiye. Ajeh chu alamlhah aboncha thudih jeng ahin, temmona imacha umlou leh kitahna dim jeng ahin, a kitah le adihna jeng ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche mite hon vang Ama hi a lam louvin abol'un, abonchauvin achate hi khalou tobang asoh tauvin, ajeh chu abonchauva nolna jeng ahiuvin, khang lamvaitah le lungput gih tah ahiuve.  
\v 6 Hitobanga chu Pakai hi lethuhna nei ding nagot uham, vo lungthim beiho, angol gam'a na hitauve! Ama hi nasempa, na Pathen hilou ham? Nangho sema tungdoh achu koi ham?  
\v 7 Nikho masa lai chu geldoh in, kum masa laiya khang tamtah jong chu geldoh in, napa chu kidoh un aman nahil chen sohkei diu, na upate hou dong leu chun ama hon nahil diu ahi.  
\v 8 Hatchungnung pen in nampi goulo ahop peh chun, Aman mihem chate alheng khen sohkeiyin. Israel mite atam leh alhom dungjuijin gamgi anasat khen pehsohkeiyin ahi. \x + \xo 32:8 \xt Act 17:26\x*  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Pakai chan chu amite chan ding ahin, Jacob hi ama chan ding hichu agoulo ding mong ahi.  
\v 10 Jacob chu gamthip laiya akimu in, gam mang thim lah a ki mudoh ahi. Pakaiyin ama hi aveng tup jingin, khohsahna anei jingin, hiti chun amitmu jenga khohsahna lhingsel aneiyin ahi.  
\v 11 Muvanlai in abu avil jinga, abu sunga anoute avet lhih jing banginave lhih jingin ahi. Jacob hi kolchah jing dingin alhaving ajah dohjin, alhaving’a Jacob hi apo le jin ahi.  
\v 12 Pakai ama tah in ahin pui len, Jacob in aki voppi chu pathen dang ahipoi.  
\v 13 Pakaiyin ama chu leiset chung mun sang lai laiya atousah jin, aman jong lhosohga akilo jin ane jin ahi. Songpia kon'in khoiju achepsah jin, meituh song a kon'in jong thaotwi apotdohsah jin ahi.  
\v 14 Bonghon lah a kon'in bongnoi apen, kelngoi hon lah a kon'in noitwi apejin, kelngoite ahin kelngoi chalte abonchan thaotwi in avah va jin, Bashan phaichama bonghon leh kelchan avah jin ahi. Suhlou chang leh lengpitwi chu nadon jin ahi.  
\v 15 Jeshurun chu ahung thaobehseh tan ahileh, akeng in athai mang mang in, nang jong nathao behseh tan nanoi gei gol jong achop lha jeng tan, Chuin asempa Pathen jeng jong asumil lotan, Ahuhhingpu Pathen jeng jong chu tot chavei nan aneitan ahi.  
\v 16 Hetphah lou pathen kin abol jeh uchun asu lunghang tauvin, chondan thet umtah tah abol'un, Pakai chu aphin lunghang tauve.  
\v 17 Pathen hilou thilha ho henga kilhaina asem uvin, imatih chana ahet phah lou-u pathen limsemthu, pathen lim kisem thu thahho, hitobang ho chu napu napate hon jong ana het khah louhel ahi. \x + \xo 32:17 \xt 1 Crth 10:20\x*  
\v 18 Nangman nasempa songpi chu nagel jing jeng pon, nahingpa Pathen hi nasumil tan ahi.  
\v 19 Pakaiyin athilbol-u ijakai amu chet phat in akidah lheh jeng tan, achapa te, acha nuteuvin aphin lunghang gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Pakaiyin aseijin, keiman hiche mihemte a konna kamai kasel mang ding, akhkonna geiya itobang tauvem ti ka vet lhih jing ding, amaho hi abonchauva khanglam vaitah ahiuvin, asung jeng uva jong tahsanna bei ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche mite ho hin Pathen hi lou achombeh pathen kinbol in apang tauvin, keima ei hepha tapouvin, milim doi asem hou jeh in keima kalung ahansah tauvin, ajeh chu keiman mihem to tethei lou ho kaphin lunghang’a achung uva ka thangtom sah ding, nam lah a angolpente ka phin lunghang peh ding ahiuve. \x + \xo 32:21 \xt 1 Crth 10:22; \xt Rm 10:19\x*  
\v 22 Keima kalung ahana kon'in mei ahung kong doh jengin, hiche meichun noimi gamchan akichai theiyin, leiset leh achunga thil jouse jong akichai hel soh jeng tan, molsang vum jouse jong meiyin akachai soh tan ahi.  
\v 23 Hiche mite chunga hi thilse simjou lou kasit dimset jeng ding, achung uva thalpi chang kakap ding ahi.  
\v 24 Hiche mite hi gilkela thigamna ato diu, meikong in aleugam diu, gamna huise in alhun den jeng diu, amaho douna gamsa ka hansah ding, leivuiya kithol gulsi achung uva kahan sah ding ahi.  
\v 25 Chule polama chemjam hem kalap sah ding, insung jenga jong tijatna jeng lhung ding, nungah—gollhangho aboncha thigam ding, nao noichep leh pasal sam kangsa jeng jong atha gamset ding ahi.  
\v 26 Keiman hitia hi ka seiya, gam jousea ka thejal soh hel ding, amaho geldohna bei hel ta ding ahi.  
\v 27 Hiche melmate kiletsahna hi kagin lou ham? Amelmate hou gilkel nan hinpha khante, ahilou jongleh hitia hi asei diu, ikhut thahat uvin gal ei josah tauvin, thil hichengse hi Pakaiyin eibol peh uva ahi oi, tia asei diu ahi.  
\v 28 Ajeh chu amaho hi lunggel beiya hinkho mang nam ahiuvin, alungthim sung uva jong hetkhenna ima umlou ahiye.  
\v 29 Hetkhenna nei hileu hitobang hi ahetthem diu, kho nung chana ato diu thil jong ahet khen thei diu ahi.  
\v 30 Mikhat chun mi sang khat chu adeljam thei pon, mini seh in jong mihem sangsom adeljam thei pon ahi.  
\v 31 Ajeh chu amaho songpi chu eiho songpi tobang ahi pon, imelma teu hi amaho leh amaho kah a thutan'a pang jeng ahiuve.  
\v 32 Amaho lengpi gui hi Sadom a konna hung jam lut ahin, Gomorrah loujao a konna hung jamdoh ahi. Hiche lengpiga ho chu thina thei jing ahin, agaboh jouse jong akha ngen ahi.  
\v 33 Amaho lengpitwi chu gulgu jeng ahin, aboncha gulsegu phalou ngen jeng ahi.  
\v 34 Hichengse keima kom'a kikhola ahipon, nathil khol khomna in mun'a chu mohor kinam khuma hilou ham?  
\v 35 Phulah leh lethuhna kiti hi ania keiya ahi. Ajeh chu keng aki lhonal uva, hamsetna ato na diu ahung nai tan ahileh, hichete manthahna chu hetphah louva hunglhung jeng ding ahi. \x + \xo 32:35 \xt Rm 12:19; Heb 10:30\x*  
\v 36 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin amite suhdihna anei ding, alhachate chunga jong lainatna ahin nei thei ding ahi. Athahat nau aboncha kichai tading, sohchanga ahin ipi hijongleh abeisoh tai, ti amuchet diu ahi. \x + \xo 32:36 \xt Labu 135:14\x*  
\v 37 Chuteng aman hiti ahi asei ding, hichete pathen limsem thu hoiya um hitam, akisel nau songpi hoiya um hitam, tia asei diu ahi.  
\v 38 Koiyin hiche te ho kilhaina sathao aneh a, lengpitwi don dinga kikoi jong koipen in adon hitam? Hitobang pathen limsem thu ho chu hung uvin tin, na thohgim nauva kon'in nahung pan pitao hen, ati.  
\v 39 Tun neihin vetem un, Pathen kiti chu keima tah hi kahin, keima tailou pathen dang aum pon, keima tah in mihem ka that jin, hin jong ka hinsah kitjin ahi. Kam'a vojin, ka sudam kit jitai, kei khut a konna eichulha jou ding koima dang aum pon ahi.  
\v 40 Ajeh chu keiman vanlam kasang'in, atonsot tonsot a hingjing ka hi jeh in hiti chun ka seiyin ahi.  
\v 41 Ka chemjam ka kinol hem teng ka khut a konna thutanna ka neiyin ahi. Keima eidou chan chunga phulahna ka lhunsah ding, keima eithette chunga lethuhna ka lhunsah ding ahi.  
\v 42 Kathalpi chang jouse thisan a ka dekot ding, ka chemjam jengin jong tahsa jeng asat gamhel ding, akithatsa mihemho thisan, sohchanna gal hinga kikai ho, melma samsao tah tah ho lu ka tansah jin ahi.  
\v 43 Vo namtin vaipite jouse, vahchoi un amiten, ajeh chu Pakaiyin alhachaa pangte thisan phu chu alatan ahi. Ama doute chunga phu alan, amite ding mong monga gam sung hi asuh theng ahi. \x + \xo 32:43 \xt Rm 15:10; Rev 19:2\x*  
\v 44 Chuin Mose chu Nun chapa Joshua toh ahung kilhonin, Mose ahin Joshua ahin ahi lhonin Israel mite jouse henga la thu kisei chu ana beng uvah ajah cheh na diuvin aseipeh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 45 Mose’n thu chu jat chu Israel mite jouse henga aseipeh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 46 Mose’n miho jouse henga hiti hin aseiyin. Tunia keiman naheng uva thu hijat ka seipeh chengse hi na lungthim cheh uvah koi sohkeiyun, hichu nung teng nachate hou henga naseipeh thei diu, chuteng ama hon jong hiche danthu a kisei doh jouse hi aboldoh tei na diuva ching thei tah a um ding ahiuve.  
\v 47 Hiche hi nangho jouse dinga thasetna ding ahipon, nahin theina diujoh ahi. Hichea konna nagal kai nadiu Jordan gal gamsunga khu nahin khou sot ding ahi, tin aheng uvah aseipeh e.   
\s1 Mose athi dinga nebo molsang lam ajut  
\p
\v 48 Chuni ma ma chun Pakaiyin, Mose jah a hiti hin aseipeh in ahi. \x + \xo 32:48 \xt Minbu 27:12-14; Danbu Ni Na 3:23-27\x*  
\v 49 Jericho toh kigalsai, Moab gamsunga, Nebo molsang, Abarim molsang kiti lai akhun kaldoh in, hiche mun'a kon khun keiman Israel mite chenna dinga kapehna gamsung, Canaan gamsung khu nagavet ding ahi, ati.  
\v 50 Hiche nakal touna molsang chunga khu nahung thiden ding, namite hotoh nahung kigop khom ding ahi. Hor molsang chunga nasopipa Aaron athia amite toh akigop khom banga nangma jong nachuti ding ahi, ati.  
\v 51 Ajeh chu Zin gamthip noi, Meribath-Kadesh twi phunga Israel mite lailungtah ah keima thu napal keh in, hiche mun'a chun Israel mite lah keima hi atheng in nei bol tapon ahi.  
\v 52 Hijeh achu nangman namasang lama hiche gamsung khu namit a namu bepding, ahinlah keiman Israel mite kapehna gamsung vang nachutlut thei louding ahitai.   
\c 33  
\s1 Mose’n ama phungsung cheh phatthei abohna  
\p
\v 1 Hiche hi Pathen mi Mose chun athi masanga Israel mite phatthei abohna thuchang chu ahi.  
\v 2 Mose’n hiti hin aseiyin, Sinai molsang akipat Pakai ahung kondoh tai, Seir a kon'in eiho mun ahunglhung tan, Paran molsang chun ahinsal vah jengin, Mitheng sang-som kikhopna kon chun ahungin, Pakai chun akhut jet lama kon'in meikong chu diu jejun ahin choiyin ahi.  
\v 3 Pakaiyin amite ho angailun, Pakai dinga thensona chang jouse chu akhut a um ahi. Ama hon nanung ahinjui diu, nangma a konna kihil diu ahi.  
\v 4 Mose’n keiho jouse dingin danthubu khat eikoi peh tauve, hichu Jacob mite dinga agoulo diuva apeh ahi.  
\v 5 Hiti chun Pakai chu Jeshurun mun'a leng achang tai, mipi lamkaiya pangho chu aki khomsohkeiyun, Israel phung jouse abonchan akikhom kimsohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 6 Reuben chu hingjing hen lang amite jong lhom cha hithei louding ahi, ati.  
\v 7 Mose chun hichengse hi Judah chung chang thudol'a asei ahi. O Pakai Judah taona awgin khu ngaiyin, Judah khu amite lah a hinpui lut teiyin, Nakhut ban thahat teni chun adihna khu panpi jou henlang, akidoupi jouse chunga jong jona chang hen, ati.  
\v 8 Levi chung chang thudol'a aman hiti hin aseiye; tun nangman Urim chu Levi henga pen lang, nadei sah tah pahi nangman petan, Massah mun'a napatepsa ahitan, Merribah mun'a twi najep doh sah ahi. \x + \xo 33:8 \xt Potdohbu 28:30; \xt Potdohbu 17:7; \xt Potdohbu 17:7; Minbu 20:13\x*  
\v 9 Hiche pa hin anu leh apa thudol'a hiti hin aseiyin, keiman kanu leh kapa kamu khapoi, ati. Asopi pasal chengse jong ahekha tapon, achate jouse jong hetphah in akoi tapoi. Ahinlah amaho chun nangma thusei jouse anit sohkeiyun, nakitepna jong anit jingun ahi.  
\v 10 Amaho hin nachon dan jouse Jacob hilna aman diu, nadan thu jouse jong Israel ahil diu ahi. Nangma angsunga gimnamtui alhutdiu, namai cham chunga jong pumgo thilto alhut vam diu ahi.  
\v 11 Pakai, anei agou jouse phattheiboh inlang, akhutsoh ijakai sanpeh tei teiyin lang, ama doumah a um jouse jong akhel buh vohchip peh inlang, amahot bolte aki thodoh kit louhel na diuvin boltan, ati.  
\v 12 Benjamin thudol'a aman hiti hin aseiye, Pakai ngailutna neipa, ama chu lung mong sel in acheng jing nai, Niseh in Pakaiyin ahongpha jing nan, alengkou teni ajong avengtup jing nai, ati.  
\v 13 Joseph thudol'a aman hiti hin aseitan, Joseph gamsung hi Pakaiyin phatthei abohtan, van gam a kon'in phatthei aboh in, leinoiya um thilpha chan geiyin apetan ahi.  
\v 14 Nisa a konna hung ga doh ji thing phapen chu apen, lha chu jat sung’a thing ga neng jen jun jong chu apen ahi.  
\v 15 Gollui laiya dinga thilpha pentah chu ahin, khangluiya pat beitih nei louva thinglhang mun nom ahi.  
\v 16 Leiset ga phapen leh asunga ga dimset ahin, hamboh lah a khosa pa dinga jong phatthei channa ahin, hichengse hi Joseph chunga hung um tahen lang, asopiho jouse lah a leng chapa bang’a umpa, a luchang’a akhuh lal lukhuh chung’a chun hunglhung jeng hen.  
\v 17 Ama dinga abongchal peng masa chun aloupina aki lahsah in, asaki jeng jong gam lah abongchal ki abangin ahi. Hiche ho jouse chu leiset kichaina lam chana galkai ding, Ephraim phung sunga galsatmi sang som soma pang chu ahiu vin, Manasseh phung a konna galsatmi asang sanga pang jong hiti ma chu ahisohkei uve.  
\v 18 Chule ama chun Zebulun chung chang thudol'a asei soh tan ahi. Nangma Zebulun vai nakon teng kipah leh thanom in kon doh jingin, Issachar nangma jong naponbuh sunga kipah leh thanom in um jingin, ati.  
\v 19 Amaho chun molsang chung dunga mitin vaipi akou khom diu, hiche mun'a chu kilhaina gantha adih lama abol diu, ajeh chu amaho hin twi khanglen twidan chu atep kha tauve, Neldi lei lah a gou ki sel guh jouse jong aga mudoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Gad chung chang thudol'a aseiyin, Koi hileh Gad dinga gam kehpeh achu nun nom hen, Gad hi sakeijin akol khum jin, ama chun miho ban aheh lha jin, amai akhot phon jin, aluchang jeng jong akhot eh peh jin ahi.  
\v 21 Ama chun gampha laitah ama ding chun akilhen doh tan, gal lamkaiya pang pa dinga kikoi chu aki mudoh tan ahi. Ama chu mipi lamkaiyin ahung pang doh tan, Pakaiya dia thu dih jing athu peh bang banginabol jin, Israel mite chung’a hiti chun vai ahom jin ahi.  
\v 22 Chule Dan chung chang thudol'a hiti hin aseiye, Dan hi sakei nou ahi. Ama chu Basan a kon'in ahung kichom doh jin ahi, ati.  
\v 23 Naptali thudol'a hiti hin aseiye, vo Naptali alungdei achun lunglhei jingin, hiche hi Pakaiya konna phattheina lhingset ahiye. Tui-khanglen leh lhanglam gamsung sese khu chonphan lang chenna gam in nei tan, ati.  
\v 24 Asher chung chang thudol'a hiti hin aseiye, Asher chate ho hi anunnom pen tah chu ahiuvin, hijeh achu asopi hon ama chunga hi lunglhaina anei cheh diu, akeng phang jeng jong thao twiya kide jol lha jeng ding ahi.  
\v 25 Nangma kelkot gol chu thih leh sum eng jeng hi ding, nadam sunga lungmong sela nachen ding ahi.  
\v 26 Jeshurun Pathen banga Pathen dang khat cha jong aumpon, nangma kithopi dinga van chunga toupa, alal loupina meibol lhang chung vum'a toupa ahi.  
\v 27 Tonsot Pathen hi nachenna mun ahin, abanjang thahat chun nangma nakol chah jingin ahi. Na masang lama namel mate adeljam in, sumang in tinjong aseitai.  
\v 28 Hiti chun Israel mite chu lungmong in acheng un, Jacob twinah chu lhen tum asoh doh tan ahi. Ajeh chu hiche mun chu chang phatna leh lengpitwi tamna mun ahi.  
\v 29 Vo Israel nangma anunnom nahiye, nang tobang ding koi ham? Pakaiyin ahuh hing nam mite, Pakai chu nangma din apang in, nagaljona chemjam ahi.  
\p Namelmate hon nangma suhmang ding nago uvinte, ahinlah nangman achen nau molsang jouse na chot chimsoh hel ding ahi.   
\p  
\c 34  
\s1 Mose thi  
\p
\v 1 Moab phaicham a kon'in Mose chu Jericho toh kinai Nebo molsang Pisgah molchunga chun akal tou tan ahi. Pakaiyin Mose chu gamsung jouse abonchan avetsah sohkeiyin, Gilead apat Dan chan chu avetsah sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 2 Naphtali gamsung jouse, Ephraim, Mannaseh, Judah gamsung leh lhum lam gamkai sung jouse ahi.  
\v 3 Negeb gamsung phaicham, tomthing kena mun, Jericho khopi phaicham apat Zoar mun chan ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga asei tan, Keima Abraham, Isaac leh Jacob henga ka kihahselna, keiman nason na chilhah te kapeh ding ahi, tia kaki tepna gam chu hiche hi ahi. Tun keiman namit in ka vetsah in, ahinlah hiche gamsung’a hi nangma nalut louhel ding ahitai, ati. \x + \xo 34:4 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; \xt Semtilbu 26:3; \xt Semtilbu 28:13\x*  
\v 5 Hiti chun Pakai lhacha Mose chu Pakai thusei bang chun Moab gam sung’a ahitan ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin Pathen'in Mose chu Beth-peor gal lam, Moab phaicham achun avuitan ahi, ahinlah tuni chan in koiman Mose kivuina lhan chu ahedoh pon ahi.  
\v 7 Mose athichun akum jakhat leh somni alhing tan, amit jong athim pon, athahatna jong alha kang hih laiyin ahi.  
\v 8 Israel mipi chu Moab phaicham sunga nisom thum sung in Mose puldounan akap tauvin ahi, Mose dingin thi opna kana chu alhung tan ahi.  
\v 9 Nun chapa Joshua chu Mose’n a chung’a akhut angap jeh in Joshua chu lhagao leh chihna adim jeng tan ahi. Pakaiyin Mose henga thu apeh bang chun Israel miten jong Joshua thusei ijakai angai tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche kalse chu Israel nam mite lah a kon'in Mose banga Pakaiyin amanchah themgao ahung peng doh tapon ahi. \x + \xo 34:10 \xt Potdohbu 33:11\x*   
\p
\v 11 Mose chu Egypt gamsunga melchihna  
\p tmapi abolsah in, thil kidang chujat abolsah in, Pharaoh leh asohte maija akilahsah in, Pharaoh angsung’a  
\p thilkidang akilahsahho bang a bolthei ding Israel sunga kon'in ahung peng doh tapon ahi.   
\p
\v 12 Thahatna kidangtah leh thilbol theina kidang nasatah tah Mose’n Israel mite lah a konna boldoh mihem khat a khat jeng cha jong akisep doh tapon ahi.   